quran[1606]{c,v,t}:
  50,1,Qaaf 128. Ndahiriye kuri iyi Quran yubahitse
  50,2,"Ahubwo batangajwe n’uko umuburizi yaje aturutse muri bo. Bityo abahakanyi baravuga bati \"Iki ni ikintu gitangaje"
  50,3,Ese nidupfa tugahinduka igitaka (tuzazurwa)? Uko kugaruka kuri kure (ntikwabaho)
  50,4,Rwose tuzi neza icyo ubutaka bugenda bugabanyaho (ku mibiri yabo igihe bari mu mva). Kandi dufite igitabo kirinzwe (kibitse buri kintu)
  50,5,"Nyamara bahinyuye ukuri ubwo kwabageragaho; bityo, barahuzagurika (ntibashobora gutandukanya ukuri n’ikinyoma)"
  50,6,"Ese ntibitegereza ikirere kiri hejuru yabo uko twacyubatse maze tukanagitaka, kikaba nta n’imyenge gifite"
  50,7,"N’isi twarayirambuye maze tuyishimangiza imisozi, nuko tuyimezaho buri bwoko bw’ibimera bushimishije"
  50,8,(Ibi twabikoze kugira ngo bibe) isomo n’urwibutso kuri buri mugaragu (wa Allah) wicuza
  50,9,"Twanamanuye amazi yuje imigisha (imvura) aturutse mu kirere, maze tuyameresha imirima n’impeke zisarurwa"
  50,10,N’imitende miremire ifite amaseri ahekeranye neza
  50,11,Kugira ngo bibe amafunguro. Tunayahesha ubuzima ubutaka bwapfuye. Uko ni ko izuka ry’abapfuye rizagenda
  50,12,"Mbere yabo (abahakanyi ba Maka), abantu ba Nuhu n’abari baturiye iriba rya Rasi ndetse n’abantu bo mu bwoko bwa Thamudu bahinyuye (intumwa zabo)"
  50,13,N’aba Adi na Farawo ndetse n’abavandimwe ba Lutwi (Loti)
  50,14,"N’abantu ba Ayikat (b’i Mediyani), n’abantu ba Tubba’i (abami bo mu gihugu cya Yemeni) bose bahinyuye intumwa zabo, maze mbasohorezaho isezerano ryanjye (ryo kubahana)"
  50,15,Ese twaba twarananijwe n’ukurema kwa mbere (ku buryo ukurema kwa kabiri kwatunanira)? Ahubwo bari mu gushidikanya k’ukurema gushya (izuka)
  50,16,"Mu by’ukuri, twaremye umuntu kandi tuzi ibyo umutima we umubwiriza. Kandi tumuri bugufi kurusha umutsi w’ubuzima (wo mu ijosi)"
  50,17,"(Zirikana) ko abakira babiri (abamalayika bashinzwe gukurikirana umuntu), bakira (ibyo avuga n’ibyo akora); umwe yicaye iburyo undi ibumoso"
  50,18,(Umuntu) nta jambo na rimwe yavuga ngo habure umugenzuzi umuri hafi (uryandika)
  50,19,"Kandi ibimenyetso bibimburira urupfu bizaza mu kuri nta kabuza. (Maze abwirwe ati) \"Ibyo ni byo wajyaga uzibukira"
  50,20,"Nuko impanda nivuzwa, uwo ni wo uzaba ari umunsi w’ibihano (umunsi w’izuka)"
  50,21,Buri muntu azaza ari kumwe n’(umumalayika) umushoreye ndetse n’(umumalayika) umushinja
  50,22,"(Umunyabyaha azabwirwa ati) \"Rwose wari mu burangare (utita) kuri ibi, ariko twagukuyeho igikingirizo (cyakingirizaga umutima wawe), none uyu munsi amaso yawe yatyaye (arabona byose)"
  50,23,"Umusangirangendo we (malayika umushinzwe) azavuga ati \"Dore iki (ni cyo gitabo cy’ibikorwa bye) mfite"
  50,24,"(Allah azabwira abo bamalayika bombi ati) \"Nimujugunye mu muriro wa Jahanamu buri muhakanyi wigometse"
  50,25,"Ubangamira ibyiza, urengera kandi ushidikanya"
  50,26,Wawundi wabangikanyije Allah n’indi mana. Nimumujugunye mu bihano bikaze
  50,27,"Mugenzi we (Shitani) azavuga ati \"Nyagasani wacu! Sinamuyobeje, ahubwo we yari mu buyobe buri kure (y’ukuri)"
  50,28,"(Allah azavuga ati) \"Mwijya impaka imbere yanjye kandi narababuriye mbere (ko hazabaho) ibihano"
  50,29,"Iwanjye ijambo ntirihindurwa, kandi sinjya mpuguza abagaragu banjye"
  50,30,"Zirikana umunsi tuzabwira umuriro wa Jahanamu tuti \"Ese wuzuye?\" Maze uvuge uti \"Ese hari inyongera (y’abandi ngo mubampe)"
  50,31,Kandi ijuru rizegerezwa abatinyamana
  50,32,"(Bazabwirwa bati) \"Iri (juru) ni ryo mwajyaga musezeranywa; (rigenewe) buri wese wicuza cyane kuri Allah, akanitwararika (ku mategeko ye)"
  50,33,"Wawundi utinya Allah Nyirimpuhwe atamubona, ndetse akaza afite umutima wicuza"
  50,34,"(Bazabwirwa bati) \"Nimuryinjiremo (Ijuru) mu mahoro. Uyu ni umunsi w’ubuzima buzahoraho"
  50,35,"Bazabonamo ibyo bifuza byose, kandi tuzabaha n’inyongera (yo kubona Allah imbona nkubone)"
  50,36,"Ese ni ibisekuru bingahe tworetse mbere yabo, byari ibinyembaraga kubarusha! Byari byarakwiriye mu bihugu byinshi bishaka ubuhungiro"
  50,37,"Mu by’ukuri, muri ibyo hari urwibutso k’ufite umutima, cyangwa uteze amatwi kandi akaba n’umuhamya (wita ku bintu)"
  50,38,"Rwose twaremye ibirere n’isi n’ibiri hagati yabyo mu minsi itandatu, kandi ntitwagize umunaniro"
  50,39,"Bityo, (yewe Muhamadi) jya wihanganira ibyo bavuga, unasingize ikuzo rya Nyagasani wawe mbere y’uko izuba rirasa na mbere y’uko rirenga"
  50,40,"Ndetse no mu ijoro ujye umusingiza, na nyuma yo kubama (nyuma y’amasengesho)"
  50,41,"Kandi uzatege amatwi umunsi uhamagara (Malayika uzavuza impanda), azahamagarira hafi"
  50,42,"Umunsi bazumva urusaku rw’impanda y’ukuri, uwo uzaba ari umunsi w’izuka"
  50,43,"Mu by’ukuri, ni twe dutanga ubuzima tukanabwisubiza, kandi iwacu ni ho garukiro"
  50,44,"Umunsi isi izabasadukiraho, bakavamo bihuta. Uko kuzaba ari ukubakoranya koroshye kuri twe"
  50,45,Tuzi neza ibyo bavuga kandi wowe (Muhamadi) ntugomba kubahatira kwemera. Ahubwo wibutse wifashishije Quran wawundi utinya ibihano byanjye. puh
  51,1,Ndahiriye ku miyaga ihuha igatatanya (ibicu)
  51,2,No ku bicu biremereye bitwara amazi (imvura)
  51,3,No ku mato agenda mu buryo bworoshye
  51,4,"No ku bamalayika bashinzwe gukwirakwiza (amafunguro, imvura n’indi migisha) ku bw’itegeko (rya Allah)"
  51,5,"Mu by’ukuri, ibyo musezeranywa (izuka n’ibindi bizaba ku munsi w’imperuka) ni impamo"
  51,6,"Kandi rwose, kuzagororerwa (cyangwa guhanwa ku bakoze ibibi) bizabaho nta kabuza"
  51,7,Ndahiriye ku kirere kirimo amayira ameze neza
  51,8,Rwose mufite imvugo zitandukanye (ku byerekeye intumwa Muhamadi ndetse n’iyi Quran)
  51,9,Uteshwa (gukurikira Quran n’intumwa Muhamadi) ni uwateshejwe (gukurikira ukuri)
  51,10,Abanyabinyoma baravumwe
  51,11,"Babandi bari mu bujiji, barangaye"
  51,12,Barabaza igihe umunsi w’ibihembo uzabera
  51,13,(Uzaba ari) umunsi bazaba bari mu muriro bahanwa
  51,14,"(Bazabwirwa bati) \"Ngaho nimusogongere ibihano byanyu; ibi ni byo mwajyaga musaba ko byihutishwa"
  51,15,"Mu by’ukuri, abatinya Allah bazaba bari mu busitani n’imigezi (mu Ijuru)"
  51,16,"Bishimisha mu byo Nyagasani wabo yabahaye. Mu by’ukuri, mbere bari abakora ibyiza"
  51,17,Bajyaga baryama gake mu ijoro (basenga Nyagasani wabo)
  51,18,No mu gicuku (wabasangaga) basaba imbabazi (Allah)
  51,19,"No mu mitungo yabo, bajyaga bagira icyo bageneramo abasabirizi n’abakene bihishira"
  51,20,No ku isi hari ibimenyetso ku bemera badashidikanya
  51,21,Ndetse no muri mwe ubwanyu (ibyo bimenyetso birimo). Ese ntimubona
  51,22,No mu kirere hari amafunguro yanyu ndetse n’ibyo musezeranywa
  51,23,"Bityo, ndahiriye ku izina rya Nyagasani w’ikirere n’isi ko (ibyo musezeranywa) ari ukuri nk’uko kuvuga kwanyu (ari ukuri)"
  51,24,Ese wamenye iby’inkuru y’abashyitsi ba Aburahamu b’abanyacyubahiro
  51,25,"Ubwo binjiraga iwe bakavuga bati \"Salamu (Amahoro nabe kuri mwe!)\" Nuko akavuga ati \"Salamu, bantu batazwi"
  51,26,"Nuko arinyabya asanga ab’iwe, azana inyama z’inyana yokeje"
  51,27,"Maze arazibegereza, (abonye batarambura amaboko ngo barye) aravuga ati \"Ese ntabwo murya"
  51,28,"Nuko arabishisha (abonye batariye). Baravuga bati \"Witinya!\" Hanyuma bamuha inkuru nziza (yo kuzabyara umwana) w’umuhungu uzaba afite ubumenyi (ku bijyanye na Allah)"
  51,29,"Nuko umugore we aza yiyamira, akubita agashyi mu buranga bwe (atangara), aravuga ati \"Umukecuru w’urubereri"
  51,30,"Baravuga bati \"Uko ni ko Nyagasani wawe yavuze. Mu by’ukuri, ni Ushishoza, Umumenyi uhebuje"
  51,31,"(Aburahamu) aravuga ati \"None ni iki kibagenza yemwe (ba malayika) mwoherejwe mwe"
  51,32,"Baravuga bati \"Rwose twoherejwe ku bantu b’inkozi z’ibibi"
  51,33,Kugira ngo tubamanurireho amabuye y’ibumba (ryo mu muriro)
  51,34,"(Ayo mabuye) yashyizweho ibimenyetso na Nyagasani wawe, akaba ari igihano ku barengera (imbago za Allah)"
  51,35,Nuko abemeramana (bari mu mudugudu w’inkozi z’ibibi) tuwubakuramo (kugira ngo ibihano bitabageraho)
  51,36,Ariko nta n’abo twasanzemo uretse urugo rumwe rw’umwemeramana (Intumwa Loti)
  51,37,Nuko (nyuma yo kuwurimbura) tuwusigamo ikimenyetso ku batinya ibihano bibabaza
  51,38,"No mu nkuru ya Musa (harimo isomo), ubwo twamwoherezaga kwa Farawo tumuhaye ibimenyetso n’ububasha bigaragara"
  51,39,"Ariko Farawo yishingikirije ububasha yari afite, atera umugongo (yanga kwemera ubutumwa yari azaniwe), aravuga ati \"Uyu ni umurozi cyangwa umusazi"
  51,40,Nuko tumufatana n’ingabo ze maze tubajugunya mu nyanja kandi agayitse (kubera ibikorwa bye by’ubuhakanyi)
  51,41,"No mu nkuru y’aba Adi (harimo isomo), ubwo twabohererezaga umuyaga ugumbahaye (usenya ntacyo usize)"
  51,42,Ntacyo wasigaga mu byo wahuraga nacyo utakigize umuyonga
  51,43,"No mu nkuru y’aba Thamudu (harimo isomo) ubwo babwirwaga bati \"Nimwishimishe by’igihe gito"
  51,44,"Ariko bigometse ku itegeko rya Nyagasani wabo, maze bakubitwa n’ikibatsi cy’umuriro w’inkuba bareba"
  51,45,Ntibashoboraga guhaguruka (ngo bahunge) cyangwa ngo bitabare
  51,46,"N’abantu ba Nuhu (ni uko twabagenje) mbere. Mu by’ukuri, bari abantu b’ibyigomeke"
  51,47,"Kandi ikirere twacyubakanye imbaraga, ndetse dufite ubushobozi bwo kucyagura"
  51,48,N’isi twarayishashe; mbega ukuntu twayishashe neza
  51,49,"No muri buri kintu twaremyemo ikigabo n’ikigore, kugira ngo mwibuke (ubushobozi bwa Allah)"
  51,50,"Bityo, nimuhungire kwa Allah. Mu by’ukuri, njye (Muhamadi) ndi umuburizi wanyu ugaragara umuturutseho"
  51,51,"Kandi ntimuzabangikanye Allah n’ikigirwamana icyo aricyo cyose. Mu by’ukuri, njye (Muhamadi) ndi umuburizi wanyu ugaragara umuturutseho"
  51,52,"Ni nk’uko, nta ntumwa n’imwe yoherejwe ku babayeho mbere yabo ngo babure kuvuga bati \"Ni umurozi cyangwa umusazi"
  51,53,"Ese (imvugo nk’izi) barazihererekanyaga? (Oya, si uko bimeze), ahubwo bose bari abantu barengera (imbibi za Allah)"
  51,54,"Bityo, (yewe Muhamadi) birengagize kandi ntuzabigayirwa (kuko wamaze gusohoza ubutumwa)"
  51,55,"Unibutse kuko mu by’ukuri, urwibutso rugirira akamaro abemeramana"
  51,56,Kandi nta kindi naremeye amajini n’abantu bitari ukugira ngo bansenge
  51,57,"Simbakeneyeho amafunguro, ndetse nta n’ubwo mbakeneyeho ko bangaburira"
  51,58,"Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni we Utanga amafunguro, Nyirimbaraga, Ukomeye bihebuje"
  51,59,"Kandi rwose abakora ibibi bazagira umugabane (w’ibihano) umeze nk’umugabane bagenzi babo bababanjirije babonye; bityo, binsaba kwihutisha (kubahana)"
  51,60,Ibihano bikomeye bizaba kuri babandi bahakanye umunsi basezeranyijwe
  52,1,Ndahiriye ku (Musozi wa) Twuri
  52,2,No ku gitabo cyanditse (Quran)
  52,3,(Cyanditswe) ku mpapuro zikozwe mu ruhu (rusukuye) ruramburwa (kugira ngo gisomwe)
  52,4,No ku nzu (yo mu ijuru) ihora isurwa (n’abamalayika)
  52,5,No ku gisenge gihanitse (ikirere)
  52,6,No ku nyanja zuzuye (amazi)
  52,7,"Mu by’ukuri, ibihano bya Nyagasani wawe bizabaho nta kabuza"
  52,8,Ntagishobora kuzabikumira
  52,9,Umunsi ikirere kizatigita umutingito (ukomeye)
  52,10,N’imisozi ikagenda (nk’uko ibicu bigenda)
  52,11,Kuri uwo munsi ibihano bikomeye bizaba ku bahinyuye (ukuri)
  52,12,"Babandi bahugira mu kwishimisha mu biganiro byuzuye ibinyoma, bidafite akamaro"
  52,13,Umunsi bazasunikirwa mu muriro wa Jahanamu ku ngufu
  52,14,"(Bazabwirwa bati) \"Uyu ni wo muriro mwajyaga muhinyura"
  52,15,Ese ibi (bihano mubona) ni uburozi cyangwa ntimubona (ko mugiye kwinjizwa mu muriro)
  52,16,"Ngaho nimuwinjiremo, kandi mwabyihanganira cyangwa mutabyi- hanganira, byose ni kimwe. Mu by’ukuri, (ibyo muri kubona) ni ibihembo by’ibyo mwakoraga"
  52,17,"Mu by’ukuri, abatinya Allah bazaba bari mu busitani n’inema (bihoraho)"
  52,18,"Binezeza mu byo Nyagasani wabo yabahaye, ndetse no kuba Nyagasani wabo yabarinze ibihano by’umuriro"
  52,19,"(Bazabwirwa bati) \"Nimurye munanywe kandi mugubwe neza kubera ibyo mwakoze"
  52,20,"Bazaba begamye ku bitanda bitondetse ku murongo.Tuzanabashyingira Huur ul- a’in (abagore bo mu Ijuru b’igikundiro, b’amaso manini)"
  52,21,"Naho babandi bemeye maze ababakomokaho bakabakurikira mu kwemera, tuzabahuza n’ababakomotseho (mu ijuru), kandi ntacyo tuzigera tugabanya mu bikorwa byabo. Buri muntu azabazwa ibyo yakoze"
  52,22,Tuzabaha imbuto n’inyama (by’amoko yose) bazajya bifuza
  52,23,"Bazajya bahererekanyamo ibirahure (by’ikinyobwa cya divayi), kitazabatera (gusinda ngo bavuge) amagambo adafite akamaro cyangwa ngo kibatere gukora ibyaha"
  52,24,"Bazaba bazengurukwamo n’abahungu b’abahereza babo, bameze nk’inigi zishashagirana (Lu’ulu’u) zikiri mu bubiko bwazo"
  52,25,"Bamwe muri bo bazajya bahindukira (barebe) bagenzi babo, babazanya"
  52,26,"Bavuga bati \"Mbere (ku isi) twabaga turi mu miryango yacu dufite ubwoba n’impungenge (z’ibihano bya Allah)"
  52,27,"None Allah yatugororeye, aturinda ibihano by’umuriro utwika"
  52,28,"Mu by’ukuri, mbere twajyaga tumusenga (wenyine). Rwose ni we Mugiraneza, Nyirimbabazi"
  52,29,"Bityo, (yewe Muhamadi) komeza wibutse! Mu by’ukuri, ku bw’ingabire za Nyagasani wawe (zo kuba warahawe ubutumwa), ntabwo uri umupfumu cyangwa umusazi (nk’uko babivuga)"
  52,30,"Cyangwa (abahakanyi) baravuga bati \"(Muhamadi) ni umusizi, reka tumutege iminsi (azapfe nk’uko abandi basizi bapfuye)"
  52,31,"Babwire uti \"Ngaho nimutegereze, mu by’ukuri, ndi kumwe namwe mu bategereje"
  52,32,Cyangwa imitekerereze yabo ni yo ibategeka (kuvuga) ibyo? Cyangwa ahubwo ni abantu barengera (imbibi za Allah)
  52,33,"Cyangwa bavuga ko (Qur’an) yayihimbiye? (Oya), ahubwo ntibemera"
  52,34,"Ngaho nibazane inkuru zimeze nk’iziyivugwamo (Quran), niba koko ari abanyakuri"
  52,35,"Ese bibwira ko baremwe ntawe ubaremye, cyangwa ni bo biremye"
  52,36,Cyangwa bibwira ko baremye ibirere n’isi? Ahubwo ntibizera
  52,37,"Cyangwa bibwira ko bafite ibigega bya Nyagasani wawe? Cyangwa ni bo bagenga (b’isi, bakora ibyo bashatse)"
  52,38,Cyangwa bibwira ko bafite urwego buririraho bajya (mu ijuru) ngo bumvirize ibivugirwayo? Ngaho umwumviriza wabo nazane ibimenyetso simusiga
  52,39,"Cyangwa bibwira ko (Allah) afite abakobwa gusa, mwe mukagira abahungu"
  52,40,"Cyangwa bibwira ko (wowe Muhamadi) ubasaba igihembo, none bakaba baremererwa n’ubwishyu"
  52,41,"Cyangwa bibwira ko bazi ibyihishe, bakaba bandika (ibyo bishakiye, badakeneye ibyo ubabwira)"
  52,42,Cyangwa baba bakugambanira (yewe Muhamadi)? Nyamara abahakanye ni bo bazahanirwa ubugambanyi bwabo
  52,43,Cyangwa bafite indi mana itari Allah? Ubutagatifu ni ubwa Allah kandi ntaho ahuriye n’ibyo bamubangikanya (nabyo)
  52,44,"N’iyo baza kubona igice cy’ikirere kigwa hasi, bari kuvuga bati \"Ni igicu gicucitse"
  52,45,"Bareke kugeza ubwo bazahura n’umunsi wabo, bazagwa igihumure (kubera ibihano)"
  52,46,"Umunsi imigambi mibisha yabo itazagira icyo ibamarira, ndetse nta n’ubwo bazatabarwa"
  52,47,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, abakora ibibi bazahanishwa ibindi bihano (ku isi) mbere y’ibyo (ku munsi w’imperuka); ariko abenshi muri bo ntibabizi"
  52,48,"Bityo (yewe Muhamadi), ihanganire itegeko rya Nyagasani wawe, kuko mu by’ukuri tuguhozaho ijisho. Ndetse unasingize ikuzo rya Nyagasani wawe igihe ubyutse (ugiye gusenga)"
  52,49,"No mu ijoro ujye umusingiza, ndetse n’igihe urumuri rw’inyenyeri ruba rugenda rukendera"
  53,1,Ndahiriye ku nyenyeri igihe ziba zirenga
  53,2,(Ko uyu) mugenzi wanyu (Intumwa Muhamadi) atigeze ayoba ndetse ko atigeze anateshuka (ku nzira y’ukuri)
  53,3,Nta n’ubwo avuga ashingiye ku marangamutima ye
  53,4,Ahubwo (ibyo avuga) ni ibyo ahishurirwa (na Allah)
  53,5,Yigishijwe (iyi Quran) n’umunyembaraga cyane (Malayika Jibrilu)
  53,6,"Ufite ububasha kandi utagira inenge, wagaragariye (Intumwa Muhamadi) mu ishusho ye y’ukuri"
  53,7,Ubwo (Malayika Jibrilu) yari mu kirere cyo hejuru
  53,8,"Nuko yegera (Intumwa Muhamadi), maze akomeza kuyegera"
  53,9,(Yamwegereye) mu ntera ingana n’iri hagati y’amahembe abiri y’umuheto cyangwa bugufi kurushaho
  53,10,"Nuko (Allah) ahishurira umugaragu we (Muhamadi, abinyujije kuri Malayika Jibrilu) ibyo yagombaga kumuhishurira byose"
  53,11,Umutima we (Muhamadi) ntiwigeze ubeshya ibyo wabonye
  53,12,Nonese muramugisha impaka ku byo yabonye (ubwo yazamukaga mu ijuru rya karindwi)
  53,13,Kandi rwose (Muhamadi) yongeye kumubona (Malayika Jibrilu) ubwo yamanukaga ku yindi nshuro
  53,14,Ubwo yari kuri Sidrat-il-Muntaha (Igiti cya nyuma)
  53,15,Ni naho hari ubuturo bw’ijuru (ry’abameramana)
  53,16,Ubwo icyo giti (Sidrat) cyatwikirwaga n’ibyagitwikiriye (urumuri rutangaje)
  53,17,"Indoro (y’Intumwa y’Imana) ntiyigeze itana (ngo irebe iburyo cyangwa ibumoso), cyangwa ngo irenge (imbibi yari yashyiriweho)"
  53,18,"Mu by’ukuri, (Intumwa Muhamadi) yabonye bimwe mu bitangaza bihambaye bya Nyagasani wayo"
  53,19,Ese ntimutekereza (ku bigirwamana musenga); Laata na Uza
  53,20,"Ndetse na Manaata, ikindi (kigirwamana) cya gatatu"
  53,21,Ese mwibwira ko mufite abana b’abahungu naho we (Allah) akagira ab’abakobwa
  53,22,Iryo ryaba ari igabana ribogamye
  53,23,"Ibyo (bigirwamana) nta kindi biri cyo usibye kuba ari amazina masa mwabihimbiye, mwe n’abakurambere banyu, Allah atigeze abahera uburenganzira. Rwose nta kindi bakurikira kitari ugukekeranya ndetse n’ibyo imitima (yabo) irarikira. Kandi mu by’ukuri, bagezweho n’umuyoboro uturutse kwa Nyagasani wabo"
  53,24,Ese (mutekereza ko) umuntu yabona ibyo yifuza byose
  53,25,Allah ni we Mugenga w’ubuzima bw’imperuka n’ubw’isi
  53,26,"Nonese ni bangahe mu bamalayika bari mu birere, ubuvugizi bwabo butazigera bugira icyo bumara Allah atabanje kubihera uburenganzira uwo ashatse kandi yishimira"
  53,27,"Mu by’ukuri, abatemera imperuka bita abamalayika amazina y’igitsina gore"
  53,28,"Kandi ibyo nta bumenyi babifitiye. Ndetse nta kindi bakurikira kitari ugukekeranya, kandi rwose ugukeka ntacyo byakongera ku kuri"
  53,29,"Bityo, irengagize wawundi wateye umugongo urwibutso rwacu nta kindi ashaka uretse ubuzima bw’isi"
  53,30,"(Ibyo bavuga) ni ho ubumenyi bwabo bugarukira. Mu by’ukuri, Nyagasani wawe ni we uzi neza uwayobye inzira ye, kandi ni na we uzi neza abayobotse"
  53,31,"Kandi ibiri mu birere n’ibiri mu isi ni ibya Allah, (yashyizeho ayo mategeko) kugira ngo ahane inkozi z’ibibi kubera ibyo zakoze, ndetse anahembe ibyiza (ijuru) abakora ibyiza"
  53,32,"Babandi birinda ibyaha bikomeye n’ibikozasoni uretse kuba bagwa mu byaha byoroshye; mu by’ukuri, imbabazi za Nyagasani wawe ziragutse. Ni we ubazi neza kuva yabarema abakuye mu gitaka, n’igihe mwari muri nyababyeyi za ba nyoko. Bityo, ntimukigire abere kuko ari we uzi neza umutinya"
  53,33,Ese (yewe Muhamadi) wabonye wawundi wateye umugongo (akanga kumvira Allah)
  53,34,"Akanatanga bike (mu byo twamuhaye), nyuma akabireka burundu"
  53,35,Ese yaba afite ubumenyi bw’ibitagaragara akaba abona (ko ibyo intumwa Muhamadi yahishuriwe atari ukuri)
  53,36,Cyangwa ntiyabwiwe ibiri mu bitabo bya Musa
  53,37,Ndetse n’ibiri mu bya Ibrahimu wasohoje ubutumwa
  53,38,Ko ntawe uzikorera umutwaro w’undi
  53,39,Kandi ko nta cyo umuntu azabona (ku munsi w’imperuka) usibye ibyo yakoze
  53,40,Kandi ko ibikorwa bye bizagaragara (ku munsi w’imperuka)
  53,41,Maze akazabihemberwa ibihembo byuzuye
  53,42,Kandi ko iherezo (rya buri kintu) ari kwa Nyagasani wawe
  53,43,Kandi ko ari we (Allah) utera guseka (kwishima) no kurira (kubabara)
  53,44,No kuba ari we wisubiza ubuzima ndetse akanabutanga
  53,45,"No kuba ari we waremye ibitsina byombi, gabo na gore"
  53,46,Mu ntanga igihe zisohowe
  53,47,No kuba ari we uzarema bundi bushya (azura abapfuye)
  53,48,No kuba ari we utanga ubukungu akanakungahaza
  53,49,No kuba ari we Nyagasani wa Shi’ira (inyenyeri Abarabu b’ababangikanyamana bajyaga basenga)
  53,50,No kuba ari we woretse aba Adi bo hambere
  53,51,N’aba Thamudu ntiyagize uwo asigaza
  53,52,"Na mbere yabo, (yoretse) abantu ba Nuhu. Mu by’ukuri, bari inkozi z’ibibi bakaba n’abarengera (amategeko ya Allah) bikabije"
  53,53,"Ndetse n’imidugudu (ya Sodoma) yabirinduwe, ni we wayibirinduye (ibyari hasi bijya hejuru n’ibyari hejuru bijya hasi)"
  53,54,Nuko (iyo midugudu) itwikirwa n’ibyayitwikiriye (ibihano bigizwe n’amabuye)
  53,55,Nonese (yewe muntu) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wawe ushidikanyaho (ko atari ize)
  53,56,Uyu (Muhamadi) ni umwe mu (ruhererekane rw’) ababurizi bo hambere
  53,57,Umunsi w’imperuka uregereje
  53,58,Nta kindi cyawukumira usibye Allah (ushobora kuwihutisha cyangwa akawutinza)
  53,59,Nonese mutangajwe n’aya magambo (ya Quran)
  53,60,Mukaba museka (muyihakana) aho kurira
  53,61,Muhugiye mu bibarangaza
  53,62,"Bityo, nimwubamire Allah munamugaragire (wenyine)"
  54,1,Igihe cy’imperuka kiregereje ndetse n’ukwezi kwarasadutse
  54,2,"N’iyo (abahakanyi) babonye igitangaza, batera umugongo bakavuga bati \"Ubu ni uburozi bukomeje"
  54,3,"Barahakanye banakurikira irari ryabo, kandi buri kintu kizagira iherezo"
  54,4,Kandi rwose bagezweho n’inkuru zibabuza (gukora ibibi)
  54,5,"(Izo nkuru ziri muri Quran) zuje ubushishozi buhebuje, ariko uko kubaburira ntacyo kwabamariye"
  54,6,"Bityo (yewe Muhamadi), birengagize kandi (unabibutse) umunsi umuhamagazi azahamagarira kugana ku kintu giteye ubwoba (gucirwa urubanza ku munsi w’imperuka)"
  54,7,"Bazaba bubitse amaso (kubera ikimwaro), basohoka mu mva bameze nk’inzige zinyanyagiye"
  54,8,"Bihuta bagana uhamagara, abahakanyi bazavuga bati \"Uyu ni umunsi ugoye"
  54,9,"Na mbere yabo, abantu ba Nuhu bahinyuye umugaragu wacu, maze baravuga bati \"Ni umusazi\", ndetse aranamaganwa"
  54,10,"Nuko asaba Nyagasani we (agira ati) \"Rwose njye naneshejwe, bityo ntabara"
  54,11,"Nuko dufungura amarembo y’ikirere, hamanuka amazi yisuka ari menshi"
  54,12,"Nuko isi tuyikuramo amasoko, maze amazi (yo mu nsi no hejuru) arahura ku bw’itegeko ryagenwe"
  54,13,Maze (Nuhu) tumutwara mu (kintu) gikozwe mu mbaho n’imisumari (inkuge)
  54,14,Cyagendaga (hejuru y’amazi) tugihanze ijisho; (ibyo) biba igihembo cy’uwahakanyijwe
  54,15,Rwose (iyi nkuru ya Nuhu) twarayiretse ngo ibe ikimenyetso (n’isomo ku bazaza nyuma ye). Ese hari uwibuka (ngo bimugirire akamaro)
  54,16,Mbega uko ibihano byanjye no kuburira kwanjye byari bimeze
  54,17,Kandi rwose tworoheje Qur’an kugira ngo ibe urwibutso. Ese hari uwibuka (ngo bimugirire akamaro)
  54,18,Aba Adi bahinyuye (Intumwa yabo Hudi); mbega uko ibihano byanjye no kuburira kwanjye byari bimeze
  54,19,"Mu by’ukuri, twaboherereje inkubi y’umuyaga uvuza ubuhuha ku munsi w’amakuba akomeye"
  54,20,Uterura abantu bakamera nk’ingiga z’ibiti by’imitende byaranduwe
  54,21,Mbega uko ibihano byanjye no kuburira kwanjye byari bimeze
  54,22,Kandi rwose tworoheje Qur’an kugira ngo ibe urwibutso. Ese hari uwibuka (ngo bimugirire akamaro)
  54,23,Aba Thamudi bahinyuye kuburira (kwacu)
  54,24,"Nuko baravuga bati \"Ese ni gute twafata umuntu umwe unadukomokamo ngo tube ari we dukurikira? Rwose ubwo twaba turi mu buyobe n’ubusazi"
  54,25,Ese ubu koko urwibutso ni we wenyine muri twe rwahawe? Ahubwo we ni umubeshyi akaba n’umwibone
  54,26,Bidatinze bazamenya umubeshyi w’umwibone uwo ari we
  54,27,Twaboherereje ingamiya kugira ngo tubagerageze; bityo bagenzure unabihanganire
  54,28,Unababwire ko amazi bagomba kuyasangira nayo (ingamiya); buri wese azajya agira umunsi we wo kuyanywaho
  54,29,Ariko bahamagaye mugenzi wabo (afata icyuma) arayica
  54,30,Mbega uko ibihano byanjye no kuburira kwanjye byari bimeze
  54,31,"Mu by’ukuri, twaboherereje urusaku rumwe gusa, maze bamera nk’ibyatsi byumye byaribaswe"
  54,32,Kandi rwose tworoheje Qur’an kugira ngo ibe urwibutso. Ese hari uwibuka (ngo bimugirire akamaro)
  54,33,Abantu ba Lutwi bahinyuye kuburira (kwacu)
  54,34,"Twaboherereje inkubi y’umuyaga uvanze n’amabuye (ubarimbura bose), usibye gusa umuryango wa Lutwi twarokoye mu rukerera"
  54,35,(Ibyo twabikoze) ku bw’ingabire ziduturutseho. Uko ni ko duhemba ushimira
  54,36,"Nyamara (Lutwi) yari yarababuriye ko bazahura n’ibihano byacu, nuko bashidikanya ku kubaburira (kwacu)"
  54,37,"Baranamwinginze (ngo abahe) abashyitsi be (kugira ngo babakorere ubutinganyi). Nuko tubahuma amaso (tuvuga tuti) \"Ngaho nimusogongere ibihano byanjye no kuburira (kwanjye)"
  54,38,Kandi rwose twabazindukirije mu bihano bikomeza (kuzageza ku munsi w’imperuka)
  54,39,Ngaho nimusogongere ibihano byanjye no kuburira (kwanjye)
  54,40,Kandi rwose tworoheje Qur’an kugira ngo ibe urwibutso. Ese hari uwibuka (ngo bimugirire akamaro)
  54,41,Kandi rwose kuburira (kwanjye) kwageze ku bantu ba Farawo
  54,42,"Bahinyuye ibitangaza byacu byose, nuko turabafata tubahanisha ibihano by’Umunyembaraga uhebuje, Ushobora byose"
  54,43,"Ese abahakanyi banyu (b’i Maka) ni bo beza kurusha abo (abantu ba Adi, aba Thamudi, aba Nuhu n’aba Farawo, boretswe)? Cyangwa mufite ubudahangarwa bwanditse mu bitabo (bwo kutazahanwa)"
  54,44,"Cyangwa (abo bahakanyi) baravuga bati \"Twe turi benshi bashyize hamwe, bashoboye kwitabara"
  54,45,Nyamara abo bishyize hamwe bazatsindwa banayabangire ingata
  54,46,"Ahubwo umunsi w’imperuka ni cyo gihe basezeranyijwe (cyo kuzahanirwaho), ndetse imperuka izaba iteye ubwoba cyane kandi irura"
  54,47,"Mu by’ ukuri, inkozi z’ibibi ziri mu buyobe (hano ku isi) kandi zizahanishwa umuriro utwika"
  54,48,"Umunsi uburanga bwabo buzakururirwa mu muriro (bazabwirwa bati) \"Ngaho nimusogongere igihano cy’umuriro"
  54,49,"Mu by’ukuri, buri kintu twakiremeye igeno ryacyo"
  54,50,Kandi itegeko ryacu ni ijambo rimwe; (ryihuta) nko guhumbya no guhumbura
  54,51,Kandi rwose tworetse abantu bameze nkamwe (mu buhakanyi). Ese hari uwibuka (ngo bimugirire akamaro)
  54,52,Kandi buri kintu cyose bakoze cyanditswe mu bitabo (by’ibikorwa byabo)
  54,53,"Na buri kintu, cyaba gito cyangwa kinini, kiranditse"
  54,54,"Mu by’ukuri, abatinya Allah bazaba bari mu busitani n’imigezi (Ijuru)"
  54,55,"Mu byicaro by’ukuri, hafi y’Umwami ushobora byose"
  55,1,Ni (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe
  55,2,Yigishije (umuntu) Qur’an
  55,3,Yaremye umuntu
  55,4,Amwigisha ububonezamvugo
  55,5,Izuba n’ukwezi bigendera ku mubare (no kuri gahunda ya Allah)
  55,6,"N’ibimera birandaranda ndetse n’ibiti, byose birubama (bikicisha bugufi imbere ya Allah)"
  55,7,N’ikirere yagishyize hejuru cyane (y’isi) ndetse ashyiraho n’ibipimo (bya buri kintu)
  55,8,Kugira ngo mutarengera ibipimo (byagenwe)
  55,9,"Bityo, mujye mupima ibintu byose mukoresheje ubutabera, kandi ntimukagabanye ibipimo"
  55,10,N’isi (Allah) yayishyiriyeho ibiremwa
  55,11,Iriho imbuto n’imitende ifite imbuto zitwikiriwe n’ibishishwa
  55,12,Ndetse n’impeke (z’ubwoko bunyuranye); iz’inyamisogwe n’izihumura
  55,13,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,14,(Allah) yaremye umuntu (Adamu) mu itaka ryumye ukomangaho rikirangira nk’ibikoresho bibumbye mu ibumba
  55,15,Anarema amajini mu birimi by’umuriro
  55,16,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,17,(Ni we) Nyagasani w’Uburasirazuba bubiri akaba na Nyagasani w’Uburengerazuba bubiri
  55,18,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,19,Yahuje inyanja ebyiri (ifite amazi y’urubogobogo n’indi y’urwunyunyu)
  55,20,"Hagati yazo ahashyira urubibi (ruzitandukanya), zikinjiranamo ariko ntizivange"
  55,21,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,22,Muri zo havamo amasaro arabagirana (Lu-ulu-u) na Marijani
  55,23,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,24,"Kandi (Allah ni we) ufite ububasha ku mato manini agendera mu nyanja, ameze nk’imisozi"
  55,25,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,26,Ikiyiriho cyose (isi) kizapfa
  55,27,"Maze hasigare gusa uburanga butagatifu bwa Nyagasani wawe, Nyir’ikuzo n’icyubahiro"
  55,28,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,29,"Buri icyaremwe cyose kiri mu birere no ku isi kimusaba (ibyo cyifuza). Naho we buri munsi aba agena gahunda (z’ibiremwa; zirimo nko kuzamura mu cyubahiro bamwe no kumanura mu cyubahiro abandi, guha ubuzima bamwe no kubwambura abandi, n’ibindi)"
  55,30,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,31,"Yemwe matsinda abiri (y’abantu n’amajini), tuzabacira imanza (ku munsi w’imperuka)"
  55,32,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,33,"Yemwe majini na mwe bantu! Niba mufite ubushobozi bwo kugenda mukarenga imbago z’ibirere n’isi (muhunga ibihano bya Allah), muzagende. Ariko ntimushobora kuzirenga keretse ku bw’itegeko (rya Allah)"
  55,34,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,35,"Muzohererezwa ikibatsi cy’umuriro n’umuringa (washongeshejwe), kandi ntimuzigera mutabarwa"
  55,36,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,37,"(Mwibuke) ubwo ikirere kizasatagurika, maze kigahinduka nk’ururabo rutukura rumeze nk’amavuta yabize"
  55,38,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,39,"Kuri uwo munsi, nta muntu cyangwa ijini bizagira icyo bibazwa ku bijyanye n’ibyaha byabyo (kuko bizaba bifite ibimenyetso bibiranga)"
  55,40,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,41,"Inkozi z’ibibi zizamenyerwa ku bimenyetso byazo, kandi zizaterurwa mu ruhanga n’ibirenge byazo"
  55,42,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,43,Uyu ni umuriro wa Jahanamu inkozi z’ibibi zajyaga zihinyura
  55,44,"Bazawuzengurukamo hagati, ndetse no hagati y’amazi yatuye cyane"
  55,45,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,46,"Ariko wawundi utinya kuzahagarara imbere ya Nyagasani we, azaba afite ubusitani bubiri (mu Ijuru)"
  55,47,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,48,(Ubwo busitani buzaba burimo ibiti) bifite amashami acucitse kandi atoshye
  55,49,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,50,"Muri ubwo (busitani) bwombi, hazaba harimo amasoko abiri atemba"
  55,51,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,52,"Muri ubwo (busitani) bwombi, hazaba harimo ubwoko bubiri bwa buri rubuto"
  55,53,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,54,"Bazaba begamye ku bitanda bishasheho ihariri iremereye, kandi imbuto zo muri ubwo busitani zizaba zibari hafi"
  55,55,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,56,"(Ubwo busitani bwombi) buzaba burimo abagore biyubashye, batigeze bagira umuntu cyangwa ijini bibakoraho kuva na mbere"
  55,57,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,58,(Bazaba bafite ubwiza) nk’ubw’amabuye y’agaciro ya Yaquut134 na Marjani
  55,59,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,60,Ese hari igihembo cy’ibyiza kitari ibyiza
  55,61,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,62,"Kandi uretse n’ubwo (busitani) bubiri, hari ubundi busitani bubiri"
  55,63,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,64,(Bufite) ibara ry’icyatsi kijimye
  55,65,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,66,"Muri ubwo (busitani) bwombi, (naho) hazaba harimo amasoko abiri avubura amazi"
  55,67,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,68,"Muri ubwo (busitani) bwombi, hazaba harimo imbuto, imitende n’imikomamanga"
  55,69,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,70,Hazaba harimo abagore beza b’imico myiza
  55,71,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,72,Hazaba harimo abagore biyubashye bahora mu mahema
  55,73,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,74,"Mbere y’abo (bagabo bazaba bahawe), nta muntu cyangwa ijini byigeze bibakoraho"
  55,75,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,76,"(Abagabo babo) bazajya begama ku misego y’icyatsi, n’amagodora atatse neza"
  55,77,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,78,"Izina rya Nyagasani wawe, Nyir’ikuzo n’icyubahiro, ryuje ubutungane n’imigisha"
  56,1,Ubwo imperuka izaba igeze
  56,2,Ntawe uzashobora guhinyura ukuza kwayo
  56,3,"Izacisha bugufi (abazajya mu muriro), inashyire hejuru (abazajya mu ijuru)"
  56,4,Ubwo isi izatigiswa n’umutingito ukomeye
  56,5,N’imisozi igahindurwa ubuvungukira
  56,6,Maze ikaba umukungugu unyanyagiye
  56,7,(Icyo gihe) muzaba muri mu byiciro bitatu
  56,8,Hari ab’iburyo135; abo bantu b’iburyo ni bantu ki
  56,9,N’ab’ibumoso; abo bantu b’ibumoso ni bantu ki
  56,10,"N’abambere (ni abakurikije amategeko ya Allah bakiri ku isi), abo bazaba ari bo ba mbere (mu kwinjira mu Ijuru)"
  56,11,Abo ni bo bazaba bari hafi (ya Allah)
  56,12,Mu ijuru ryuje ingabire
  56,13,Abenshi (muri bo) bazaba ari itsinda rinini ryo mu bantu bo hambere (mbere y’Intumwa Muhamadi)
  56,14,Na bake mu bantu bo hanyuma (bakurikiye intumwa Muhamadi)
  56,15,Bazaba bari ku bitanda bitatswe na zahabu
  56,16,"Babyegamyeho, berekeranye"
  56,17,Bazaba bazengurukwamo n’abana b’abahungu bahoraho (badasaza cyangwa ngo bapfe)
  56,18,"(Bazaba babazengurutsamo) ibikombe, amabirika n’ibirahuri birimo ibinyobwa byiza"
  56,19,Ntibizabatera kurwara umutwe ndetse nta n’ubwo bizabasindisha
  56,20,(Bazaba banazengurutswamo) imbuto bazihitiramo
  56,21,Ndetse n’inyama z’inyoni bazifuza
  56,22,Kandi (hazaba hari) ba Huur ul- a’in (abagore bo mu Ijuru b’igikundiro n’amaso manini)
  56,23,Bameze nk’inigi zishashagirana (Lu’ulu’u) zikiri mu bubiko bwazo
  56,24,Bizaba ari ibihembo by’ibyo bakoraga
  56,25,Muri ryo (Ijuru) nta magambo adafite akamaro cyangwa se ayatuma bakora ibyaha bazumvamo
  56,26,"Uretse (imvugo yo kuramukanya, igira iti) \"Salamu, Salamu (amahoro, amahoro)"
  56,27,Naho ab’iburyo; ni bantu ki (mbega ibihembo by’abantu b’iburyo)
  56,28,Bazaba (mu Ijuru ririmo) ibiti bya Sidiri bidafite amahwa
  56,29,N’ibitoki by’amaseri agerekeranye
  56,30,No mu gicucu kirambuye (kandi gihoraho)
  56,31,N’amazi ahora atemba
  56,32,Ndetse n’imbuto nyinshi
  56,33,"Ntizizahundura (bitewe n’ihinduka ry’ibihe cyangwa ngo zigire igihe cyo kwera), kandi ntizizaba zibujijwe (kuri bo)"
  56,34,Bazaba banafite ibitanda biri hejuru
  56,35,"Mu by’ukuri, (abagore bo ku isi bazajya mu ijuru) tuzabarema bundi bushya"
  56,36,Maze tubagire amasugi
  56,37,"Bakunda (abagabo babo gusa), kandi ari urungano"
  56,38,(Ibi byose) byateganyirijwe abantu b’iburyo
  56,39,Abenshi (muri bo) bazaba ari itsinda rinini ryo mu bantu bo hambere (mbere y’Intumwa Muhamadi)
  56,40,Na benshi mu bantu bo hanyuma (bakurikiye Intumwa Muhamadi)
  56,41,Naho abantu b’ibumoso; ni bantu ki (mbega ibihano by’abantu b’ibumoso)
  56,42,Bazaba bari mu muyaga utwika ndetse n’amazi yatuye
  56,43,No mu gicucu cy’umwotsi w’umukara
  56,44,(Icyo gicucu) nta mbeho kizatanga ndetse nta n’icyiza kizagiturukaho
  56,45,"Mu by’ukuri, mbere bari babayeho mu buzima bwo kwinezeza (bigomeka kuri Allah)"
  56,46,Kandi bajyaga batsimbarara ku byaha bihambaye (ntibagire umugambi wo kubyicuza)
  56,47,"Kandi bajyaga bavuga bati \" Ese nidupfa tugahinduka igitaka n’amagufa (akabora), tuzazurwa koko"
  56,48,N’abakurambere bacu (bazazurwa) se
  56,49,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"(Yego) rwose, abo hambere n’abo hanyuma"
  56,50,"Bazakoranywa ku munsi uzwi, wagenwe (umunsi w’imperuka)"
  56,51,Nuko mwe abayobye mukanahinyura ukuri
  56,52,Rwose muzarya ku giti cya Zaqumu
  56,53,Maze mucyuzuze inda
  56,54,Mukirenzeho amazi yatuye
  56,55,Muzayanywa nk’ingamiya zinywa zidashira inyota
  56,56,Iryo ni ryo zimano ryabo ku munsi w’ibihembo
  56,57,Ni twe twabaremye. Nonese kuki mutemera (izuka)
  56,58,Ese mutekereza iki ku matembabuzi (amasohora) musohora
  56,59,Ese ni mwe muyarema cyangwa ni twe Muremyi
  56,60,Ni twe twabageneye urupfu kandi ntitwananirwa
  56,61,"Kubasimbuza abameze nka mwe, maze tukabaremamo (amashusho y’) ibindi mutazi"
  56,62,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, mwamenye ukuremwa (kwanyu) kwa mbere. Nonese kuki mutibuka"
  56,63,Ese ntimubona ibyo muhinga
  56,64,"Ese ni mwe mubiha kumera no gukura, cyangwa ni twe tubikora"
  56,65,"Tubishatse twabigira ubushingwe, maze mugakomeza kumirwa"
  56,66,"(Muvuga muti) \"Rwose twaruhiye ubusa"
  56,67,Ahubwo twimwe (ibintu byose)
  56,68,Ese ntimubona amazi munywa
  56,69,Ese ni mwe muyamanura mu bicu cyangwa ni twe tuyamanura
  56,70,"Iyo tuza kubishaka, twari kuyagira urwunyunyu (ntanyobwe). Nonese kuki mudashimira (Allah)"
  56,71,Ese ntimubona umuriro mucana
  56,72,Ese ni mwe mwaremye igiti cyawo (muwukomoramo) cyangwa ni twe Muremyi
  56,73,"Ni twe twawugize urwibutso (rw’umuriro wa Jahanamu), ndetse n’ingirakamaro ku bagenzi (n’abandi bose bawukeneye)"
  56,74,"Ngaho singiza izina rya Nyagasani wawe, Uhambaye"
  56,75,Ndahiriye ahantu inyenyeri (zirengera bwenda gucya)
  56,76,Kandi rwose iyo ni indahiro ihambaye iyo muza kumenya
  56,77,"Ko mu by’ukuri, (iyi) ari Quran Ntagatifu"
  56,78,Iri mu gitabo kirinzwe neza (mu Ijuru)
  56,79,Kitajya kigira ugikoraho uretse abejejwe (abamalayika)
  56,80,Cyahishuwe giturutse kwa Nyagasani w’ibiremwa
  56,81,Ese iyi nkuru (Qur’an) ni yo muhinyura
  56,82,"Aho (gushimira Allah) ku bw’amafunguro abaha, (mumwitura) kumuhakana"
  56,83,Nonese (kuki ntacyo mukora) igihe roho (y’umuntu ugiye gupfa) igeze mu muhogo
  56,84,Icyo gihe muba murebera
  56,85,"Kandi tuba turi hafi ye kubarusha, ariko mwe ntimubibona"
  56,86,Nonese niba mwibwira ko ntacyo muzabazwa (mukaba mwibwira ko muri abanyembaraga)
  56,87,Ngaho nimuyigarure (iyo roho mu mubiri wayo) niba koko muri abanyakuri
  56,88,Niba (uwo muntu ugiye gupfa) ari mu ba hafi (ya Allah)
  56,89,"(Ateganyirijwe) umunezero n’impumuro y’ibyishimo, ndetse n’ubusitani bwuje ingabire (Ijuru)"
  56,90,Naho (uwo muntu ugiye gupfa) naba ari mu bantu b’iburyo
  56,91,"(Azabwirwa ati) \"Amahoro ni abe kuri wowe kuko uri mu bantu b’iburyo"
  56,92,"Ariko (uwo muntu ugiye gupfa) naba ari mu bahinyura (izuka), akaba yaranayobye"
  56,93,Izimano rye rizaba ari amazi yatuye
  56,94,No kuzatwikirwa mu muriro
  56,95,"Mu by’ukuri, uku ni ko kuri kudashidikanywaho"
  56,96,"Bityo, tagatifuza izina rya Nyagasani wawe, Uhambaye"
  57,1,"Ibiri mu birere n’ibiri ku isi bisingiza Allah, kandi ni we Nyirimbaraga zihebuje, Ushishoza"
  57,2,Ubwami bw’ibirere n’ubw’isi ni ubwe. Ni we utanga ubuzima n’urupfu. Kandi ni we ufite ubushobozi bwa buri kintu
  57,3,"Ni we Ntangiriro akaba n’Iherezo, Ugaragara akaba n’Utagaragara. Kandi ni we Mumenyi uhebuje wa buri kintu"
  57,4,"Ni we waremye ibirere n’isi mu minsi itandatu, hanyuma aganza ku ntebe y’icyubahiro (Ar’shi). Azi ibyinjira mu butaka n’ibibusohokamo, ibimanuka mu kirere ndetse n’ibikizamukamo. Kandi aba ari kumwe na mwe aho muri hose. Kandi Allah ni Ubona bihebuje ibyo mukora"
  57,5,Ubwami bw’ibirere n’isi ni ubwe. Kandi kwa Allah ni ho ibintu byose bizasubizwa
  57,6,"Yinjiza ijoro mu manywa, akaninjiza amanywa mu ijoro. Kandi ni we Mumenyi uhebuje w’ibiri mu bituza (by’abantu)"
  57,7,"Nimwemere Allah n’Intumwa ye (Muhamadi), munatange mu byo yabaragije; kuko bamwe muri mwe bemeye bakanatanga (mu nzira ya Allah), bazagororerwa ibihembo bihebuje"
  57,8,Nonese kuki mutemera Allah kandi Intumwa ibahamagarira kwemera Nyagasani wanyu? Kandi (Allah) yaranakiriye isezerano ryanyu rikomeye; (bityo) niba muri abemera nyakuri (ngaho nimwemere)
  57,9,"Ni we uhishurira umugaragu we (Muhamadi) amagambo asobanutse, kugira ngo abakure mu mwijima abaganisha ku rumuri. Rwose Allah ni Umunyempuhwe nyinshi kuri mwe, Umunyembabazi"
  57,10,"Nonese kuki mudatanga mu nzira ya Allah, kandi Allah ari we ufite izungura ry’ibirere n’isi? Abatanze bakanarwana mbere y’urugamba (rwo kubohora Maka) muri mwe, ntibahwanye (na babandi babikoze nyuma yaho); abo (babikoze mbere) bafite urwego rwisumbuye urw’abatanze bakanarwana nyuma. Ariko bose Allah yabasezeranyije ibyiza. Kandi Allah azi bihebuje ibyo mukora"
  57,11,"Ni nde waguriza Allah inguzanyo nziza (atanga amaturo n’ibindi bikorwa by’ubugiraneza), ngo (Allah azayimwishyure) amukubiye inshuro nyinshi, ndetse azanamugororere ibihembo bihebuje"
  57,12,"Umunsi uzabona abemeramana n’abemeramanakazi urumuri rwabo rukataje imbere n’iburyo bwabo (babwirwa) bati \"Dore inkuru nziza yanyu uyu munsi! Ni ubusitani butembamo imigezi (Ijuru), muzabamo ubuziraherezo. Iyi ni yo ntsinzi ihambaye"
  57,13,"Umunsi indyarya z’abagabo n’iz’abagore zizabwira abemeramana ziti \"Nimudutegereze turahure ku rumuri rwanyu!\" Zizabwirwa ziti \"Nimusubire inyuma (ku isi) mushake urumuri!\" Maze hagati yabo hashyirwe urukuta rufite umuryango. Imbere yarwo hari impuhwe, na ho hanze yarwo hakaba ibihano"
  57,14,"(Indyarya) zizahamagara (abemera) zibabwira ziti \"Ese ntitwari kumwe namwe (ku isi)?\" Bazisubize bati \"Yego! Ariko mwishyize mu bigeragezo, mutega iminsi (Intumwa n’abemeramana), munishyira mu gushidikanya kandi munashukwa n’irari ryanyu kugeza ubwo itegeko rya Allah (urupfu) risohoye. Nuko umushukanyi (Shitani) abatesha umurongo wa Allah"
  57,15,Uyu munsi nta nshungu yanyu (mwe ndyarya) cyangwa iy’abahakanye iri bwakirwe. Ubuturo bwanyu ni mu muriro. Ni wo muzabana kandi ni nawo herezo ribi
  57,16,"Ese igihe nticyari cyagera ngo imitima y’abemeye yicishe bugufi kubera kwibuka Allah n’ibyahishuwe by’ukuri (Quran)? No kugira ngo ntibabe nk’abahawe igitabo mbere yabo, nuko igihe (cyo gutegereza ibyo Intumwa zabasezeranyije) kikababana kirekire, maze imitima yabo ikinangira; kandi abenshi muri bo bari ibyigomeke"
  57,17,"Mumenye ko Allah aha isi ubuzima nyuma yo gupfa kwayo (gukakara). Mu by’ukuri, twabasobanuriye ibimenyetso kugira ngo mutekereze"
  57,18,"Mu by’ukuri, babandi batanga amaturo b’abagabo n’abagore, bakanaguriza Allah inguzanyo nziza, (Allah azabishyura) abakubiye inshuro nyinshi, ndetse azanabagororera ibihembo bihebuje"
  57,19,"Na babandi bemeye Allah n’intumwa ze (nta n’imwe barobanuye), ni bo banyakuri ndetse bakaba n’abahamya kwa Nyagasani wabo. Bazagororerwa ibihembo byabo n’urumuri rwabo. Naho abahakanye bakanahinyura amagambo yacu, bazaba abo mu muriro"
  57,20,"Mumenye ko ubuzima bw’isi nta kindi buri cyo uretse kuba ari umukino, kwinezeza, imitako, kwiyemera hagati yanyu ndetse no kwiratana imitungo n’abana. (Ibyo bigereranywa) nk’ibimera bishimisha abahinzi nyuma yo kubona imvura, hanyuma bikuma ukabona bibaye umuhondo; nuko (byamara utuvungukira. kumagana) Ariko bigahinduka ku munsi w’imperuka hazaba ibihano bikomeye (ku bahakanyi), ndetse n’imbabazi no kwishimirwa na Allah (ku bemeramana). Kandi ubuzima bw’isi ntacyo buri cyo uretse kuba ari umunezero ushukana"
  57,21,"Nimwihutire gushaka imbabazi ziva kwa Nyagasani wanyu, n’ijuru rifite ubugari bungana n’ubw’ikirere n’isi; ryateguriwe abemeye Allah n’intumwa ze. Izo ni ingabire za Allah aha uwo ashatse; kandi Allah ni Nyiringabire zihambaye"
  57,22,"Nta kibi cyagera ku isi cyangwa ngo kibabeho kitanditse mu gitabo (kirinzwe) mbere y’uko kiba. Mu by’ukuri, ibyo kuri Allah biroroshye"
  57,23,"Kugira ngo mutababazwa n’ibyabacitse cyangwa ngo mwiratane ibyo mwahawe. Mu by’ukuri, Allah ntakunda umunyagasuzuguro wese, umwibone"
  57,24,"Babandi bagira ubugugu bakanabushishikariza abantu. Ariko uzatera umugongo (kumvira Allah, amenye ko) Allah ari Umukungu, Usingizwa cyane"
  57,25,"Rwose twohereje intumwa zacu tuzihaye ibimenyetso bigaragara n’ibitangaza, ndetse tunazihishurira ibitabo n’ubutabera, kugira ngo abantu bimakaze ubutabera. Twanabamanuriye icyuma cy’umuringa gifite imbaraga zihambaye kandi kinafitiye abantu akamaro. (Ibyo byose byakozwe) kugira ngo Allah yerekane abamutabara (abatabara idini rye) ndetse n’Intumwa ze kandi batamuzi. Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Umunyembaraga zihebuje, Utsinda"
  57,26,"Kandi rwose twohereje Nuhu na Ibrahimu, maze duha urubyaro rwabo ubuhanuzi n’ibitabo. Muri bo hari abayobotse ariko abenshi muri bo babaye ibyigomeke"
  57,27,"Hanyuma tubakurikiza (izindi) ntumwa zacu zaje zitera ikirenge mu cyabo. Twakurikijeho kohereza Issa mwene Mariamu, tumuha Ivanjili, tunashyira impuhwe n’imbabazi mu mitima y’abamukurikiye, ariko bihimbiye kwiyegurira Imana (banga gushaka cyangwa gushakwa) nyamara ntabyo twabategetse, uretse ko babikoze bashaka ishimwe rya Allah, gusa ntibabyubahirije nk’uko bikwiye. Bityo, abemeye muri bo twabahaye ibihembo bakwiye, nyamara abenshi muri bo bari ibyigomeke"
  57,28,"Yemwe abemeye (Intumwa Musa na Issa)! Nimutinye Allah kandi munemere Intumwa ye (Muhamadi)! (Allah) azabaha impuhwe ze zikubye kabiri, anabahe urumuri mugendana ndetse anabababarire ibyaha byanyu. Allah ni Ubabarira bihebuje, Nyirimbabazi"
  57,29,"(Ibyo byose abikora) kugira ngo abahawe ibitabo bamenye ko nta bushobozi ubwo ari bwo bwose bagira mu ngabire za Allah, kandi ko ingabire zose ziri mu biganza bya Allah, akaba aziha uwo ashatse. Kandi Allah ni Nyiringabire zihambaye"
  58,1,"Mu by’ukuri, Allah yumvise imvugo (ubusabe) ya wa wundi (Khawulat bint Tha’laba) wakugishaga impaka (wowe Muhamadi) ku bijyanye n’umugabo we (Awus bin As-Samit), anaregera Allah. Kandi Allah yumvise ikiganiro cyanyu mwembi. Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Uwumva bihebuje, Ubona cyane"
  58,2,"Babandi muri mwe biziririza abagore babo babita ba nyina, kandi atari ba nyina, nyamara ba nyina (b’ukuri) ari abababyaye. Mu by’ukuri, baba bavuga ijambo ribi kandi ry’ikinyoma. Kandi mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Ubabarira ibyaha, Nyirimbabazi"
  58,3,"Na babandi biziririza abagore babo babita ba nyina, hanyuma bagashaka kwisubiraho ku byo bavuze (icyiru) cyabyo ni uko bagomba kubohora umucakara mbere y’uko bongera kubonana (n’abagore babo). Ibyo ni inyigisho muhabwa (na Allah), kandi Allah ni Umumenyi uhebuje w’ibyo mukora"
  58,4,"Naho utamubonye (uwo mucakara ngo amubohore), agomba gusiba amezi abiri akurikiranye mbere y’uko yongera kubonana (n’umugore we), ariko utabishoboye, agomba kugaburira abakene mirongo itandatu. Ibyo ni ukugira ngo mwemere Allah n’Intumwa ye. Izo ni imbago zashyizweho na Allah, kandi abahakanyi bazahanishwa ibihano bibabaza"
  58,5,"Mu by’ukuri, abaca ukubiri na Allah n’Intumwa ye, bazasuzuguzwa nk’uko ababayeho mbere yabo basuzugujwe. Kandi twohereje bisobanutse, kandi ibimenyetso abahakanyi bazahanishwa ibihano bisuzuguza"
  58,6,Umunsi Allah azabazura bose akababwira ibyo bakoze. Allah yarabibaruye mu gihe bo babyibagiwe. Kandi Allah ni Umuhamya wa buri kintu
  58,7,"Ese ntubona ko Allah azi ibiri mu birere n’ibiri ku isi? Nta biganiro byo mu ibanga bya batatu bibaho ngo abure kuba uwa kane, cyangwa ibya batanu ngo abure kuba ari uwa gatandatu, ndetse no munsi yabo cyangwa abarenzeho, ngo abure kuba ari kumwe na bo aho bari hose. Hanyuma ku munsi w’izuka akazababwira ibyo bakoraga. Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Umumenyi uhebuje wa buri kintu"
  58,8,"Ese ntiwabonye ababujijwe kugirana ibiganiro byo mu ibanga, nyuma bagasubira ku byo babujijwe, bakagirana ibiganiro mu ibanga bigamije icyaha n’ubugome ndetse no kwigomeka ku Ntumwa (Muhamadi)? N’iyo baje bagusanga, bagusuhuza mu ndamutso Allah atagusuhujemo, maze mu mitima yabo bakigamba bati \"Kubera iki Allah ataduhanira ibyo tuvuga?\" Umuriro wa Jahanamu urabahagije, bazawutwikirwamo kandi ni wo herezo ribi"
  58,9,"Yemwe abemeye! Nimujya mugirana ibiganiro mu ibanga, ntimukabikore mugamije icyaha n’ubugome ndetse no kwigomeka ku Ntumwa (Muhamadi). Ahubwo mujye mubigirana mugamije ibyiza no gutinya Allah, kandi mutinye Allah, kuko iwe ari ho muzakoranyirizwa"
  58,10,"Mu by’ukuri, kugirana ibiganiro mu ibanga hagamijwe ikibi (ubugambanyi) bituruka kwa Shitani, kugira ngo atere agahinda abemera, ariko ntacyo yabatwara keretse Allah abishatse. Ngaho abemera nibiringire Allah"
  58,11,"Yemwe abemeye! Nimubwirwa muti \"Nimwegerane muhane ibyicaro aho muteraniye\", mujye mubikora; Allah azabagurira (mu mpuwe Nimunabwirwa muti \"Muhaguruke ze). (mujye gusenga cyangwa mu kindi gikorwa cyiza)\", mujye muhaguruka. Allah azazamura mu ntera abemeye n’abahawe ubumenyi muri mwe. Kandi Allah ni Umumenyi uhebuje w’ibyo mukora"
  58,12,"Yemwe abemeye! Nimujya (mushaka) kugira ibyo muganira mu ibanga n’Intumwa (Muhamadi), mujye mubanza mutange amaturo mbere y’uko mubonana. Ibyo ni byo byiza kuri mwe kandi ni byo birushijeho kubeza (imitima). Ariko nimutabona (amaturo yo gutanga, mumenye ko muzababarirwa kuko) mu by’ukuri Allah ari Nyirimpuhwe, Nyirimbabazi"
  58,13,"Ese mufite ubwoba (bw’ubukene) igihe mwatanze amaturo mbere yo kugirana ibiganiro by’ibanga (n’Intumwa y’Imana)? Ibyo nimutabikora kandi Allah yarabababariye, mujye muhozaho amasengesho, mutange amaturo, ndetse mwumvire Allah n’Intumwa ye. Kandi Allah azi neza ibyo mukora"
  58,14,"Ese (yewe Muhamadi) ntiwabonye babandi (indyarya) bagiranye ubucuti n’abantu Allah yarakariye? Ntabwo bari muri mwe (Abayisilamu) ndetse ntibari no muri bo (Abayahudi), kandi barahira mu binyoma nyamara babizi"
  58,15,"Allah yabateguriye ibihano bikaze. Mu by’ukuri, ibyo bakoraga ni bibi"
  58,16,"Indahiro zabo bazigize ingabo (y’ibikorwa byabo bibi), banakumira abantu kugana inzira ya Allah. Bityo, bazahanishwa ibihano bisuzuguza"
  58,17,"Imitungo yabo n’abana babo ntacyo bizabamarira imbere ya Allah. Abo ni abantu bo mu muriro, bazawubamo ubuziraherezo"
  58,18,"Umunsi Allah azabazura bose, bazamurahirira nk’uko babarahiriraga (mwe Abayisilamu), kandi bakibwira ko hari icyo bishingikirije. Mu by’ukuri, ni abanyabinyoma"
  58,19,"Shitani yabagize imbata ze, maze abibagiza kwibuka Allah. Abo ni abambari ba Shitani. Mu by’ukuri, abambari ba Shitani ni bo bazaba abanyagihombo"
  58,20,"Mu by’ukuri, abaca ukubiri na Allah n’Intumwa ye (Muhamadi), bazaba basuzuguritse cyane"
  58,21,"Allah yaciye iteka agira ati \"Rwose, njye n’intumwa zanjye tuzatsinda\". Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Umunyembaraga, Ushobora byose"
  58,22,"Ntuzigera ubona abantu bemera Allah n’umunsi w’imperuka bagirana ubucuti na babandi baciye ukubiri na Allah n’Intumwa ye, kabone n’ubwo baba ari ababyeyi babo cyangwa abana babo cyangwa abavandimwe babo cyangwa se imiryango yabo. Abantu nk’abo, Allah yanditse ukwemera nyako mu mitima yabo, anabashyigikiza umwuka (inkunga) uturutse iwe, kandi azabinjiza mu busitani butembamo imigezi (Ijuru) bazabamo ubuziraherezo. Allah yarabishimiye na bo baramwishimira. Abo ni bo tsinda rya Allah, kandi mu by’ukuri itsinda rya Allah ni ryo rizatsinda"
  59,1,"Ibiri mu birere n’ibiri mu isi byose bisingiza Allah. Kandi (Allah) ni Umunyembaraga, Ushishoza"
  59,2,"Ni we wamenesheje abahakanye bo mu bahawe igitabo, abakura mu ngo zabo ku ikoraniro rya mbere 136. Ntimwakekaga ko bagenda kandi nabo bakekaga ko ingabo zabo zabarinda (ibihano bya) Allah! Nyamara ibihano bya Allah byabagezeho biturutse aho batakekaga, nuko abateza ubwoba mu mitima kugeza ubwo bisenyeye amazu bakoresheje amaboko yabo ndetse n’amaboko y’abemeramana. Ngaho nimubikuremo isomo yemwe abashishoza"
  59,3,"N’iyo bitaza kuba ko Allah yaciye iteka ko bameneshwa, rwose yari kubahana (mu bundi buryo) hano ku isi, kandi ku munsi w’imperuka bakazahanishwa ibihano by’umuriro"
  59,4,Ibyo ni ukubera ko baciye ukubiri na Allah n’Intumwa ye; kandi uca ukubiri na Allah (amenye ko) Allah ari Nyiribihano bikaze
  59,5,"(Yemwe abemeye!) Ibiti by’imitende (by’abanzi banyu) mwatemye cyangwa ibyo mwaretse bihagaze ku bitsinsi byabyo, byari ku bw’uburenganzira bwa Allah, no kugira ngo asuzuguze ibyigomeke"
  59,6,"N’ibyo Allah yahaye Intumwa ye (Muhamadi) nk’iminyago bibaturutseho, ibyo ntabwo mwigeze mwiyuha akuya mukoresheje amafarasi cyangwa ingamiya; ariko Allah atiza imbaraga intumwa ze (ngo zitsinde) uwo ashaka . Kandi Allah ni Ushobora byose"
  59,7,"Ibyo Allah yahaye Intumwa ye nk’iminyago iturutse ku bantu bo mu midugudu (hatabayeho imirwano), ni ibya Allah n’Intumwa ye, abafitanye isano (n’Intumwa), imfubyi, abakene n’abashiriwe ku rugendo; kugira ngo bitiharirwa n’abakire muri mwe gusa. Kandi ibyo Intumwa ibahaye (mu mitungo n’ibyo yabategetse) mujye mubyakira, ndetse n’ibyo ibabujije mujye mubireka. Munatinye Allah, mu by’ukuri Allah ni Nyiribihano bikaze"
  59,8,"(Muri iyo minyago kandi harimo igice cyagenewe) abakene bimutse bameneshejwe mu ngo zabo n’imitungo yabo, (babikoze) bashaka ingabire ziturutse kwa Allah no kwishimirwa na we, ndetse no gutera inkunga Allah n’Intumwa ye. Abo ni bo banyakuri"
  59,9,"Naho babandi batuye mbere yabo iki gihugu (cya Madina), bahisemo ukwemera banakunda abimutse babagana, kandi mu mitima ntibararikire ibyo (abo bimukira) bahawe, ahubwo bagaharira abandi bo biretse, kabone n’ubwo nabo ubwabo bagaba babikeneye. Kandi abarinzwe kugira ubugugu ni bo bazatsinda"
  59,10,"Na babandi baje nyuma yabo, baravuga bati \"Nyagasani wacu! Tubabarire, twe n’abavandimwe bacu badutanze kwemera, kandi ntuzatume mu mitima yacu harangwamo urwango ku bemeramana. Nyagasani wacu! Mu by’ukuri, ni wowe Nyirimpuhwe, Nyirimbabazi"
  59,11,"Ese (yewe Muhamadi) ntiwabonye ababaye indyarya, babwira bagenzi babo bahakanye bo mu bahawe igitabo bati \"Nimumeneshwa, rwose tuzajyana na mwe, kandi ntawundi tuzigera twumvira utari mwe. Ndetse nimunaterwa tuzabatabara\". Nyamara Allah ahamya ko ari abanyabinyoma"
  59,12,"Mu by’ukuri, (Abayahudi) nibaramuka bameneshejwe, (indyarya) ntizizigera zijyana na bo, nibanaterwa ntizizabatabara. Kandi (n’iyo) zanabatabara, zizahindukira zitera umugongo maze ntibatabarwe"
  59,13,"Mu by’ukuri, (yemwe abemeye) ni mwe mutinyitse cyane mu mitima yabo (indyarya) kurusha Allah. Ibyo ni uko ari abantu badasobanukiwe"
  59,14,"(Abahakanyi) ntibazigera babarwanya bari hamwe, keretse bari mu midugudu irinzwe cyangwa inyuma y’inkuta. Intambara hagati yabo iba ikaze. Ukeka ko bari kumwe nyamara imitima yabo iba itatanye. Ibyo ni uko ari abantu badafite ubwenge"
  59,15,"(Urugero rw’ibyababayeho ni) nk’urw’ibyabaye mbere yabo (abahakanyi ba Maka mu rugamba rwa Badr n’Abayahudi bo mu bwoko bwa Qayinuqa’i) basogongeye ingaruka z’ibikorwa byabo (hano ku isi), kandi (ku munsi w’imperuka) bazahanishwa ibihano bibabaza"
  59,16,"(Urugero rwabo kandi ni) nk’urwa Shitani ubwo yabwiraga umuntu iti \"Hakana (Allah)!\" Nyamara yamara guhakana, ikavuga iti (Shitani \"Mu ikamwitakana) by’ukuri, njye nitandukanyije na we; njye ntinya Allah, Nyagasani w’ibiremwa byose"
  59,17,Ubwo iherezo ryabo bombi ni uko bazaba mu muriro ubuziraherezo. Icyo ni cyo gihembo cy’inkozi z’ibibi
  59,18,"Yemwe abemeye! Nimutinye Allah kandi buri muntu arebe ibyo yiteganyirije ejo. Munatinye Allah, mu by’ukuri, Allah azi neza ibyo mukora"
  59,19,"Kandi ntimuzanabe nk’abibagiwe Allah (banze kumvira Allah), ku bw’iyo mpamvu akabatera kwiyibagirwa ubwabo (bakareka gukora ibikorwa byiza). Abo ni bo byigomeke"
  59,20,(Mumenye ko) abantu bo mu muriro n’abantu bo mu Ijuru badahwanye. Abantu bo mu Ijuru ni bo bazatsinda
  59,21,"Iyo iyi Qur’an tuza kuyihishurira ku musozi, wari kuwubona wibombaritse ndetse ukanasatagurika kubera gutinya Allah. Izo ni ingero duha abantu kugira ngo batekereze"
  59,22,"Ni Allah, nta yindi mana ibaho itari we. Umumenyi w’ibitagaragara ndetse n’ibigaragara. Ni Nyirimpuhwe, Nyirimbabazi"
  59,23,"Ni Allah, nta yindi mana ibaho itari we; Umwami, Umutagatifu, Umuziranenge, Umwishingizi, Umugenzuzi, Ushobora byose, Igihangange, Ukwiye ikuzo. Ubutagatifu ni ubwa Allah, ntaho ahuriye n’ibyo bamubangikanya nabyo"
  59,24,"Ni Allah, Umuremyi, Umuhanzi, Utangishusho. Afite amazina meza. Ibiri mu birere n’isi biramusingiza, kandi ni Umunyembaraga uhebuje, Ushishoza"
  60,1,"Yemwe abemeye! Ntimukagire abanzi banjye n’abanzi banyu inshuti magara, mubereka urukundo kandi barahakanye ibyabagezeho by’ukuri (kwemera Allah n’Intumwa yayo Muhamadi na Qur’an) ndetse baranamenesheje Intumwa (Muhamadi) na mwe ubwanyu (bakabirukana mu gihugu cyanyu) kubera ko mwemeye Allah, Nyagasani wanyu. Niba mugiye mugamije guharanira inzira yanjye no gushaka kwishimirwa nanjye (ntimukabagire inshuti). Muhisha urukundo mubafitiye kandi njye nzi ibyo muhisha n’ibyo mugaragaza. Ukora ibyo muri mwe, rwose yayobye inzira itunganye"
  60,2,"Baramutse babatsinze, bababera ababisha (ku mugaragaro) bakabaramburaho amaboko yabo (babica) n’indimi zabo bagamije inabi, ndetse bakanifuza ko mwahakana"
  60,3,(Mumenye ko) imiryango yanyu n’abana banyu ntacyo bizabamarira (imbere ya Allah). Ku munsi w’imperuka (Allah) azabakiranura. Kandi Allah ni Ubona bihebuje ibyo mukora
  60,4,"Mu by’ukuri, mwagize urugero rwiza kuri Ibrahim n’abari kumwe na we, ubwo babwiraga abantu babo bati \"Rwose twitandukanyije namwe ndetse n’ibyo mugaragira bitari Allah. Turabahakanye. Hagati yacu na mwe havutse ububisha n’ubugome bihoraho, kugeza ubwo muzemera Allah wenyine.\" Uretse imvugo ya Ibrahim abwira se ati \"Rwose nzagusabira imbabazi (kuri Allah), ariko nta bushobozi mfite bwo kugira icyo nkumarira imbere ya Allah.\" (Basabye Nyagasani bagira bati) Nyagasani wacu! Ni wowe twiringiye kandi ni na we twicuzaho ndetse iwawe ni ho garukiro (ryacu twese)’"
  60,5,"Nyagasani wacu! Ntutugire ikigeragezo ku bahakanye, kandi utubabarire Nyagasani wacu! Mu by’ukuri, ni wowe Munyembaraga uhebuje, Ushishoza"
  60,6,"Rwose bababereye urugero rwiza (mugomba gukurikira) kuri babandi bizeye Allah n’umunsi w’imperuka. Ariko uzatera umugongo (inzira ya Allah, amenye ko) mu by’ukuri, Allah ari we Mukungu, Ushimwa cyane"
  60,7,"Hari ubwo Allah yashyira urukundo hagati yanyu ndetse na bamwe mu bo mufitanye urwango, kandi Allah ni Ushobora byose. Ndetse Allah ni Nyirimpuhwe, Nyirimbabazi"
  60,8,"Allah ntababuza kugirira ineza n’ubutabera abatarabarwanyije mu idini ntibanabameneshe mu ngo zanyu. Mu by’ukuri, Allah akunda abatabera"
  60,9,"Ahubwo Allah ababuza kugira inshuti magara ababarwanyije mu idini bakanabakura mu ngo zanyu, ndetse bakanashyigikira kubamenesha. Ariko (abandi) abazabagira inshuti magara ni bo byigomeke"
  60,10,"Yemwe abemeye! Abemeramanakazi b’abimukira nibabagana, mujye mubagerageza (kugira ngo mumenye ukwemera kwabo). Allah ni we uzi neza ukwemera kwabo. Nimumara kumenya ko ari abemera nyakuri, ntimukabasubize mu bahakanyi. (Abo bagore) ntibaziruriwe (abagabo b’abahakanyi) ndetse na bo (abagabo b’abahakanyi) ntibabaziruriwe. Ahubwo mujye mwishyura (abagabo babo b’abahakanyi) ibyo babatanzeho (inkwano). Kandi nta kibi kuri mwe muramutse mubarongoye igihe mwabahaye inkwano zabo. Ntimukihambire ku masezerano mwagiranye n’abagore bahakanye, ahubwo mujye musaba gusubizwa ibyo mwatanze, maze na bo (abagabo b’abahakanyi) basabe ibyo batanze. Iryo ni itegeko rya Allah abakiranurisha. Kandi Allah ni Umumenyi uhebuje, Ushishoza"
  60,11,"Nihagira umwe mu bagore banyu ubacika akajya mu bahakanyi (ntibabasubize inkwano mwabatanzeho), hanyuma habaho impamvu yo kurwana nabo mukabatsinda (mukagira iminyago mubakuraho), mujye muha abo abagore babo bagiye ibingana n’ibyo babatanzeho (inkwano). Kandi mutinye Allah we mwemera"
  60,12,"Yewe Muhanuzi! Abemeramanakazi nibakugana bagusezeranya ko ntacyo bazabangikanya na Allah, ko bataziba, ko batazasambana, ko batazica abana babo, ko batazagira uwo bahimbira ibinyoma, kandi ko batazakwigomekaho mu byiza; ujye wakira ibyo bagusezeranyije unabasabire imbabazi kwa Allah. Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Nyirimpuhwe, Nyirimbabazi"
  60,13,"Yemwe abemeye! Ntimukagire inshuti magara abantu Allah yarakariye. Mu by’ukuri, bihebye (kuzagira icyiza babona) ku munsi w’imperuka, nk’uko abahakanyi bari mu mva bihebye ko (batazabona imbabazi za Allah). puh"
  61,1,"Ibiri mu birere n’ibiri ku isi bisingiza Allah; kandi ni Umunyembaraga uhebuje, Ushishoza"
  61,2,Yemwe abemeye! Kuki muvuga ibyo mudakora
  61,3,Ibyo birakaza Allah bikomeye kuba muvuga ibyo mudakora
  61,4,"Mu by’ukuri, Allah akunda abarwana mu nzira ye bari ku mirongo (bashyize hamwe), bameze nk’inyubako isobetse"
  61,5,"Unibuke ubwo Musa yabwiraga abantu be ati \"Yemwe bantu banjye! Kuki muntoteza kandi muzi ko rwose ndi Intumwa ya Allah yaboherejweho? Nuko ubwo bayobaga (inzira ya Allah), Allah yarekeye imitima yabo mu buyobe, kuko Allah atayobora abantu b’ibyigomeke"
  61,6,"Unibuke ubwo Issa mwene Mariyamu yavugaga ati \"Yemwe bene Isiraheli! Mu by’ukuri, njye ndi intumwa ya Allah yaboherejweho, nshimangira ibyambanjirije byo muri Tawurati, kandi nkanatanga inkuru nziza y’intumwa izaza nyuma yanjye. Izina ryayo rizaba ari Ahmad (ari we Muhamadi).\" Nuko ubwo yabazaniraga ibitangaza, baravuze bati \"Ubu ni uburozi bugaragara"
  61,7,"Ese ni nde nkozi y’ibibi kurusha uhimbira Allah ikinyoma, kandi ahamagarirwa kuyoboka Isilamu? Kandi Allah ntayobora abantu b’inkozi z’ibibi"
  61,8,"Barashaka kuzimya urumuri rwa Allah (idini ye) bakoresheje iminwa yabo, ariko Allah azasendereza urumuri rwe kabone n’ubwo byababaza abahakanyi"
  61,9,"Ni we wohereje Intumwa ye (Muhamadi) ayihaye umuyoboro n’idini ry’ukuri, kugira ngo arirutishe amadini yose, kabone n’ubwo byababaza ababangikanyamana"
  61,10,Yemwe abemeye! Mbarangire ubucuruzi buzabarokora ibihano bibabaza
  61,11,"Nimwemere Allah n’Intumwa ye (Muhamadi), munaharanire inzira ya Allah mukoresheje imitungo yanyu na mwe ubwanyu. Ibyo ni byo byiza kuri mwe, iyaba mwari mubizi"
  61,12,"(Nimubigenza mutyo) azabababarira ibyaha byanyu, anabinjize mu busitani butembamo imigezi, n’ubuturo bwiza mu busitani buhoraho (Ijuru). Uko ni ko gutsinda guhambaye"
  61,13,"(Azanabaha) n’ibindi mukunda: ugutabara guturutse kwa Allah n’intsinzi ya bugufi. Bityo, tanga inkuru nziza ku bemeramana"
  61,14,"Yemwe abemeye! Nimube abashyigikira (idini rya) Allah, nk’uko Issa mwene Mariyamu yabwiye abigishwa be ati \"Ni bande banshyigikira mu nzira ya Allah?\" Abigishwa baravuga bati \"Turi abashyigikiye Allah\". Nuko itsinda rya bamwe muri bene Isiraheli riremera, irindi rirahakana. Maze dushyigikira abemeye batsinda abanzi babo"
  62,1,"Ibiri mu birere n’ibiri ku isi bisingiza Allah, Umwami, Umutagatifu, Umunyembaraga uhebuje, Ushishoza"
  62,2,"Ni we wohereje Intumwa (Muhamadi) mu batazi gusoma no kwandika (b’Abarabu), ibakomokamo, ibasomera amagambo ye, ibeza ndetse ikanabigisha igitabo (Qur’an) n’ubushishozi (imigenzo y’intumwa); kandi mu by’ukuri, mbere bari mu buyobe bugaragara"
  62,3,"(Iyo Ntumwa yanoherejwe) no ku bandi muri bo (batari Abarabu), bari batarabakurikira (ariko bazaza). Kandi (Allah) ni Umunyembaraga uhebuje, Ushishoza"
  62,4,"Izo ni ingabire za Allah aha uwo ashatse, kandi Allah ni Nyiringabire zihambaye"
  62,5,"Abaragijwe (amategeko ya) Tawurati ariko ntibayikurikize, bagereranywa nk’indogobe yikoreye ibitabo (ariko ikaba itazi ibyanditsemo). Mbega urugero rubi rw’abantu bahinyuye amagambo ya Allah! Kandi Allah ntayobora abantu b’abahakanyi"
  62,6,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Yemwe ababaye Abayahudi! Niba mwibwira ko muri inshuti za Allah kurusha abandi bantu bose, ngaho nimwifuze urupfu niba koko muri abanyakuri"
  62,7,Nyamara rwose ntibarwifuza na gato kubera ibyo bakoze (bibi). Kandi Allah azi neza inkozi z’ibibi
  62,8,"Babwire uti \"Mu by’ukuri, urupfu muhunga ruzabageraho nta kabuza, hanyuma mugarurwe kuri we (Allah), Umumenyi w’ibitagaragara n’ibigaragara, maze ababwire ibyo mwakoraga"
  62,9,"Yemwe abemeye! Umuhamagaro w’isengesho ry’umunsi wa gatanu (Ijuma) nuhamagarwa, mujye mwihuta mujya gusingiza Allah, kandi muhagarike ubucuruzi (n’ibindi bintu byose). Ibyo ni byo byiza kuri mwe, iyaba mwari mubizi"
  62,10,"Isengesho nirirangira, mujye muhita mugendagenda ku isi, mushakisha zimwe mu ngabire za Allah, kandi munasingize Allah cyane kugira ngo mukiranuke"
  62,11,"Ariko iyo (bamwe) babonye ubucuruzi cyangwa ibindi byo kwinezeza, barabishidukira bakagusiga uhagaze wenyine (wowe Muhamadi, uri gutanga inyigisho z’umunsi wa gatanu). Vuga uti \"Ibiri kwa Allah ni byo byiza kurusha kwishimisha n’ubucuruzi! Kandi Allah ni we Uhebuje mu batanga amafunguro"
  63,1,"Iyo indyarya zije zikugana (yewe Muhamadi), ziravuga ziti \"Turemeza ko mu by’ukuri, uri Intumwa ya Allah.\" Ndetse na Allah azi neza ko uri Intumwa ye, kandi Allah ahamya ko indyarya ari inyabinyoma"
  63,2,"Indahiro zabo bazigize ingabo (zibakingira uburyarya bwabo), bityo bakumiriye (abantu) kugana inzira ya Allah. Mu by’ukuri, ibyo bakoraga ni bibi"
  63,3,"Ibyo ni ukubera ko babanje kwemera hanyuma bagahakana. Bityo, imitima yabo yaradanangiwe, ikaba ari yo mpamvu badasobanukirwa"
  63,4,"N’iyo ubarebye imibiri yabo iragushimisha, ndetse n’iyo bavuze, wumva amagambo yabo. Bameze nk’ibiti byegetse (ku nkuta kubera kutumva kwabo). Bakeka ko buri nduru ivugijwe ari bo iba ivugirijwe. Ni abanzi, bityo jya ubirinda. Umuvumo wa Allah nubabeho! Ni gute bateshwa (inzira igororotse)"
  63,5,"N’iyo babwiwe bati \"Nimuze Intumwa ya Allah ibasabire imbabazi,\" bazunguza imitwe, ukababona basubira inyuma (bagutera umugongo), buzuye ubwibone"
  63,6,"Wabasabira imbabazi utazibasabira, byose ni kimwe kuri bo, Allah ntazigera abababarira. Mu by’ukuri, Allah ntayobora abantu b’ibyigomeke"
  63,7,"Ni bo bavuga bati \"Ntimukagire icyo muha abari kumwe n’Intumwa ya Allah, kugeza ubwo bitandukanije na yo. Nyamara Allah ni we Nyir’ibigega by’ibirere n’isi, ariko indyarya ntizibisobanukirwa"
  63,8,"(Indyarya) ziravuga ziti \"Nituramuka dusubiye i Madina, mu by’ukuri umunyacyubahiro cyane (ari we Abdullah bin Ubay bin Salul, wari umuyobozi w’Indyarya i Madina) azahirukana usuzuguritse cyane (Intumwa y’Imana Muhamadi).\" Nyamara icyubahiro nyacyo ni icya Allah n’Intumwa ye (Muhamadi) ndetse n’abemeramana; ariko indyarya ntabwo zibizi"
  63,9,Yemwe abemeye! Imitungo yanyu n’abana banyu ntibikabarangaze ngo bibabuze kwambaza Allah. Abakora ibyo ni bo bazaba abanyagihombo
  63,10,"Mujye mutanga mu byo twabahaye mbere y’uko urupfu rugera kuri umwe muri mwe maze akavuga ati \"Nyagasani! Iyaba wari untije igihe gito ngatanga amaturo ndetse nkaba no mu bakora ibikorwa byiza"
  63,11,Kandi Allah ntazigera arindiriza umuntu igihe cye (cyo gupfa) cyageze. Allah ni Umumenyi uhebuje w’ibyo mukora
  64,1,"Ibiri mu birere n’ibiri ku isi bisingiza Allah. Ubwami n’ishimwe ndetse n’ikuzo byuzuye ni ibye, kandi ni we Ushobora byose"
  64,2,"Ni we wabaremye, ariko bamwe muri mwe ni abahakanyi ndetse na bamwe muri mwe ni abemeramana. Kandi Allah ni Ubona bihebuje ibyo mukora"
  64,3,"Yaremye ibirere n’isi mu kuri, nuko abaha amashusho maze arayatunganya; kandi iwe ni ho garukiro (ryacu twese)"
  64,4,"Azi ibiri mu birere n’isi, akanamenya ibyo muhisha n’ibyo mugaragaza; kandi Allah ni Umumenyi uhebuje w’ibiri mu bituza (by’abantu)"
  64,5,"Ese inkuru ya babandi bahakanye mbere ntiyabagezeho ko basogongeye ingaruka z’ibikorwa byabo (hano ku isi), kandi (ko ku munsi w’imperuka) bazahanishwa ibihano bibabaza"
  64,6,"Ni na ko Intumwa zabo zabageragaho zibazaniye ibimenyetso bigaragara, ariko bakavuga bati \"Ese abantu (bameze nkatwe) batuyobora?\" Nuko bagahakana bagatera umugongo. Nyamara Allah arihagije, ntacyo abakeneyeho, kandi Allah ni Umukungu, Ushimwa cyane"
  64,7,"Abahakanyi bakeka ko batazazurwa (ngo babazwe)? Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Yego! Ndahiye ku izina rya Nyagasani wanjye, rwose muzazurwa maze mubwirwe ibyo mwakoze, kandi kuri Allah ibyo biroroshye"
  64,8,"Bityo, nimwemere Allah n’Intumwa ye (Muhamadi) ndetse n’urumuri (Quran) twahishuye. Kandi Allah ni Umumenyi uhebuje w’ibyo mukora"
  64,9,"(Unibuke) umunsi azabakoranya (mwese) ku munsi w’ikoraniro; uwo uzaba ari munsi w’igihombo (ku banyabyaha). Kandi uwemera Allah akanakora ibikorwa byiza, azamubabarira ibibi (yakoze) anamwinjize mu busitani butembamo imigezi (Ijuru), azabamo ubuziraherezo. Uko ni ko gutsinda guhambaye"
  64,10,"Naho abahakanye bakanahinyura amagambo yacu, bazaba abo mu muriro bazabamo ubuziraherezo; kandi iryo ni igarukiro ribi"
  64,11,"Nta kibi gishobora kuba (ku muntu) bitari mu bushake bwa Allah. Ndetse n’uwemeye Allah, (Allah) ayobora umutima we (mu kwemera nyako). Kandi Allah ni Umumenyi uhebuje wa buri kintu"
  64,12,"Nimwumvire Allah kandi munumvire Intumwa (Muhamadi). Ariko nimutera umugongo, mu by’ukuri, Intumwa yacu nta kindi ishinzwe uretse gusohoza ubutumwa mu buryo bugaragara"
  64,13,"Allah! Nta yindi mana itari we. Bityo, abemera ngaho nibiringire Allah (wenyine)"
  64,14,"Yemwe abemeye! Mu by’ukuri, bamwe mu bagore banyu n’abana banyu, ni abanzi banyu (bashobora kubabuza kumvira Allah); bityo, mujye mubitondera! Ariko nimubababarira, mukirengagiza (amakosa yabo) ndetse mukanarenzaho, mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Nyirimpuhwe, Nyirimbabazi"
  64,15,"Mu by’ukuri, imitungo yanyu n’abana banyu ni ikigeragezo, ariko Allah afite ibihembo bihambaye (Ijuru)"
  64,16,"Bityo, nimutinye Allah uko mubishoboye, mwumve (ibyo Intumwa ibigisha) kandi mwumvire (amategeko yayo) ndetse munatange amaturo; bizaba ari byo byiza kuri mwe. Kandi abarinzwe kugira ubugugu ni bo bazatsinda"
  64,17,"Nimuramuka mugurije Allah inguzanyo nziza (mutanga kubera we), azayibatuburira anabababarire. Kandi Allah ni Ushima (ibikorwa by’abagaragu be), Uworohera (abagaragu be)"
  64,18,"Umumenyi w’ibitagaragara n’ibigaragara, Umunyembaraga uhebuje, Ushishoza"
  65,1,"Yewe Muhanuzi (Muhamadi)! Nimusenda abagore, mujye mubasenda mukurikije igihe cyabo cyagenwe (Eda)137, ndetse mujye mubara igihe cyabo (Eda) neza, kandi munatinye Allah, Nyagasani wanyu. Ntimukabasohore mu ngo zabo cyangwa se na bo ngo bijyane, keretse bakoze icyaha kigaragara (ubusambanyi). Izo ni imbago zashyizweho na Allah, kandi urenze imbago za Allah, aba yihemukiye. (Wowe wasenze umugore wawe) ntiwamenya, hari ubwo nyuma y’ibyo, Allah yabihindura ukundi (mukaba mwakongera gusubirana)"
  65,2,"Nibaba begereje igihe cyabo, mushobora kugumana nabo ku neza cyangwa mugatandukana nabo ku neza. (Igihe mwahisemo kugumana cyangwa gutandukana na bo) mujye mubishakira abahamya babiri b’inyangamugayo muri mwe. Kandi (mwe batangabuhamya) mujye mutanga ubuhamya kubera Allah. Ibyo ni inyigisho ku wemera Allah n’umunsi w’imperuka. Kandi utinya Allah, amucira icyanzu"
  65,3,"Akanamuha amafunguro mu buryo atakekaga. Kandi uwiringira Allah, aramuhagije. Mu by’ukuri, Allah azasohoza umugambi we. Kandi buri kintu Allah yagishyiriyeho igeno (ryacyo)"
  65,4,"Na babandi bacuze mu bagore banyu (batakijya imugongo), nimuramuka mushidikanyije (ku gihe cyabo cya Eda); igihe cyabo (bagomba gutegereza bakiri mu ngo zabo) ni amezi atatu, ni kimwe na babandi batari bajya imugongo (na bo igihe cyabo ni amezi atatu). Naho abatwite (baba baratandukanye n’abagabo cyangwa abagabo babo barapfuye), igihe cyabo ni ukugeza babyaye. Kandi utinya Allah, amworohereza ibye"
  65,5,"Iryo ni itegeko rya Allah yabahishuriye. Kandi utinya Allah, azamubabarira ibyaha bye anamutuburire ibihembo"
  65,6,"(Abo bagore bategereje igihe cyabo cya Eda) mujye mubarekera aho mutuye bijyanye n’ubushobozi bwanyu. Ntimukanabatoteze mugamije kubabuza amahwemo (kugira ngo babavire mu ngo). Nibaba batwite, mujye mubaha ibibatunga kugeza babyaye. Nibabonkereza (bakabasaba igihembo) mujye mubaha ibihembo byabo, kandi mujye mubijyaho inama ku neza. Ariko nimutumvikana, undi (mugore) yamumwonkereza"
  65,7,"(Umugabo) wishoboye, ajye atanga bijyanye n’ubushobozi bwe. N’ufite ubushobozi buciriritse ajye atanga mu byo Allah yamuhaye (bingana n’ubushobozi bwe). Allah ntategeka umuntu gukora ibirenze ubushobozi yamuhaye. Rwose nyuma y’ibihe bikomeye, Allah arabyoroshya"
  65,8,"Ese ni imidugudu ingahe yigometse ku itegeko rya Nyagasani wayo n’intumwa ze, nuko tukayiryoza mu buryo bukomeye ibyo yakoze, ndetse tukazanayihanisha ibihano bikaze (ku munsi w’imperuka)"
  65,9,"Bityo, (iyo midugudu) yasogongeye ingaruka z’ibikorwa byayo, kandi iherezo ryayo ryabaye igihombo gikomeye"
  65,10,Allah yabateguriye ibihano bikaze. Ngaho nimutinye Allah yemwe bantu mufite ubwenge mukaba mwaranemeye! Rwose Allah yabahishuriye urwibutso
  65,11,"(Ari rwo) ntumwa ibasomera amagambo ya Allah (Quran) asobanutse, kugira ngo akure mu mwijima babandi bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza anabaganisha ku rumuri. Bityo, uwemera Allah akanakora ibikorwa byiza, (Allah) azamwinjiza mu busitani butembamo imigezi (Ijuru) bazabamo ubuziraherezo. Rwose Allah yamutunganyirije amafunguro (meza)"
  65,12,"Allah ni we waremye ibirere birindwi (anarema) isi (zirindwi) nkabyo. Itegeko rye rimanuka hagati yabyo (ibirere n’isi), kugira ngo mumenye ko Allah ari Ushobora byose, ndetse ko Allah azi neza buri kintu"
  66,1,"Yewe Muhanuzi (Muhamadi)! Kuki wiziririza ibyo Allah yakuziruriye ugamije gushimisha abagore bawe? Kandi Allah ni Nyirimpuhwe, Nyirimbabazi"
  66,2,"Rwose (yemwe abemeramana) Allah yabategetse uburyo muzirura indahiro zanyu (mutanga icyiru) 138. Kandi Allah ni Umurinzi wanyu akaba n’Umumenyi uhebuje, Ushishoza"
  66,3,"(Zirikana) ubwo Umuhanuzi (Muhamadi) yabitsaga ibanga umwe mu bagore be (Hafsa), maze ubwo yarimenaga (aribwira mukeba we Ayisha), (Allah abihishurira Umuhanuzi) maze (Umuhanuzi) amenyesha (Hafsa) bimwe muri byo, ibindi arabireka. Nuko ubwo yabimubwiraga, (Hafsa) aravuga ati \"Ni nde wakubwiye ibi? (Intumwa) iravuga iti \"Nabibwiwe n’Umumenyi uhebuje, Uzi neza buri kintu"
  66,4,"Nimwicuza mwembi (Hafsa na Ayisha) kuri Allah (bizaba ari byo byiza kuri mwe) kuko imitima yanyu yateshutse. Ariko nimumuteraniraho (Umuhanuzi, mugamije kumubuza amahoro), mu by’ukuri Allah ni we Murinzi we; azanatabarwa na (Malayika) Jibrilu n’abemeramana bakora ibikorwa byiza ndetse n’abamalayika (bazamutabara)"
  66,5,"(Umuhanuzi) aramutse abahaye ubutane, hari ubwo Nyagasani we yamuguranira akamuha abagore beza babaruta: b’abayisilamukazi, abemeramanakazi, bibombarika (kuri Allah), bicuza, bagaragira Allah, basiba (Swawumu), baba barashatse cyangwa bakiri amasugi"
  66,6,"Yemwe abemeye! Nimwirinde (murinde) n’imiryango yanyu umuriro, kuko ibicanwa byawo bizaba abantu n’amabuye; (kandi) urinzwe n’abamalayika b’inkazi, b’abanyembaraga, ntibajya bigomeka na rimwe ku byo Allah abategetse, ahubwo bakora ibyo bategetswe"
  66,7,"(Abahakanyi bazabwirwa bati) \"Yemwe abahakanye! Uyu munsi nta rwitwazo (muri bugire)! Mu by’ukuri, murahanirwa ibyo mwajyaga mukora"
  66,8,"Yemwe abemeye! Nimwicuze kwa Allah ukwicuza nyako, kugira ngo Nyagasani wanyu abababarire ibyaha byanyu, azanabinjize mu busitani butembamo imigezi (Ijuru). Umunsi Allah atazakoza isoni Umuhanuzi (Muhamadi) n’abemeye hamwe na we. Urumuri rwabo ruzaba rukataje imbere n’iburyo bwabo, bavuga bati \"Nyagasani wacu! Twuzurize urumuri, unatubabarire ibyaha. Mu by’ukuri, ni wowe Ushobora byose"
  66,9,Yewe Muhanuzi (Muhamadi)! Rwanya abahakanyi n’indyarya unabakarire. Kandi ubuturo bwabo ni umuriro wa Jahanamu; ndetse ni ryo herezo ribi
  66,10,"Allah yatanze urugero ku bahakanye: (ari bo) umugore w’Intumwa Nuhu n’umugore w’Intumwa Lutwi. (Abo bombi) bari abagore b’abagaragu bacu babiri b’intungane, ariko (abo bagore) baje kubahemukira (bahakana ubutumwa bwabo, nuko abagabo babo) ntibagira icyo babamarira kwa Allah (ngo babasabire kudahanwa), maze (abo bagore) barabwirwa bati \"Nimwinjire mu muriro hamwe n’abawinjiramo"
  66,11,"Allah yanatanze urugero ku bemeye: (ari bo) umugore wa Farawo, ubwo yavugaga ati \"Nyagasani wanjye! Nyubakira inzu iwawe mu Ijuru unandinde Farawo n’ibikorwa bye, kandi undinde abantu b’inkozi z’ibibi"
  66,12,"Na Mariyamu mwene Imrani, we warinze ubusugi bwe maze tumuhumekeramo (tubinyujije kuri) Roho wacu (Malayika Jibrilu), nuko yemera amagambo ya Nyagasani we n’ibitabo bye (ko ari ukuri), kandi yari mu bibombarika (kuri Allah)"
  67,1,"Ubutagatifu ni ubwa (Allah), ufite ubwami (bwose) mu kuboko kwe, kandi ni Ushobora byose"
  67,2,"Ni we waremye urupfu n’ubuzima kugira ngo abagerageze (hanyuma amenye) ukora ibikorwa byiza kurusha abandi muri mwe, kandi ni Umunyembaraga uhebuje, Ubabarira ibyaha"
  67,3,Ni we waremye ibirere birindwi bigerekeranye. Ntushobora kubona inenge mu byo (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe yaremye. Ngaho ongera wubure amaso (urebe); ese hari inenge ubona
  67,4,"Hanyuma wongere wubure amaso ubugira kabiri, amaso aragaruka yamwaye kandi yacitse intege"
  67,5,"Rwose ikirere cyegereye isi twagitakishije amatara (inyenyeri), tunayagira nk’ibisasu bya Misile byo gutera za shitani (zigometse), kandi twanaziteguriye igihano cy’umuriro ugurumana"
  67,6,"Abahakanye Nyagasani wabo bazahanishwa ibihano by’umuriro wa Jahanamu, kandi iryo ni ryo garukiro ribi"
  67,7,"Ubwo bazaba bajugunywemo (mu muriro wa Jahanamu), bazumva utogota kandi ubira"
  67,8,"(Uwo muriro) uzaba wenda gusandara kubera umujinya (ufitiye abanyabyaha)! Buri uko agatsiko kazajya kawujugunywamo, abarinzi bawo bazajya bakabaza bati \"Ese nta muburizi wabagezeho"
  67,9,"Bazavuga bati \"Yego! Rwose umuburizi yatugezeho ariko twaramuhinyuye, turanavuga tuti \" Allah nta kintu yigeze ahishura, tuti ahubwo mwe muri mu buyobe buhambaye"
  67,10,"Bazanavuga bati \"Iyo tuza kumva cyangwa tukanatekereza, ntitwari kuba mu bo mu muriro ugurumana"
  67,11,"Baziyemerera ibyaha byabo (ariko ntacyo bizabamarira). Bityo, ukorama nikube ku bantu bo mu muriro ugurumana"
  67,12,"Mu by’ukuri, abatinya Nyagasani wabo batamubona, bazababarirwa ibyaha ndetse banahabwe ibihembo bihebuje"
  67,13,"Kandi ibiganiro byanyu mwabikorera mu bwiru cyangwa mukabigaragaza, mu by’ukuri (Allah) ni Umumenyi uhebuje w’ibiri mu bituza (by’abantu)"
  67,14,"Ese Uwaremye yayoberwa (ibyo yaremye)? Kandi ni we Uworohera (ibiremwa bye), Uzi byimazeyo (buri kintu)"
  67,15,"Ni we waborohereje isi; ngaho nimutambagire mu mpande zayo (zinyuranye), ndetse murye mu mafunguro ye (Allah). Kandi iwe ni ho muzazurirwa"
  67,16,Ese muratekanye (yemwe bahakanyi) ku buryo (mwizeye ko) uri mu Ijuru (Allah) atatigisa isi maze mukarigitamo
  67,17,Cyangwa se muratekanye ku buryo (mwizeye ko) uri mu Ijuru ataboherereza inkubi y’umuyaga uvanze n’amabuye (wabarimbura mwese)? Ubwo ni bwo muzamenya uko ukuburira kwanjye (kumeze)
  67,18,Rwose ababayeho mbere yabo (abahakanyi b’i Maka) barahinyuye. Mbega uko uburakari bwanjye bwari bumeze
  67,19,"Ese ntibabona ibiguruka (inyoni) hejuru yabo uko biguruka birambura amababa yabyo bikanayahina? Nta wubifata (ngo bitagwa hasi) usibye (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe. Mu by’ukuri, ni Ubona bihebuje buri kintu"
  67,20,Ahubwo se ni nde wababera ingabo (yemwe bahakanyi) ngo abatabare usibye (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe? Nyamara Abahakanyi baribeshya
  67,21,"Cyangwa se ni nde wabaha amafunguro, (Allah) aramutse ahagaritse amafunguro ye? Ahubwo (abahakanyi) bakomeje kwinangira no kwanga (ukuri)"
  67,22,Ese wawundi ugenda yubitse umutwe (ahuzagurika) ni we wayobotse kurusha wawundi ugenda yemye mu nzira igororotse
  67,23,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"(Allah) ni we wabaremye, abaha ukumva (amatwi), amaso n’imitima (ibafasha gutekereza); ariko mushimira gake"
  67,24,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Ni we wabakwirakwije ku isi, kandi iwe ni ho muzakoranyirizwa"
  67,25,"Baranavuga bati \"Ese iryo sezerano (izuka) rizaba ryari, niba koko muri abanyakuri"
  67,26,"Vuga uti \"Mu by’ukuri, ubumenyi (bw’igihe iryo zuka rizabera) buri kwa Allah, kandi njye ndi umuburizi ugaragara"
  67,27,"Ariko ubwo bazabibona (ibihano byo ku munsi w’imperuka) biri hafi, uburanga bw’abahakanye buzijima bugire agahinda, maze babwirwe bati \"Ngibi ibyo mwajyaga musaba (ngaho byaje)"
  67,28,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Nimumbwire! Allah ashatse kunyoreka njye n’abo turi kumwe (nk’uko mubyifuza) cyangwa akatugirira impuhwe (ibyo ntacyo byabamarira). Ni nde warinda abahakanyi ibihano bibabaza"
  67,29,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Ni we (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe, twaramwemeye kandi ni na we twiringira. Vuba aha muzamenya uri mu buyobe bugaragara (ibihano nibigera)"
  67,30,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Nimumbwire! Amazi yanyu aramutse arigitiye ikuzimu (agakama), ni nde (utari Allah) wabagarurira amazi (y’isoko) atemba"
  68,1,Nuuni139 Ndahiriye ku ikaramu no ku byo (abamalayika n’abantu) bandika
  68,2,"Ku bw’ingabire za Nyagasani wawe (z’ubutumwa wahawe), ntabwo wowe (Muhamadi) uri umusazi"
  68,3,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, uzahabwa ibihembo bidashira (ku bw’ingorane uhura nazo)"
  68,4,"Rwose mu by’ukuri, ufite ubupfura buhambaye"
  68,5,"Bityo, vuba aha uzabona n’abo (abahakanyi) babone"
  68,6,Umusazi muri mwe (uwo ari we)
  68,7,"Mu by’ukuri, Nyagasani wawe ni we uzi neza uwayobye inzira ye, kandi ni na we uzi neza abayobotse"
  68,8,"Bityo, ntukumvire abahinyura"
  68,9,Bifuje ko waborohera (ukabakorera ibyo bashaka) na bo bakakorohera (ntibakurwanye)
  68,10,Kandi ntukumvire buri (muntu) urahira kenshi unasuzuguritse
  68,11,"Umuneguzi wa cyane, unabunza amagambo"
  68,12,"Ubuza ibyiza, urengera, umunyacyaha"
  68,13,"Uw’umutima winangiye, akaba atanazwi inkomoko ye (kwa se)"
  68,14,N’ubwo yaba afite umutungo mwinshi n’urubyaro (rwinshi)
  68,15,"Iyo asomewe amagambo yacu, aravuga ati \"Ni inkuru z’abo hambere"
  68,16,Tuzamushyiraho ikimenyetso ku mutonzi (w’izuru rye)
  68,17,"Mu by’ukuri, (abantu b’i Maka), twarabagerageje nk’uko twagerageje abantu bari bafite umurima ubwo barahiraga ko rwose bawusarura mu rukerera"
  68,18,Ariko ntibavuze In-sha-Allah (Imana nibishaka)
  68,19,"Bityo, ikiza (inkongi y’umuriro) giturutse kwa Nyagasani wawe kirawugota, mu gihe bo bari baryamye"
  68,20,(Umurima wabo) uhinduka nk’uruhira
  68,21,Nuko bucyeye barahamagarana
  68,22,"Bagira bati \"Nimuzindukire mu murima wanyu niba mugikomeje umugambi wo kuwusarura"
  68,23,Nuko bagenda bongorerana
  68,24,Ko uyu munsi nta mukene n’umwe uri buwinjiremo (umurima)
  68,25,Nuko bazinduka bagana (mu murima wabo) biyumvamo ubushobozi
  68,26,"Maze bawubonye baravuga bati \"Mu by’ukuri, twayobye (inzira)"
  68,27,"Ahubwo twimwe (umusaruro wawo, kubera umugambi wacu mubi wo kwima abakene)"
  68,28,"Ushyira mu gaciro muri bo aravuga ati \"Sinari nababwiye ko iyo muza gusingiza (Allah mukanamushimira, mukanavuga muti: In-sha-Allah, mutari guhura n’ibi byago)"
  68,29,"Baravuga bati \"Ubutagatifu ni ubwa Nyagasani wacu, mu by’ukuri twari inkozi z’ibibi"
  68,30,Nuko bamwe batangira guhindukirira abandi (bitana bamwana) bagayana
  68,31,"Baravuga bati \"Mbega ishyano tubonye! Mu by’ukuri, twari abarengera (imbibi za Allah)"
  68,32,Hari ubwo Nyagasani wacu yadushumbusha (umurima) mwiza kuwuruta. Rwose twerekeje ibyifuzo byacu kwa Nyagasani wacu
  68,33,"Uko ni ko ibihano (bya Allah ku isi bimera)! Ariko ibihano byo ku munsi w’imperuka birahambaye cyane, iyaba bari babizi"
  68,34,"Mu by’ukuri, abatinya Allah bazagororerwa Ijuru ryuje ingabire kwa Nyagasani wabo"
  68,35,Ese abicisha bugufi imbere ya Allah (Abayisilamu) twabafata kimwe n’inkozi z’ibibi
  68,36,Ese mwabaye mute? Amahitamo yanyu ashingiye kuki
  68,37,Cyangwa mwaba mufite igitabo mubisomamo (ko abicisha bugufi ari kimwe n’inkozi z’ibibi)
  68,38,"Ese mu by’ukuri, mwaba mufitemo (muri icyo gitabo) ibyo mutoranya"
  68,39,Cyangwa mwaba mufitanye natwe amasezerano ntakuka yo kuzabona ibyo muzifuza kuzageza ku munsi w’imperuka
  68,40,"Babaze (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Ni nde muri bo wabyishingira (akabibera umuhamya)"
  68,41,Cyangwa se (abahakanyi) baba bafite ibigirwamana (bizabafasha ku munsi w’imperuka)? Ngaho nibazane ibyo bigirwamana byabo niba ari abanyakuri
  68,42,"(Ibuka) umunsi (ibintu bizaba bikomeye kandi biteye ubwoba), ubwo igice cyo hepfo cy’ukuguru (kwa Allah) kizagaragarizwa (ibiremwa), nuko (abahakanyi) bagahamagarirwa kubamira (Allah) ariko ntibabishobore"
  68,43,"Bazaba bubitse amaso (kubera ikimwaro), batwikiriwe n’agasuzuguro. Nyamara bajyaga bahamagarirwa kubamira Allah ari bazima (ntibabikore kubera ubwibone)"
  68,44,"Bityo, (yewe Muhamadi) ndekera uwo ari we wese uhinyura iyi nkuru (Qur’an). Rwose (abo bayihinyura) tuzabajyana buhoro buhoro (tubaganisha mu bihano) mu buryo batazi"
  68,45,"Nzanabaha igihe (bibwire ko batazahanwa); mu by’ukuri, imigambi yanjye irakomeye"
  68,46,"Cyangwa bibwira ko (wowe Muhamadi) ubasaba igihembo, none bakaba baremererwa n’ubwishyu"
  68,47,"Cyangwa bibwira ko bazi ibitagaragara, bakaba bandika (ibyo bishakiye, badakeneye ibyo ubabwira)"
  68,48,"Bityo (yewe Muhamadi), ihanganire itegeko rya Nyagasani wawe, kandi ntube nk’umwe wamizwe n’ifi (Umuhanuzi Yunusu) ubwo yadutakambiraga n’agahinda kenshi"
  68,49,"Iyo bitaza kuba ingabire iturutse kwa Nyagasani we yamugezeho, (ifi) yari kumuruka ku musenyi wo ku nkombe kandi akabigayirwa"
  68,50,"Nuko Nyagasani we aramutoranya, maze amushyira mu ntungane"
  68,51,"Kandi iyo abahakanye bumvaga urwibutso (Qur’an), bakurebeshaga indoro ikomeye, bifuza ko wagwa igihunga kugira ngo bavuge bati \"Rwose ni umusazi"
  68,52,Kandi (Qur’an) nta kindi iri cyo usibye kuba ari urwibutso ku biremwa byose
  69,1,Ukuri kudakumirwa (umunsi w’izuka)
  69,2,Ukuri kudakumirwa ni iki
  69,3,Ni iki kizakubwira ukuri kudakumirwa
  69,4,Aba Thamudu n’aba Adi bahinyuye umunsi w’imperuka
  69,5,Aba Thamudu borekeshejwe urusaku ndengakamere
  69,6,"Naho aba Adi borekeshwa umuyaga uvuza ubuhuha, usenya"
  69,7,(Allah) yawubateje mu gihe cy’amajoro arindwi n’amanywa umunani bikurikiranye. Wabonaga abantu ari imirambo irambaraye imeze nk’ingiga z’ibiti by’imitende byaranduwe
  69,8,Ese urabona hari n’umwe wasigaye muri bo
  69,9,Farawo n’ababayeho mbere ye ndetse n’abo mu midugudu yabirinduwe (abantu ba Loti) bakoze ibyaha
  69,10,"Nuko bigomeka ku ntumwa ya Nyagasani wabo, maze (Allah) abahanisha ibihano bikaze"
  69,11,"Mu by’ukuri, ubwo amazi yarengaga inkombe (mu gihe cy’umwuzure wo ku bwa Nuhu, abamwemeye) twabatwaye mu bwato"
  69,12,Kugira ngo tubigire urwibutso kuri mwe ndetse n’amatwi yumva abizirikane
  69,13,Ubwo impanda izavuzwa inshuro imwe (ya mbere)
  69,14,"Isi n’imisozi bigaterurwa, bigahondwa inshuro imwe"
  69,15,"Kuri uwo munsi, imperuka izaba igeze"
  69,16,"N’ikirere kizasatagurika, maze uwo munsi kibe cyoroshye (ku buryo cyakwiyasagura)"
  69,17,N’abamalayika bazaba bakizengurutse (ikirere) impande zacyo. Kandi kuri uwo munsi abamalayika umunani biyongera kuri abo bazaba bahetse intebe y’icyubahiro (Ar’shi) ya Nyagasani wawe
  69,18,Uwo munsi muzagezwa (imbere ya Allah). Nta kintu na kimwe cyanyu kizayoberana
  69,19,"Bityo, uzahabwa igitabo cye mu kuboko kw’iburyo, azavuga (aratira abandi) agira ati \"Nimuze musome igitabo cyanjye"
  69,20,Rwose njye nari nzi neza ko nzahura n’ibarura ryanjye nk’iri (kubera ibikorwa byiza nakoze)
  69,21,Azaba mu buzima bw’umunezero
  69,22,Mu busitani buhebuje
  69,23,Imbuto zabwo zizaba ziri bugufi (yabo)
  69,24,"(Bazabwirwa bati) \"Nimurye munanywe kandi muryoherwe, ibyo ni ukubera ibyo mwakoze mu minsi yahise (mukiri ku isi)"
  69,25,"Naho uzahabwa igitabo cye mu kuboko kw’ibumoso, azavuga (yicuza n’agahinda kenshi) ati \"iyaba ntari mpawe iki gitabo cyanjye"
  69,26,Sinahure n’ibarura ryanjye
  69,27,Iyaba urupfu (rwanjye napfuye mva ku isi) rwari rwo rwa burundu
  69,28,Umutungo wanjye ntacyo wamariye
  69,29,N’ubutware bwanjye bwabaye imfabusa
  69,30,"(Abarinzi b’umuriro bazabwirwa bati) \"Mumufate mumubohe"
  69,31,Maze mumwinjize mu muriro
  69,32,Nyuma mumuboheshe umunyururu ufite uburebure bwa Dhira’a142 mirongo irindwi
  69,33,"Mu by’ukuri, ntiyemeraga Allah w’ikirenga"
  69,34,Nta n’ubwo yajyaga ashishikariza (abantu) kugaburira abakene
  69,35,None uyu munsi nta nshuti ari bugire (yamuvuganira cyangwa ngo imurinde ibihano)
  69,36,Nta n’ibyo kurya (ari buhabwe) uretse amashyira (y’abantu bo mu muriro)
  69,37,Nta bandi (bahabwa) ibyo biribwa uretse abanyabyaha
  69,38,Rwose ndahiriye ku byo mureba
  69,39,N’ibyo mutareba
  69,40,"Mu by’ukuri, iyi (Qur’an) ni ijambo (rya Allah risomwa) n’Intumwa yubahitse (Muhamadi)"
  69,41,Ntabwo ari imvugo y’umusizi. Ariko mwemera gake
  69,42,Nta n’ubwo ari imvugo y’umupfumu. Ariko mwibuka gake
  69,43,(Ahubwo ni igitabo) cyahishuwe giturutse kwa Nyagasani w’ibiremwa
  69,44,N’iyo (Muhamadi) aza kugira ibyo aduhimbira (tutavuze)
  69,45,Twari kumufatisha imbaraga n’ukuboko kw’iburyo
  69,46,"Maze tukamuca umutsi w’ijosi (uva ku mutima, utanga ubuzima)"
  69,47,Nta n’umwe muri mwe wari kugira icyo amumarira (ngo amutabare)
  69,48,Kandi mu by’ukuri (Qur’an) ni urwibutso ku batinya Allah
  69,49,Rwose tuzi neza ko muri mwe hari abahinyura (iyi Qur’an)
  69,50,"Kandi rwose (ku munsi w’imperuka, Qur’an) izaba amakuba ku bahakanyi"
  69,51,Kandi mu by’ukuri (Qur’an) ni ukuri kudashidikanywaho
  69,52,"Bityo, tagatifuza izina rya Nyagasani wawe, Uhambaye"
  70,1,Usaba yisabiye ko ibihano biza
  70,2,(Nyamara ibyo bihano) ntibizagira gikumira ku bahakanyi
  70,3,"(Bizabageraho ku munsi w’imperuka) biturutse kwa Allah, Nyir’ubutagatifu bw’ikirenga"
  70,4,"Abamalayika ndetse na Roho (Malayika Jibrilu) bazamuka iwe (Allah) mu gihe cy’umunsi umwe ungana n’imyaka ibihumbi mirongo itanu (ya hano ku isi, abandi batari bo bakoresha muri urwo rugendo)"
  70,5,"Bityo, ihangane (yewe Muhamadi) wifashishije ukwihangana kwiza"
  70,6,"Mu by’ukuri, bo babona (imperuka) iri kure"
  70,7,Nyamara twe tukabona iri hafi
  70,8,Umunsi ikirere kizaba nk’umushongi w’umuringa
  70,9,N’imisozi ikaba nk’ipamba
  70,10,Kandi nta nshuti izigera ibaza iby’inshuti yayo
  70,11,"N’ubwo bazaba barebana (ndetse bakanamenyana, ariko ntacyo bazamarirana). Kubera ibihano by’uwo munsi, umunyabyaha azifuza gutangaho inshungu abana be"
  70,12,"Umugore we, umuvandimwe we"
  70,13,N’umuryango we yahungiragaho (akiri ku isi igihe ahuye n’ibimuteye ubwoba)
  70,14,Ndetse n’abari mu isi bose (azifuza kubatangaho inshungu) kugira ngo arokoke
  70,15,Ariko ntacyo bizamumarira! Ahubwo bizaba umuriro ugurumana
  70,16,Ukuraho uruhu rw’umubiri
  70,17,Uzaba uhamagara uwo ari we wese wateraga umugongo akanirengagiza (ukuri gukubiye muri Qur’an)
  70,18,Akanakusanya (umutungo) akawuhunika (ntawukoreshe mu nzira ya Allah)
  70,19,"Mu by’ukuri, umuntu yaremanywe ukutihangana"
  70,20,"Iyo ikibi kimugezeho, ariheba cyane"
  70,21,"Naho icyiza cyamugeraho, akaba umunyabugugu cyane"
  70,22,Uretse abakora amasengesho
  70,23,Babandi bahozaho amasengesho yabo
  70,24,Na babandi bagena umugabane uzwi (Zakat) mu mitungo yabo
  70,25,Wagenewe usaba n’uwiyumanganyije (nyamara akeneye ubufasha)
  70,26,Na babandi bemera umunsi w’ibihembo
  70,27,Na babandi batinya ibihano bya Nyagasani wabo
  70,28,"Kubera ko mu by’ukuri, nta n’umwe warokoka ibihano bya Nyagasani wabo"
  70,29,Na babandi barinda ubwambure bwabo (ubusambanyi)
  70,30,"Uretse ku bagore babo cyangwa se ku bo bafiteho ububasha (abaja). Mu by’ukuri, bo ntibabigayirwa"
  70,31,"Ariko abazashaka (kwinezeza) ku batari abo (bavuzwe), rwose abo bazaba batandukiriye"
  70,32,Na babandi barinda ibyo baragijwe ndetse bakubahiriza n’amasezerano yabo
  70,33,Na babandi batanga ubuhamya bw’ukuri
  70,34,Na babandi bahozaho amasengesho yabo (ku bihe byagenwe)
  70,35,Abo bazajya mu busitani (Ijuru) kandi bubashywe
  70,36,"Nonese ni iyihe mpamvu ituma abahakanyi bakugana (yewe Muhamadi) bihuta (bashaka kukumva, kandi batakwemera)"
  70,37,(Bicaye) mu matsinda iburyo n’ibumoso bwawe
  70,38,Ese buri wese muri bo yibwira ko azinjira mu Ijuru ryuje ingabire
  70,39,"Ntabwo ari ko bimeze! Mu by’ukuri, twabaremye tubakomoye mu byo bazi143 (ariko banga kwemera)"
  70,40,"Bityo, ndahiye ku izina rya Nyagasani w’Iburasirazuba bwose n’Iburengerazuba bwose, ko rwose dushoboye"
  70,41,"Kubasimbuza abeza kubarusha, kandi ntibyatunanira"
  70,42,"Bityo, bareke bavuge ibidafite umumaro, banikinire kugeza ubwo bazahura n’umunsi wabo basezeranyijwe"
  70,43,"Umunsi bazasohoka mu mva zabo bihuta, nk’uko bihutaga bagana ibigirwamana byabo"
  70,44,"Bazaba bubitse amaso (kubera ikimwaro), batwikiriwe n’agasuzuguro. Uwo ni wo munsi basezeranyijwe"
  71,1,"Mu by’ukuri, twohereje Nuhu ku bantu be (tugira tuti) \"Burira abantu bawe mbere y’uko ibihano bibabaza bibageraho"
  71,2,"(Nuhu) aravuga ati \"Bantu banjye! Mu by’ukuri, njye ndi umuburizi wanyu ugaragara"
  71,3,"(Ubaburira ko) mugomba kugaragira Allah (wenyine), mumutinye kandi munanyumvire"
  71,4,"(Ibyo nimubikora, Allah) azabababarira ibyaha byanyu, anabahe kubaho kugeza igihe cyagenwe. Mu by’ukuri, iyo igihe ntarengwa (cyo gupfa) Allah yagennye kigeze nticyongerwa, iyaba mwari mubizi"
  71,5,"(Nuhu) aravuga ati \"Nyagasani wanjye! Mu by’ukuri, nahamagariye abantu banjye ijoro n’amanywa (ko bagomba gusenga Imana imwe)"
  71,6,Ariko uguhamagara kwanjye ntacyo kwabongereye uretse guhunga (ukuri)
  71,7,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, buri uko nabahamagariraga (kwemera Imana imwe) kugira ngo ubababarire ibyaha byabo, bashyiraga intoki mu matwi, bakitwikira imyambaro, bagatsimbarara ndetse bakanibona cyane"
  71,8,Hanyuma kandi nabahamagaye ku mugaragaro
  71,9,Hanyuma nanabatangarije (mu ijwi riranguruye) ndetse nanababwira mu ibanga
  71,10,"Narababwiye nti \"Nimusabe imbabazi Nyagasani wanyu, mu by’ukuri ni we uhebuje mu kubabarira ibyaha"
  71,11,(Kugira ngo) azaboherereze imvura nyinshi (ihagije)
  71,12,"Anabongerere imitungo n’urubyaro, abahe ubusitani (Ijuru) ndetse abahe n’imigezi (yaryo)"
  71,13,Kubera iki mudaha Allah icyubahiro kimukwiye
  71,14,Kandi ari we wabaremye mu byiciro (bitandukanye)
  71,15,Ese ntimubona uburyo Allah yaremye ibirere birindwi bigerekeranye
  71,16,Hanyuma akabishyiramo ukwezi akakugira urumuri ndetse n’izuba akarigira itara
  71,17,Kandi Allah yabakujije abakuye mu butaka nk’ibimera
  71,18,Hanyuma azabubasubizamo (igihe cyo gupfa) ndetse anabubasohoremo (ku munsi w’izuka)
  71,19,Kandi Allah ni we wabagiriye isi nk’isaso
  71,20,Kugira ngo muyigendeho (mugendera) mu mayira magari
  71,21,"Nuhu aravuga ati \"Nyagasani wanjye! Mu by’ukuri, (abantu banjye) banyigometseho, banakurikira uwo imitungo n’abana bitagize icyo byongerera uretse igihombo"
  71,22,Nuko (abantu be) bacura umugambi mubi (wo kubangamira ubutumwa bwe)
  71,23,"Baranavuga bati \"Rwose ntimuzareke imana zanyu, kandi ntimuzareke (gusenga) Wadan, Suwa’a, Yagutha, Ya’uqa ndetse na Nasra"
  71,24,"(Nuhu aravuga ati) \"Kandi rwose (ibyo bigirwamana) byayobeje benshi. Bityo (yewe Allah), ntuzagire ikindi wongerera ababangikanyamana kitari ubuyobe"
  71,25,"Kubera ibyaha byabo, baroretswe kandi bazinjizwa mu muriro, ndetse ntibazigera babona ababatabara batari Allah"
  71,26,"Nuhu aravuga ati \"Nyagasani wanjye! Ntuzagire n’umwe muri aba bahakanyi usiga ku isi"
  71,27,"Kuko mu by’ukuri nubareka, bazayobya abagaragu bawe, kandi ntibazigera babyara abandi batari abanyabyaha b’abahakanyi"
  71,28,"(Nuhu aravuga ati) \"Nyagasani wanjye! Mbabarira, njye n’ababyeyi banjye, n’uzinjira mu nzu yanjye ari umwemeramana, ndetse n’abemeramana n’abemeramanakazi. Kandi ntuzagire ikindi wongerera abahakanyi kitari ukorama"
  72,1,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Nahishuriwe ko hari itsinda ry’amajini ryumvise (Qur’an isomwa), nuko rikavuga riti \"Mu by’ukuri, twumvise Qur’an itangaje"
  72,2,"Iyobora iganisha ku kuri, nuko turayemera kandi ntituzigera tubangikanya Nyagasani wacu (Allah) n’icyo ari cyo cyose"
  72,3,"Kandi ko icyubahiro cy’ikirenga ari icya Nyagasani wacu, utarigeze umugore cyangwa umwana"
  72,4,Kandi ko umunyabwenge buke muri twe (Shitani) yajyaga avuga ibidahwitse kuri Allah
  72,5,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, twakekaga ko abantu n’amajini badashobora guhimbira Allah ikinyoma"
  72,6,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, mu bantu hari abagabo bajyaga biyambaza amajini y’igitsinagabo, ariko (ibyo) byongereraga (abo bantu) gukora ibyaha (ndetse n’ayo majini bikayongerera kwibona)"
  72,7,"Kandi ko mu by’ukuri, batekerezaga nk’uko mwatekerezaga ko Allah atazigera agira n’umwe azura"
  72,8,Kandi twagerageje kugera mu kirere dusanga cyuzuye abarinzi bakomeye ndetse n’ibishirira
  72,9,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, twajyaga tuhagira ibyicaro kugira ngo twumvirize (ibivugirwa mu Ijuru), ariko ubu uwagerageza kumviriza yahura n’igishirira kimwubikiriye"
  72,10,"Kandi ntitwigeze tumenya niba hari ikibi giteganyirizwa abari ku isi, cyangwa niba Nyagasani wabo abifuriza icyiza"
  72,11,Kandi ko muri twe hari abakora ibyiza n’abatameze batyo. Turi amatsinda afite amayira (imyizerere) atandukanye
  72,12,"Kandi twizeraga ko tudashobora kunanira Allah (aramutse ashatse kuduhana) ku isi, cyangwa ngo tube twagira aho tumuhungira"
  72,13,"Kandi ko mu by’ukuri, ubwo twumvaga umuyoboro (Qur’an) twarawukurikiye. Kandi uwemeye Nyagasani we, ntatinya kugabanyirizwa (ibihembo bye) cyangwa ngo abe yatinya kongererwa (ibihano)"
  72,14,Kandi ko muri twe hari mo abicishije bugufi (Abayisilamu) n’abatannye. Nyamara abicishije bugufi ni bo bagannye inzira igororotse
  72,15,Naho abatannye bazaba inkwi z’umuriro wa Jahanamu
  72,16,"Kandi ko iyo (abahakanyi) baza kuyoboka inzira igororotse (bakayishikamamo), rwose twari kubaha amazi (imvura) menshi (kandi y’umugisha)"
  72,17,"Kugira ngo tuyabageragereshe. Kandi uzirengagiza urwibutso rwa Nyagasani we, azamuhanisha ibihano bihambaye"
  72,18,"Kandi ko imisigiti yose ari iya Allah (wenyine). Bityo, ntimukagire undi musaba mumubangikanyije na Allah"
  72,19,"Kandi ubwo umugaragu wa Allah (Muhamadi) yahagurukaga amusenga, (amajini) yabaga amuzengurutse (kugira ngo yumve Intumwa isoma Qur’an)"
  72,20,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Mu by’ukuri, njye nsaba Nyagasani wanjye wenyine nta wundi mubangikanyije na we"
  72,21,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Mu by’ukuri, nta bubasha mfite bwo kuba nagira ikibi mbakorera, cyangwa ngo mbe nabayobora (mu nzira igororotse)"
  72,22,"Vuga uti \"Mu by’ukuri, nta n’umwe wandinda (ibihano bya) Allah (ndamutse mwigometseho), ndetse nta n’ahandi nabona ubuhungiro hatari kuri we"
  72,23,"(Umurimo wanjye nta wundi) usibye gusohoza (ukuri) n’ubutumwa biturutse kwa Allah. Ariko uzigomeka kuri Allah n’intumwa ye, azahanishwa umuriro wa Jahanamu azabamo ubuziraherezo"
  72,24,"Kugeza ubwo (ababangikanyamana) bazabona ibyo basezeranyijwe, ni bwo bazamenya ufite abatabazi b’abanyantege nke n’ufite bake"
  72,25,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Sinzi niba (ibihano) musezeranywa biri bugufi cyangwa niba Nyagasani wanjye azabiha igihe kirekire"
  72,26,Ni we (wenyine) mumenyi w’ibitagaragara kandi nta n’umwe ajya ahishurira ibye
  72,27,"Uretse uwo yishimiye mu ntumwa ze, akamwoherereza abarinzi (abamalayika) bamugenda imbere n’inyuma"
  72,28,(Ibyo Allah abikora) kugira ngo amenye ko (Intumwa) zasohoje neza ubutumwa bwa Nyagasani wazo. Kandi (ko Allah) azi neza ibyo zitunze ndetse azi byimazeyo umubare wa buri kintu
  73,1,Yewe uwiyoroshe (uvugwa aha ni Intumwa Muhamadi)
  73,2,"Byuka (usenge) nijoro, uretse igice gito (cyaryo)"
  73,3,Kimwe cya kabiri cyaryo cyangwa igito kuri cyo
  73,4,Cyangwa wongereho gato. Unasome Qur’an neza (mu ijwi rituje kandi ryiza)
  73,5,"Mu by’ukuri, tuzaguhishurira ijambo riremereye (ari ryo Qur’an ikubiyemo amategeko n’amabwiriza)"
  73,6,"Mu by’ukuri, amasengesho y’ijoro ni ingirakamaro (ku mutima) ndetse anatuma (umuntu atekereza ku magambo ya Allah, atuje)"
  73,7,"Mu by’ukuri, ku manywa uba uhugiye muri byinshi"
  73,8,Kandi ujye wibuka izina rya Nyagasani wawe unamwiyegurire utizigama
  73,9,"Nyagasani w’Uburasirazuba n’Uburengerazuba; nta yindi mana ikwiye gusengwa itari we. Bityo, mugire umurinzi (wawe)"
  73,10,"Unihanganire ibyo (abo bahakanyi) bavuga, kandi unabitarure mu buryo bwiza"
  73,11,"Maze undekere abahinyura (amagambo yanjye); bahawe ingabire (yo kubaho mu buzima bwiza), unabarindirize igihe gito"
  73,12,Rwose dufite iminyururu n’umuriro ugurumana (byo kuzabahanisha ku munsi w’imperuka)
  73,13,N’ibyo kurya bizabaniga ndetse n’ibihano bibabaza
  73,14,"Umunsi isi n’imisozi bizatigita, maze imisozi ikaba nk’ikirundo cy’umusenyi wanyanyagijwe"
  73,15,"Mu by’ukuri, twaboherereje Intumwa (Muhamadi) ngo ibabere umuhamya nk’uko twoherereje Farawo Intumwa (Musa)"
  73,16,"Ariko Farawo yigometse ku ntumwa (Musa), nuko turamufata tumuhanisha ibihano bikomeye"
  73,17,Ni gute mwakwirinda ibihano kandi muhakana umunsi uzagira abana abasaza (kubera uko uzaba uteye ubwoba)
  73,18,Ubwo ikirere kizasatagurika. Isezerano rye (Allah) rizasohora nta gushidikanya
  73,19,"Mu by’ukuri, ibi ni urwibutso. Bityo ushaka nayoboke inzira imuganisha kwa Nyagasani we"
  73,20,"Mu by’ukuri, Nyagasani wawe azi ko wowe (Muhamadi) n’itsinda muri kumwe mubyuka mugasenga hafi bibiri bya gatatu by’ijoro, cyangwa icya kabiri cyaryo, cyangwa se icya gatatu cyaryo. Kandi Allah ni we ugena indeshyo y’ijoro n’amanywa. Azi ko mutari gushobora gusenga ijoro ryose, bityo yabagiriye impuhwe (araborohereza). Ku bw’ibyo, mujye musoma ibiboroheye muri Qur’an. Azi ko muri mwe hazabamo abarwayi, abandi bakaba bari mu ngendo bashakisha ingabire za Allah, naho abandi bakazaba bari ku rugamba barwana mu nzira ya Allah. Bityo, mujye musoma ibiboroheye muri yo, muhozeho amasengesho, mutange amaturo, munagurize Allah inguzanyo nziza (mutanga kubera we). Kandi icyiza cyose mwiteganyirije imbere, muzagisanga kwa Allah ari cyiza kurushaho kandi gifite ibihembo bihebuje. Munasabe imbabazi Allah, kuko mu by’ukuri Allah ari Nyirimpuhwe, Nyirimbabazi"
  74,1,Yewe uwitwikiriye (uvugwa aha ni Intumwa Muhamadi)
  74,2,Haguruka uburire (ibiremwa)
  74,3,Unahe ikuzo Nyagasani wawe
  74,4,Unasukure imyambaro yawe
  74,5,Unitarure ibigirwamana
  74,6,Ntukanatange (ikintu) ugamije indonke
  74,7,Kandi ujye wihangana kubera Nyagasani wawe
  74,8,Ubwo impanda izavuzwa
  74,9,Uwo munsi uzaba ari umunsi ukomeye
  74,10,Uzaba utoroheye abahakanyi
  74,11,(Yewe Muhamadi) ndekera uwo naremye ari wenyine (uvugwa aha ni Al Walid bun al Mughirat)
  74,12,Nkamuha imitungo itubutse
  74,13,N’urubyaro rumukikije
  74,14,Nkanamworohereza ubuzima
  74,15,"Nyuma y’ibyo byose, akaba yifuza ko namwongera"
  74,16,"Oya! Mu by’ukuri, yajyaga ahinyura amagambo yacu cyane"
  74,17,Nzamunaniza muhanisha ibihano bikomeye
  74,18,"Mu by’ukuri, yatekereje (ku byo avuga) maze afata umwanzuro (wo gutuka Allah n’Intumwa ye ndetse na Qur’an)"
  74,19,"Bityo, navumwe kubera umwanzuro yafashe"
  74,20,Niyongere avumwe kubera umwanzuro yafashe
  74,21,Nuko (yubura amaso) areba (abari bamukikije)
  74,22,"Maze azinga umunya, akambya agahanga"
  74,23,"Nuko atera umugongo (ukuri), maze aribona"
  74,24,"Aravuga ati \"Ibi (Muhamadi yigisha) nta kindi biri cyo uretse ko ari uburozi (akomora ku barozi bo hambere bakomeye)"
  74,25,Ibi (Muhamadi yigisha) nta kindi biri cyo uretse ko ari amagambo y’umuntu
  74,26,Nzamwinjiza mu muriro
  74,27,N’iki cyakumenyesha uwo muriro
  74,28,Ntacyo ureka ndetse nta n’icyo usigaza
  74,29,Utwika imibiri ukanayishiririza
  74,30,Urinzwe (n’abamalayika) cumi n’icyenda
  74,31,"Kandi nta bandi twagize abarinzi b’umuriro batari abamalayika. Ndetse twanashyizeho umubare wabo (cumi n’icyenda) kugira ngo tugerageze abahakanyi, no kugira ngo abahawe ibitabo bemere badashidikanya (ko Qur’an ari ukuri kuko ihuriye kuri uwo mubare wanditse mu bitabo byabo); ndetse no kugira ngo abemeramana barusheho kwemera, no kugira ngo abahawe igitabo n’abemeramana batagira ugushidikanya (ku byo bemeye), ndetse no kugira ngo abafite uburwayi (bw’uburyarya) mu mitima n’abahakanyi bavuge bati \" Allah yari agamije iki mu gutanga uru rugero?\" Uko ni ko Allah arekera mu buyobe uwo ashatse akanayobora uwo ashatse. Kandi nta wamenya ingabo za Nyagasani wawe utari we. Kandi uyu (muriro) nta kindi uri cyo usibye ko ari urwibutso ku bantu"
  74,32,Oya si ko biri! Ndahiriye ku kwezi
  74,33,No ku ijoro igihe ricyeye
  74,34,No ku gitondo igihe gitangaje
  74,35,"Mu by’ukuri, uwo (muriro) ni kimwe mu (byago) bihambaye"
  74,36,Ukaba n’umuburizi ku bantu
  74,37,K’uwo ari we wese muri mwe ushaka kujya imbere (yiyegereza Nyagasani we) cyangwa gusubira inyuma (amwigomekaho)
  74,38,Buri wese azafungirwa (mu muriro) bitewe n’ibibi yakoze
  74,39,Uretse abantu b’iburyo (b’abemera nyakuri)
  74,40,"Bazaba bari mu busitani (Ijuru), babazanya"
  74,41,"Ku byerekeye inkozi z’ibibi, (maze bazibaze bati)"
  74,42,Ni iki cyabateye kuba muri mu muriro
  74,43,"(Izo nkozi z’ibibi) zizavuga ziti \"Ntitwari bamwe mu basenga"
  74,44,Nta n’ubwo twajyaga tugaburira abakene
  74,45,Kandi twajyaga tugirana ibiganiro n’abavuga ibidafite umumaro
  74,46,Ndetse twajyaga duhinyura umunsi w’ibihembo (imperuka)
  74,47,Kugeza ubwo ukuri kudashidikanywaho (urupfu) kutugezeho
  74,48,"Bityo, nta buvugizi bw’abavugizi buzagira icyo bubamarira"
  74,49,Nonese ni iyihe mpamvu ituma (abahakanyi) batera umugongo urwibutso
  74,50,Bameze nk’imparage ziruka (zifite ubwoba)
  74,51,Zihunga intare
  74,52,Ahubwo buri wese muri bo aba ashaka ko yahishurirwa ibitabo birambuye (bishimangira ko Isilamu ari idini ry’ukuri)
  74,53,Oya si ko biri! Ahubwo ntibatinya umunsi w’imperuka
  74,54,"Oya si ko biri! Mu by’ukuri, iyi (Qur’an) ni urwibutso"
  74,55,"Bityo, ushaka (ko imubera urwibutso) nayibuke (ayisoma, anatekereza ku nyigisho ziyikubiyemo)"
  74,56,"Kandi ntibashobora kwibuka keretse Allah abishatse. Ni we ukwiriye gutinywa, ndetse ni na we utanga imbabazi"
  75,1,Ndahiriye ku munsi w’izuka
  75,2,Nanarahiriye ku mutima (w’umwemeramana) ugaya nyirawo (kubera guteshuka ku nzira igororotse)
  75,3,Ese umuntu (w’umuhakanyi) akeka ko tutazashobora gukoranya amagufa ye (tumuzura)
  75,4,Nibyo! Dushoboye no kuringaniza imitwe y’intoki ze (imirongo iyiriho igasubira nk’uko yari imeze mbere)
  75,5,Ahubwo umuntu (ahakana izuka) ashaka icyatuma akomeza kwibera mu bwangizi
  75,6,"Arabaza (akerensa) ati \"Uwo munsi w’izuka uzaba ryari"
  75,7,(Uwo munsi uzaba) igihe amaso azakanaguzwa (kubera ubwoba)
  75,8,N’ukwezi kukazima
  75,9,Ndetse izuba n’ukwezi bizahurizwa hamwe (kimwe kinjire mu kindi)
  75,10,"Icyo gihe umuntu azavuga ati \"Ni he ho guhungira"
  75,11,"(Azabwirwa ati) \"Oya! Ntaho guhungira hahari"
  75,12,"Kuri uwo munsi, igarukiro rizaba ari kwa Nyagasani wawe (wenyine)"
  75,13,"Kuri uwo munsi, umuntu azabwirwa ibyo yakoze mbere n’ibyo yaherutse (byaba ibyiza cyangwa ibibi)"
  75,14,Ahubwo umuntu azibera umuhamya w’ibyo yakoze (kuko ingingo z’umubiri we ari zo zizamushinja ibyo yakoze)
  75,15,Kabone n’ubwo yatanga impamvu ze (agamije kwiregura)
  75,16,"(Yewe Muhamadi), ntukanyeganyeze ururimi rwawe ugira ubwira (bwo kuvuga ibyo uhishurirwa, ahubwo ujye utega amatwi wumve ibyo uba uhishurirwa na Malayika Jiburilu)"
  75,17,"Mu by’ukuri, ni twe tuzayikusanyiriza (mu gituza cyawe) kandi ni natwe (tuzakwigisha) kuyisoma (Qur’an)"
  75,18,"Nituyigusomera (binyuze kuri Malayika wacu), ujye ukurikira isomwa ryayo"
  75,19,Hanyuma ni twe (Allah) tuzayigusobanurira
  75,20,(Ibyo mukeka ko mutazazurwa mukanabazwa ibyo mwakoze) si ko biri; ahubwo mukunda ubuzima bwo ku isi butaramba
  75,21,Mukirengagiza imperuka
  75,22,"Kuri uwo munsi, uburanga (bw’abemeramana) buzaba burabagirana"
  75,23,Bureba Nyagasani wabwo
  75,24,"Kuri uwo munsi kandi, uburanga (bw’abahakanyi) buzaba bwijimye"
  75,25,Bibaza ko bagiye guhura n’ishyano
  75,26,Oya! Ahubwo iyo (roho) igeze mu ngoto (igihe cyo gupfa)
  75,27,"Hanyuma hakavugwa ngo \"Ni nde wamutabara (akamurinda urupfu)"
  75,28,Nuko (ugiye gupfa) akamenya ko igihe cyo gutandukana (gupfa) cyageze
  75,29,"Maze (kubera ububabare bwo gukurwamo roho), ukuguru kwe kuzahuzwa n’ukundi"
  75,30,"Kuri uwo munsi, (wowe muntu ukuwemo roho) uzerekezwa kwa Nyagasani wawe"
  75,31,Ariko (umuhakanyi) ntiyigeze yemera ndetse nta n’ubwo yigeze asenga
  75,32,Ahubwo yahinyuye (Qur’an) maze ayitera umugongo
  75,33,Hanyuma akagenda yibona yerekeza mu muryango we
  75,34,Ufite akaga (yewe muntu w’umuhakanyi)! Kandi nanone ufite akaga
  75,35,Nanone ufite akaga (yewe muntu w’umuhakanyi)! Kandi nanone ufite akaga
  75,36,Ese umuntu yibwira ko azarekwa gusa (atabajijwe ibyo yakoze ngo abihemberwe cyangwa ngo abihanirwe)
  75,37,Ese ntiyari intanga zisohorwa
  75,38,"Hanyuma akaba urusoro rw’amaraso, maze Allah akamurema, akanamutunganya (akaba umuntu wuzuye)"
  75,39,"Maze akamuremamo ibitsina bibiri: ikigabo n’ikigore"
  75,40,Ese uwo (Allah ukora ibyo) si we ushoboye kuzura abapfuye
  76,1,Ese nta gihe kirekire cyabayeho umuntu ari ikintu kitazwi
  76,2,"Mu by’ukuri, twaremye umuntu mu ntanga zivanze (iz’umugabo n’iz’umugore) kugira ngo tumugerageze. (Ni yo mpamvu) twamuhaye kumva no kubona"
  76,3,"Mu by’ukuri, twamweretse inzira; abishatse (yahitamo kwemera) agashimira cyangwa agahakana"
  76,4,"Mu by’ukuri, abahakanyi twabateguriye (kuzabahanisha) iminyururu, ingoyi ndetse n’umuriro ugurumana"
  76,5,"Mu by’ukuri, abakiranutsi bazanywera mu kirahuri (cya divayi idasindisha) ivanze (n’amazi y’isoko y’umugezi wo mu ijuru witwa) Kafuur"
  76,6,"(Iyo Kafuur) ni isoko y’amazi abagaragu ba Allah bazanywaho, ikazajya ivubura amazi menshi (bakayerekeza aho bashatse)"
  76,7,"(Abo bakiranutsi) ni abesa imihigo (yabo bahigiye Allah), bakanatinya umunsi ikibi cyazakwira hose (umunsi w’imperuka)"
  76,8,"Bakanaha amafunguro abakene, imfubyi n’imbohe, kabone n’iyo nabo baba bayakeneye"
  76,9,"(Bavuga bati) \"Rwose, turabagaburira kubera gushaka kwishimirwa na Allah. Nta nyiturano cyangwa ishimwe tubashakaho"
  76,10,"Rwose dutinya umunsi ukomeye kandi uzaba urimo ingorane, uturutse kwa Nyagasani wacu, uzatuma (uburanga bw’abahakanyi) bwijima"
  76,11,"Bityo, Allah azabarinda ibibi by’uwo munsi, kandi azabaha umucyo (mu buranga) ndetse n’ibyishimo"
  76,12,Azanabagororera ijuru n’imyambaro y’ihariri kubera ko barangwaga no kwihangana
  76,13,"Bazaba begamye ku bitanda bitatse, (kandi mu Ijuru) ntibazigera bahabona ubushyuhe bw’izuba cyangwa imbeho bikabije"
  76,14,"Kandi igicucu (cy’ibiti byo mu ijuru) kizaba kibegereye, ndetse n’imbuto zabyo zizabegerezwa"
  76,15,Bazazengurutswamo amasahane ya Feza (arimo ibiribwa byiza) n’ibikombe bikozwe mu birahuri
  76,16,"Ibirahuri bikoze muri Feza, byuzuye neza (bijyanye n’ibyifuzo bya buri wese)"
  76,17,Bazanahabwa ikirahuri (cya divayi idasindisha) ivanze na tangawizi
  76,18,Izavomwa mu isoko ryitwa Salisabila
  76,19,"Bazaba bazengurukwamo n’abana b’abahungu bahoraho (badasaza cyangwa ngo bapfe, babaha amafunguro), ubabonye wagira ngo ni inigi zishashagirana (Lu’ulu’u) zanyanyagijwe"
  76,20,Kandi nunarebayo (mu Ijuru) uzabona ingabire (zitagereranywa) ndetse n’ubwami buhebuje
  76,21,Bazaba bambaye imyambaro y’icyatsi kibitsi ikoze mu ihariri yorohereye n’iremereye. Bazanambikirwamo ibikomo bya Feza kandi Nyagasani wabo azabaha ikinyobwa gisukuye
  76,22,"(Bazanabwirwa bati) \"Mu by’ukuri, ibi ni ibihembo byanyu, kandi umuhate wanyu warakiriwe"
  76,23,"Mu by’ukuri, (yewe Muhamadi) ni twe twaguhishuriye Qur’an mu byiciro"
  76,24,"Bityo, ihanganire itegeko rya Nyagasani wawe, kandi ntuzumvire umunyabyaha cyangwa umuhakanyi muri bo"
  76,25,Kandi ujye wibuka izina rya Nyagasani wawe mu gitondo no ku gicamunsi
  76,26,Na nijoro umwubamire kandi unamusingize igihe kirekire mu ijoro
  76,27,"Mu by’ukuri, abo (bahakanyi) bakunda ubuzima bwo ku isi butaramba, bakirengagiza umunsi uremereye (w’ibihano)"
  76,28,Ni twe twabaremye dukomeza ingingo zabo. Kandi tubishatse twabasimbuza abandi bameze nka bo
  76,29,"Mu by’ukuri, iyi (mirongo ya Qur’an) ni urwibutso, bityo ushaka nayoboke inzira imuganisha kwa Nyagasani we"
  76,30,"Kandi ntacyo mwashaka (ngo mukigereho) keretse Allah abishatse. Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Umumenyi uhebuje, Ushishoza"
  76,31,Yinjiza mu mpuhwe ze uwo ashatse. Naho inkozi z’ibibi yaziteguriye ibihano bibabaza
  77,1,Ndahiriye ku (miyaga) yoherezwa ikurikiranye
  77,2,No ku (miyaga) y’inkubi
  77,3,No ku (miyaga) itwara ibicu n’imvura
  77,4,No ku (mirongo ya Qur’an) itandukanya ukuri n’ikinyoma
  77,5,No ku (bamalayika) bazanira amahishurirwa (intumwa za Allah)
  77,6,Kugira ngo bivaneho urwitwazo cyangwa kugira ngo biburire
  77,7,"Mu by’ukuri, ibyo musezeranywa bizasohora"
  77,8,Igihe inyenyeri zizakurwaho (urumuri rwazo rukazima)
  77,9,N’igihe ikirere kizasandazwa
  77,10,N’igihe imisozi izariturwa
  77,11,N’igihe intumwa zizakoranyirizwa hamwe ku gihe cyagenwe (kugira ngo zitange ubuhamya ku bo zatumweho)
  77,12,Ni uwuhe munsi (ibyo byose) byarindirijwe
  77,13,Ni ku munsi w’urubanza (ubwo Allah azakiranura ibiremwa)
  77,14,Ni iki cyakumenyesha umunsi w’urubanza
  77,15,Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri babandi bahinyura (umunsi w’izuka)
  77,16,Ese ntitworetse abo hambere
  77,17,Nuko tukabakurikiza abo hanyuma
  77,18,Uko ni ko tugenza inkozi z’ibibi
  77,19,Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri babandi bahinyura (umunsi w’izuka)
  77,20,Ese ntitwabaremye mu mazi asuzuguritse
  77,21,Nuko tukayashyira mu cyicaro gitekanye (nyababyeyi)
  77,22,Kugeza igihe kizwi
  77,23,Nuko tukagena (igihe umwana avukira) kandi ni twe duhebuje mu kugena
  77,24,Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri babandi bahinyura (umunsi w’izuka)
  77,25,Ese isi ntitwayigize ihuriro
  77,26,Ry’abazima (bayituyeho) n’abapfuye (bayishyinguwemo)
  77,27,"Hanyuma tukanayishyiramo imisozi miremire, ndetse tukabaha n’amazi y’urubogobogo"
  77,28,Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri babandi bahinyura (umunsi w’izuka)
  77,29,"(Abahakanyi bazabwirwa bati) \"Ngaho nimujye (mu muriro wa Jahanamu) mwajyaga muhinyura"
  77,30,Ngaho nimujye mu gicucu (cy’umwotsi wa Jahanamu) kigabanyijemo amashami atatu
  77,31,Nta bwugamo gitanga ndetse nta n’ubwo kirinda ikibatsi cy’umuriro
  77,32,"Mu by’ukuri, (uwo muriro) utera ibishashi bingana n’inyubako nini"
  77,33,(Ibyo bishashi) bimeze nk’ingamiya z’amagaju
  77,34,Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri babandi bahinyura (umunsi w’izuka)
  77,35,Uwo uzaba ari umunsi (batazashobora kugira) icyo bavuga
  77,36,Kandi nta n’uburenganzira bazahabwa bwo kugira urwitwazo batanga
  77,37,Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri babandi bahinyura (umunsi w’izuka)
  77,38,"Uwo uzaba ari umunsi w’urubanza, ubwo (mwe) n’abo hambere tuzaba twabakoranyirije hamwe"
  77,39,"Niba hari amayeri mufite (yo guhunga ibihano byanjye), ngaho nimuyankorere"
  77,40,Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri babandi bahinyura (umunsi w’izuka)
  77,41,"Mu by’ukuri, abatinya Allah (ku munsi w’imperuka) bazaba bari hagati y’ibicucu (by’ibiti byo mu ijuru) ndetse n’amasoko (atemba)"
  77,42,(Bazaba bafitemo) n’imbuto (z’amoko anyuranye) bazajya bifuza
  77,43,"(Bazabwirwa bati) \"Nimurye, munywe kandi mugubwe neza kubera ibyo mwakoze"
  77,44,"Mu by’ukuri, uko ni ko tugororera abakoze neza"
  77,45,Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri babandi bahinyura (umunsi w’izuka)
  77,46,"(Yemwe bahakanyi) \"Nimurye munishimishe by’igihe gito (mu buzima bwo ku isi), kuko rwose muri inkozi z’ibibi"
  77,47,Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri babandi bahinyura (umunsi w’izuka)
  77,48,"N’iyo babwiwe bati \"Nimwuname (musenge)!\" Ntabwo bunama (ngo basenge)"
  77,49,Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri babandi bahinyura (umunsi w’izuka)
  77,50,Nonese nyuma y’iyi (Qur’an) ni ayahe magambo yandi bazemera
  78,1,Ni iki (abahakanyi b’abakurayishi) babazanyaho
  78,2,Ku nkuru ihambaye (Qur’an n’umunsi w’imperuka)
  78,3,(Iyo nkuru) batavugaho rumwe (hagati y’abayemera n’abayihakana)
  78,4,Oya! Rwose bidatinze bazamenya
  78,5,Oya nanone! Bidatinze bazamenya
  78,6,Ese isi ntitwayigize nk’isaso
  78,7,N’imisozi tukayigira nk’imambo
  78,8,Tukanabarema muri ibitsina byombi (ikigabo n’ikigore)
  78,9,Kandi ibitotsi byanyu twabigize uburyo bw’ikiruhuko
  78,10,N’ijoro turigira nk’umwambaro (binyuze mu mwijima waryo)
  78,11,N’amanywa tuyagira ayo gushakiramo imibereho
  78,12,Tunubaka hejuru yanyu (ibirere) birindwi bikomeye
  78,13,Ndetse n’(izuba) turigira itara rimurika
  78,14,Tunamanura mu bicu amazi menshi yisuka
  78,15,Kugira ngo tuyereshe impeke n’ibimera
  78,16,N’imirima y’ibiti byegeranye
  78,17,"Mu by’ukuri, umunsi w’urubanza ufite igihe ntarengwa"
  78,18,"Umunsi impanda izavuzwa, maze mukaza muri amatsinda"
  78,19,N’ikirere kizakingurwa maze gihinduke nk’amarembo
  78,20,"N’imisozi izakurwa mu myanya yayo, imere nk’ibirorirori"
  78,21,"Mu by’ukuri, umuriro wa Jahanamu urarekereje"
  78,22,Ni wo garukiro ry’ibyigomeke
  78,23,Bizawubamo imyaka n’imyaniko
  78,24,(Ibyo byigomeke) ntibizawusogongereramo ubukonje cyangwa ikinyobwa
  78,25,Uretse amazi yatuye n’amashyira
  78,26,(Ibyo bikazaba) ari igihembo gikwiye (ibikorwa bibi bakoraga)
  78,27,"Kuko mu by’ukuri, batajyaga bizera ibarura"
  78,28,Ndetse banahinyuraga amagambo yacu cyane
  78,29,Kandi byose twarabibaruye mu nyandiko
  78,30,"Ngaho nimusogongere (ingaruka z’ibikorwa byanyu bibi), kandi nta kindi tubongerera usibye ibihano"
  78,31,"Mu by’ukuri, abatinya Allah bazabona intsinzi (Ijuru)"
  78,32,Ubusitani n’imizabibu
  78,33,N’inkumi z’urungano (Huur-ul Ayn)
  78,34,Ndetse n’ibirahuri byuzuye (divayi idasindisha)
  78,35,Nta magambo adafite umumaro cyangwa ikinyoma bazumviramo
  78,36,(Ibyo bizaba) ari ibihembo biturutse kwa Nyagasani wawe; impano ijyanye (n’ibikorwa byabo)
  78,37,"Nyagasani w’ibirere n’isi n’ibiri hagati yabyo, Nyirimpuhwe. (Ku munsi w’imperuka), nta bushobozi bwo kugira icyo bamuvugisha bazaba bafite (keretse abishatse)"
  78,38,"Umunsi Roho (Malayika Jiburilu) n’abandi bamalayika bazahagarara ku murongo, ntibazavuga keretse uwo (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe azabihera uburenganzira, kandi akavuga ibiri ukuri"
  78,39,"Uwo munsi ni ukuri (uzaza nta gushidikanya). Bityo, ubishaka yakwiteganyiriza kwa Nyagasani we aho azashyikira"
  78,40,"Mu by’ukuri, twababuriye ibihano byegereje; umunsi umuntu azabona ibyo yakoze, naho umuhakanyi akazavuga ati \"Iyaba nari mbaye igitaka"
  79,1,Ndahiriye ku (bamalayika) bashikanuza (roho z’abahakanyi) n’ubukana buhambaye
  79,2,No ku (bamalayika) bakuramo (roho z’abemeramana) bitonze
  79,3,No ku (bamalayika) bogoga ikirere bihuta (batwaye izo roho)
  79,4,No ku (bamalayika) bihutana (ubutumwa babuzaniye intumwa za Allah ku isi)
  79,5,No ku (bamalayika) bashyira mu bikorwa ibyo bategetswe
  79,6,"Umunsi (impanda ya mbere izavuzwa), maze isi n’imisozi bigatigita bikabije (buri kiremwa kigapfa)"
  79,7,(Umutingito wa mbere) uzakurikirwa n’undi mutingito (maze buri kiremwa kizuke)
  79,8,Uwo munsi imitima (ya bamwe) izaba ifite ubwoba n’agahinda
  79,9,Ndetse n’indoro yabo izaba yaciye bugufi (isuzuguritse)
  79,10,"Bazavuga bati \"Ese mu by’ukuri, tuzasubizwa mu buzima (bwacu bwo ku isi) twahozemo"
  79,11,Na nyuma y’uko tubaye amagufa ashangutse
  79,12,"Baravuga bati \"Uko kugaruka kwacu (ku isi twifuza) kwaba ari igihombo"
  79,13,(Ubwo impanda izavuzwa bwa kabiri) bizaba ari urusaku rumwe
  79,14,Icyo gihe bazisanga imusozi (bongeye kuba bazima nyuma yo gupfa)
  79,15,Ese inkuru ya Musa yakugezeho
  79,16,Ubwo Nyagasani we yamuhamagaraga mu kibaya gitagatifu cya Tuwa (agira ati)
  79,17,Jya kwa Farawo kuko rwose yigometse
  79,18,"Umubwire uti \"Ese ushobora kwiyeza (ukareka icyaha cy’ubuhakanyi, ukaba umwemeramana)"
  79,19,Nkakuyobora kwa Nyagasani wawe kugira ngo umutinye
  79,20,Nuko (Musa) amwereka igitangaza gihambaye
  79,21,Ariko (Farawo) yarahinyuye aranigomeka
  79,22,Maze atera umugongo akataza (ashishikariza abantu be kudakurikira Musa)
  79,23,"Nuko akoranya (abantu be), avuga mu ijwi riranguruye"
  79,24,"Agira ati \"Ni njye nyagasani wanyu w’ikirenga"
  79,25,"Bityo, Allah amuhanira icyaha cya nyuma (cyo kuvuga ko ari we nyagasani w’ikirenga) n’icya mbere (cyo kuba yarabwiye ibyegera bye ko atazi ko bafite indi mana itari we)"
  79,26,"Mu by’ukuri, muri ibyo harimo isomo kuri buri wese utinya Allah"
  79,27,"Ese (yemwe bantu) iremwa ryanyu ni ryo rikomeye, cyangwa ikirere (Allah) yubatse (ni cyo gikomeye)"
  79,28,"Yazamuye igisenge cyacyo, maze aragitunganya"
  79,29,"Ijoro ryacyo arigira umwijima, amanywa yacyo arayakesha"
  79,30,Nyuma y’ibyo arambura isi
  79,31,Ayisohoramo amazi yayo n’inzuri zayo
  79,32,Anashimangira imisozi
  79,33,"Kugira ngo bibagirire akamaro, mwe n’amatungo yanyu"
  79,34,Ariko igihe icyago gihambaye (umunsi w’imperuka) kizaza
  79,35,Umunsi umuntu azibuka ibyo yakoze
  79,36,Umuriro wa Jahanamu uzagaragarizwa (buri wese) ureba
  79,37,Ubwo kuri wa wundi wigometse
  79,38,Agahitamo ubuzima bwo kuri iyi si (agakurikira ibibi aterwa n’irari rye)
  79,39,"Mu by’ukuri, umuriro wa Jahanamu uzaba ubuturo (bwe)"
  79,40,"Ariko wa wundi watinye kuzahagarara imbere ya Nyagasani we, akanabuza umutima we kurarikira ibibi"
  79,41,"Mu by’ukuri, Ubusitani (Ijuru) buzaba ubuturo (bwe)"
  79,42,(Abahakanyi) barakubaza (yewe Muhamadi) ku bijyanye n’igihe imperuka izabera
  79,43,Nta bumenyi ufite bwo kugira icyo uyivugaho
  79,44,Ubumenyi bwayo bwihariye Nyagasani wawe
  79,45,Ahubwo wowe (Muhamadi) nta kindi uri cyo uretse kuba uri umuburizi w’abatinya (umunsi w’imperuka)
  79,46,"Umunsi bazawubona, bazamera nk’aho babaye ku isi ikigoroba kimwe cyangwa igitondo kimwe"
  80,1,(Intumwa Muhamadi) yazinze umunya inatera umugongo
  80,2,Ubwo umuntu utabona (Abdullah bin Umm-Maktum) yari aje ayisanga (igihe yigishaga bamwe mu bikomerezwa by’Abakurayishi)
  80,3,Nonese ni iki cyakumenyesha ko yaba (aje kubaza) ashaka kwiyeza (ibyaha)
  80,4,"Cyangwa akakira urwibutso, hanyuma urwibutso rukamugirira akamaro"
  80,5,Naho wawundi wirata yumva ko adakeneye (kuyoboka)
  80,6,Ni we witaho
  80,7,"Kandi ntacyo wabazwa aramutse atiyejeje (ngo ave mu buhakanyi, kuko wowe icyo ushinzwe ari ugusohoza ubutumwa bwa Allah gusa)"
  80,8,Ariko wawundi uje akugana yihuta
  80,9,Kandi akaba atinya (Allah n’ibihano bye)
  80,10,Uramwirengagiza (ukita ku bandi)
  80,11,Oya ntibikwiye! Mu by’ukuri (iyi Qur’an) ni urwibutso
  80,12,"Bityo, ubishaka nayizirikane"
  80,13,(Iri) mu nyandiko zirinzwe mu cyubahiro (Lawuhu Mahfudh)
  80,14,Zubahitse kandi zejejwe
  80,15,Ziri mu maboko y’abanditsi (abamalayika)
  80,16,B’abanyacyubahiro kandi b’inyangamugayo
  80,17,Umuntu (w’umuhakanyi) navumwe! Mbega ukuntu ari umuhakanyi
  80,18,Ese (Allah) yamuremye mu ki
  80,19,"Yamuremye mu ntanga, arangije amugenera uko azabaho"
  80,20,Nuko amworohereza inzira (y’imibereho ye)
  80,21,Nyuma amugenera urupfu no gushyingurwa
  80,22,Kandi igihe azabishakira azamuzura
  80,23,Oya! Nyamara (umuntu) ntarakora ibyo yamutegetse
  80,24,Ngaho umuntu niyitegereze amafunguro ye
  80,25,Uko tumanura amazi (mu kirere) yisuka ari menshi
  80,26,Nuko tugasatura ubutaka uko bikwiye (kugira ngo amazi abashe kubwinjiramo)
  80,27,Maze tukabumezamo impeke
  80,28,N’imizabibu n’imboga
  80,29,N’imizeti n’imitende
  80,30,N’imirima igizwe n’ibiti by’inzitane
  80,31,N’imbuto n’ubwatsi
  80,32,"Kugira ngo bibagirire akamaro, mwe n’amatungo yanyu"
  80,33,Ariko ubwo urusaku ruziba amatwi (impanda y’imperuka) ruzaza
  80,34,Uwo munsi umuntu azahunga umuvandimwe we
  80,35,(Ahunge) nyina na se
  80,36,N’umugore we n’abana be
  80,37,"Kuri uwo munsi, buri muntu azaba afite ibimuhangayikishije (bituma atita ku bandi)"
  80,38,"Kuri uwo munsi, uburanga (bw’abemeramana) buzaba bwererana"
  80,39,"Bamwenyura, bishimiye inkuru nziza bahawe (y’Ijuru)"
  80,40,Naho uburanga (bw’abahakanyi) kuri uwo munsi buzaba bwuzuye umukungugu
  80,41,Bwarenzwe n’umwijima
  80,42,Abo ni bo bahakanyi b’inkozi z’ibibi
  81,1,Igihe izuba rizazingazingwa (urumuri rwaryo rukazimira)
  81,2,N’igihe inyenyeri zizazima
  81,3,N’igihe imisozi izakurwa mu myanya yayo
  81,4,N’igihe ingamiya z’imbyeyi zizarekwa (ntizitabweho)
  81,5,N’igihe inyamaswa z’inkanzi zizakoranyirizwa hamwe
  81,6,N’igihe inyanja zizaka umuriro
  81,7,N’igihe roho zizasubizwa mu mibiri yazo (abeza bakajya ukwabo n’ababi bakajya ukwabo)
  81,8,N’igihe umwana w’umukobwa wahambwe ari muzima azabazwa
  81,9,Icyaha yakoze cyatumye yicwa
  81,10,N’igihe ibitabo (bikubiyemo ibikorwa byiza n’ibibi bya buri muntu) bizaramburwa
  81,11,N’igihe ikirere kizakurwaho
  81,12,N’igihe umuriro wa Jahanamu uzenyegezwa
  81,13,N’igihe Ijuru rizegerezwa hafi
  81,14,Icyo gihe buri muntu azamenya ibyo yakoze
  81,15,"Bityo, ndahiriye ku nyenyeri zitagaragara ku manywa zikongera kugaragara nijoro"
  81,16,Zigenda zihuta kandi zikanihisha
  81,17,Nanarahiriye ku ijoro igihe riguye
  81,18,No ku gitondo igihe gitangaje
  81,19,"Mu by’ukuri, (Qur’an) ni ijambo ryazanywe n’Intumwa yubahitse [(Malayika Jibrilu), (riturutse kwa Allah)"
  81,20,"(Iyo ntumwa) ifite imbaraga (yahawe na Allah), Nyagasani w’intebe y’icyubahiro"
  81,21,Yumvirwa (n’abamalayika mu birere) kandi ikaba yizewe (kwa Allah)
  81,22,Kandi (yemwe bahakanyi) mugenzi wanyu (Intumwa Muhamadi ibakomokamo) si umusazi
  81,23,Kandi rwose yabonye (Malayika Jibrilu) ari mu kirere gikeye
  81,24,Kandi (Intumwa Muhamadi) ntigundira ibyo yahishuriwe (ngo ireke kubyigisha abantu)
  81,25,Kandi (Qur’an) si ijambo rya Shitani wavumwe
  81,26,Nonese muragana he
  81,27,"Mu by’ukuri, iyi (Qur’an) nta kindi iri cyo usibye kuba ari urwibutso ku biremwa (byose)"
  81,28,Kuri wawundi muri mwe ushaka gukurikira inzira igororotse
  81,29,"Kandi nta cyo mwashaka (ngo kibe) keretse Allah, Nyagasani w’ibiremwa (byose) aramutse agishatse"
  82,1,Igihe ikirere kizasatagurika
  82,2,N’igihe inyenyeri zizagwa zikanyanyagira
  82,3,N’igihe inyanja zizuzura (amazi yazo akarenga inkombe)
  82,4,N’igihe imva zizabirindurwa (zigakurwamo ibizirimo)
  82,5,(Icyo gihe) umuntu azamenya ibyo yakoze mbere n’ibyo yaherutse (byaba ibyiza cyangwa ibibi)
  82,6,"Yewe muntu! N’iki cyaguteye kwirengagiza Nyagasani wawe, Nyirubutagatifu"
  82,7,We wakuremye akagutunganya ndetse akanaguha imiterere igukwiye
  82,8,Yaragutunganyije aguha ishusho ashatse
  82,9,Oya! Nyamara muhakana umunsi w’ibihembo
  82,10,"Ariko mu by’ukuri, mufite (abamalayika babashinzwe) babagenzura"
  82,11,Bubashywe kandi bandika (ibikorwa byanyu byiza n’ibibi)
  82,12,Bazi ibyo mukora byose
  82,13,"Mu by’ukuri, abakora ibyiza bazaba mu munezero uhambaye (Ijuru)"
  82,14,Naho abangizi bazaba mu muriro ugurumana
  82,15,Bazawinjiramo ku munsi w’ibihembo
  82,16,Kandi ntibazigera bawuvamo
  82,17,Nonese ni iki kizakumenyesha umunsi w’ibihembo
  82,18,"Nanone, ni iki kizakumenyesha umunsi w’ibihembo"
  82,19,"(Uzaba) ari umunsi umuntu atazagira icyo amarira undi, kandi kuri uwo munsi itegeko ryose rizaba ari irya Allah"
  83,1,Ibihano bikomeye bizahanishwa abatuzuza ibipimo
  83,2,"Babandi igihe bapimiwe (n’abandi) bantu, basaba kuzurizwa ibipimo"
  83,3,"Nyamara bo bapimira (abandi), bakabaha ibituzuye"
  83,4,Ese bakeka ko batazazurwa (ngo babazwe)
  83,5,Ku munsi uhambaye
  83,6,Umunsi abantu (bose) bazahagarara imbere ya Nyagasani w’ibiremwa
  83,7,"Oya! Mu by’ukuri, igitabo (cyanditsemo ibikorwa) by’inkozi z’ibibi gishyinguwe mu bubiko bwabugenewe bwitwa Sijiini"
  83,8,Nonese ni iki cyakumenyesha Sijiini
  83,9,Ni igitabo cyanditse mu buryo bunoze kandi budasibama
  83,10,Uwo munsi ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri babandi bahinyura
  83,11,Babandi bahinyura umunsi w’ibihembo
  83,12,Kandi nta wundi wawuhakana usibye urengera (imbibi za Allah) w’umunyabyaha
  83,13,"(Wawundi) usomerwa amagambo yacu (yo muri Qur’an) akavuga ati \"Ni inkuru z’abo hambere"
  83,14,Oya! Ahubwo ibyo bakoraga (ibyaha) byatwikiriye imitima yabo
  83,15,"Oya! Mu by’ukuri, kuri uwo munsi bazabuzwa kureba Nyagasani wabo"
  83,16,Maze binjire mu muriro ugurumana
  83,17,"Nuko babwirwe bati \"Ibi ni byo mwajyaga muhinyura"
  83,18,"Oya! Mu by’ukuri, igitabo (cyanditsemo ibikorwa) by’abakora ibyiza gishyinguwe mu bubiko bwabugenewe bwitwa Iliyuna"
  83,19,Nonese ni iki cyakumenyesha Iliyuna
  83,20,Ni igitabo cyanditse mu buryo bunoze kandi budasibama
  83,21,(Abamalayika) begereye Allah ni bo bazakibera abahamya
  83,22,"Mu by’ukuri, abakora ibyiza bazaba mu munezero uhambaye (Ijuru)"
  83,23,"Bicaye ku bitanda byiza, bitegereza (ibyiza barimo)"
  83,24,Mu buranga bwabo uzahabwirwa no kurabagirana kubera ibyishimo
  83,25,Bazahabwa ikinyobwa gipfundikiye
  83,26,"Intama ya nyuma (y’icyo kinyobwa) izaba ifite impumuro y’umubavu wa Miski. Kubera ibyo rero, ngaho abarushanwa nibarushanwe"
  83,27,(Icyo kinyobwa) kizavangwa n’ (amazi y’isoko ituruka mu iriba ryo mu ijuru ryitwa) Tas’niim
  83,28,Isoko izanyobwaho n’abazaba bari hafi (ya Allah)
  83,29,"Mu by’ukuri, (ku isi) inkozi z’ibibi zajyaga ziseka abemeramana"
  83,30,Bazinyuraho zikabaryanira inzara
  83,31,"Zaba zisubiye mu miryango yazo, zikabigira urwenya"
  83,32,"N’iyo zababonaga, zaravugaga ziti \"Mu by’ukuri, bariya barayobye"
  83,33,Nyamara ntabwo (izo nkozi z’ibibi) zashinzwe kuba abagenzuzi (b’abemeramana)
  83,34,"Ariko uyu munsi, abemeramana ni bo bari buseke abahakanyi"
  83,35,"Bicaye ku bitanda byiza, bitegereza (ibyiza barimo)"
  83,36,Ese abahakanyi ntabwo bahembewe ibyo bajyaga bakora
  84,1,Igihe ikirere kizasandara (ku munsi w’imperuka)
  84,2,Nuko kikumvira (itegeko rya) Nyagasani wacyo kandi ibyo birakwiye (ko kimwumvira)
  84,3,N’igihe isi izaringanizwa
  84,4,"Maze igasohora ibiyirimo (abapfuye), igasigarira aho"
  84,5,Nuko ikumvira (itegeko rya) Nyagasani wayo kandi ibyo birakwiye (ko imwumvira)
  84,6,"Yewe muntu! Mu by’ukuri, ukorana umuhate imirimo yawe ugana kwa Nyagasani wawe, kandi muzahura (ku munsi w’imperuka)"
  84,7,"Bityo, uzahabwa igitabo cye (cy’ibikorwa bye) mu kuboko kw’iburyo"
  84,8,Azabarurirwa mu buryo bworoshye
  84,9,"Kandi azasubira mu bantu be (umuryango we wakoze neza ku isi, ndetse n’abagore azagororerwa bo mu ijuru) yishimye"
  84,10,"Naho uzahabwa igitabo cye (cy’ibikorwa bye, akacyakirira) inyuma y’umugongo"
  84,11,Azisabira kurimbuka
  84,12,Kandi azinjira mu muriro ugurumana
  84,13,"Mu by’ukuri, (mu buzima bwo ku isi) yabagaho mu muryango we mu bwirasi"
  84,14,"Mu by’ukuri, yibwiraga ko atazagaruka (kwa Nyagasani we)"
  84,15,"Nyamara si byo! Mu by’ukuri, Nyagasani we yabaga amubona neza"
  84,16,"Bityo, ndahiriye ku gicu gitukura cy’izuba rirenga"
  84,17,No ku ijoro n’ibyo ritwikira (byose)
  84,18,No ku kwezi igihe kuzuye
  84,19,Ko rwose muzanyura mu byiciro bitandukanye (mu buzima bwa hano ku isi no ku munsi w’imperuka)
  84,20,"Ese babaye bate, kuki batemera"
  84,21,Ndetse n’iyo basomewe Qur’an ntibajya bubama
  84,22,Ahubwo abahakanye bahinyura (Intumwa Muhamadi n’inyigisho zayo)
  84,23,Kandi Allah azi neza ibyo bahisha (mu mitima yabo)
  84,24,"Bityo, bagezeho inkuru y’ibihano bibaza"
  84,25,"Uretse abemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza, bazagororerwa ibihembo bidashira (Ijuru)"
  85,1,Ndahiriye ku kirere gifite inyenyeri nini nyinshi
  85,2,No ku munsi w’isezerano (umunsi w’imperuka)
  85,3,No ku munsi w’ubuhamya (umunsi wa Idjuma) ndetse n’umunsi w’ikoraniro (umunsi wa Arafat)
  85,4,Abantu bacukuriye abemeramana imyobo (yo kubatwikiramo) baravumwe
  85,5,Ubwo bacanaga umuriro ugurumana
  85,6,Ubwo bari bawicaye impande
  85,7,Kandi babaga bashungereye ibyo bakoreraga abemeramana (babatwika)
  85,8,"Kandi nta kindi babahoraga usibye kuba baremeye Allah, Umunyembaraga uhebuje, Ushimwa cyane"
  85,9,Ufite ubwami bw’ibirere n’isi! Kandi Allah ni Umuhamya wa buri kintu
  85,10,"Mu by’ukuri, abatoteje abemeramana n’abemeramanakazi (babakorera iyicarubozo), nyuma ntibicuze (kuri Allah), bazahanishwa ibihano by’umuriro wa Jahanamu, banahanishwe ibihano bitwika"
  85,11,"Mu by’ukuri, abemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza, bazagororerwa ubusitani butembamo imigezi (Ijuru). Iyo ni yo ntsinzi ihebuje"
  85,12,"Mu by’ukuri, ibihano bya Nyagasani wawe (yewe Muhamadi) birakaze"
  85,13,"Mu by’ukuri, ni we waremye (ibiremwa bitari biriho) kandi ni na we uzabigarura (ku munsi w’imperuka)"
  85,14,"Kandi ni we Munyembabazi uhebuje, Umukunzi (w’abemeramana)"
  85,15,Ny’ir’intebe y’icyubahiro
  85,16,Ukora ibyo ashatse
  85,17,Ese wamenye inkuru z’ingabo
  85,18,Za Farawo n’iz’aba Thamudu
  85,19,Ahubwo abahakanye (bakomeje) guhinyura (ukuri)
  85,20,Kandi Allah azi neza ibikorwa byabo byose (kandi azabibahanira)
  85,21,Ahubwo iyi ni Qur’an yubahitse
  85,22,(Yanditse) ku rubaho rurinzwe
  86,1,Ndahiriye ku kirere no ku kimurika nijoro
  86,2,Ni iki cyakumenyesha ikimurika nijoro
  86,3,Ni inyenyeri imurika
  86,4,Nta muntu utagira umugenzuzi (abamalayika bashinzwe kugenzura ibikorwa bya muntu)
  86,5,Ngaho umuntu niyitegereze icyo yaremwemo
  86,6,Yaremwe mu mazi ataruka (intanga)
  86,7,Aturuka hagati y’urutirigongo n’ibituza
  86,8,"Mu by’ukuri, (Allah waremye uwo muntu mu ntanga) afite ubushobozi bwo kumuzura"
  86,9,Umunsi amabanga azahishurwa
  86,10,Icyo gihe (umuntu) nta mbaraga azaba afite cyangwa ngo agire umutabara
  86,11,Ndahiriye ku kirere gitanga imvura igenda igaruka
  86,12,No ku isi isaduka (kugira ngo ibiti n’ibimera bimere)
  86,13,"Mu by’ukuri, iyi (Qur’an) ni ijambo ritandukanya (ukuri n’ikinyoma)"
  86,14,Kandi ntabwo ari ijambo ridafite umumaro
  86,15,"Mu by’ukuri, (abahinyura ukuri) bacura umugambi mubisha (wo kurwanya ubutumwa bw’ukuri)"
  86,16,Maze nanjye (Allah) nkaburizamo umugambi wabo
  86,17,"Bityo, abo bahakanyi bahe igihe (yewe Muhamadi), ubarindirize gato (bazibonera ibizababaho)"
  87,1,"Singiza izina rya Nyagasani wawe, Uwikirenga"
  87,2,We waremye (buri kintu) akagitunganya
  87,3,"Akanakigenera (gahunda yacyo yose), hanyuma akayikiyoboramo"
  87,4,Ni nawe umeza ubwatsi mu nzuri
  87,5,Hanyuma akabwumisha bukijima
  87,6,"Rwose (yewe Muhamadi) tuzakwigisha (gusoma Qur’an), bityo ntuzayibagirwa"
  87,7,"Keretse ibyo Allah azashaka (ko wibagirwa). Mu by’ukuri, azi ibigaragara n’ibitagaragara"
  87,8,Tuzanakorohereza inzira yo gukora ibyiza
  87,9,"Bityo, ibutsa (abantu) igihe urwibutso rwabagirira akamaro"
  87,10,"Mu by’ukuri, hazibuka wa wundi utinya (Allah)"
  87,11,Kandi inkozi y’ibibi izarugendera kure
  87,12,(Uwo) ni we uzinjira mu muriro uhambaye
  87,13,Aho atazapfa (ngo aruhuke) cyangwa ngo agiriremo ubuzima (bwiza)
  87,14,"Mu by’ukuri, wawundi wiyejeje (akirinda ibyaha) yamaze kubona intsinzi"
  87,15,Akanasingiza izina rya Nyagasani we ndetse akanakora amasengesho
  87,16,Ariko mwe mukunda ubuzima bwo kuri iyi si
  87,17,Kandi ubwo ku mperuka ari bwo bwiza ndetse buzanahoraho
  87,18,"Mu by’ukuri, ibi (mubwirwa) biri mu byanditswe byo hambere"
  87,19,Inyandiko (zahishuriwe) Ibrahim na Musa
  88,1,Ese inkuru y’ibizatwikira (abantu ku munsi w’imperuka) yakugezeho
  88,2,"Kuri uwo munsi, uburanga bwa bamwe buzaba busuzuguritse"
  88,3,"(Igihe bari ku isi) babaga bakora cyane (basenga ibindi bitari Allah), (ariko ku mperuka) bazaba bananiwe (kandi bafite ikimwaro)"
  88,4,Bazinjira mu muriro utwika
  88,5,Kandi bazanyweshwa ku isoko (y’amazi) yatuye
  88,6,Nta byo kurya bazaba bafite uretse ibyatsi birura kandi bifite amahwa
  88,7,(Ibyo byo kurya) ntibizigera bibabyibushya cyangwa ngo bibamare inzara
  88,8,Kuri uwo munsi kandi (ubundi) buranga buzaba bukeye
  88,9,Bishimiye ibikorwa byabo
  88,10,(Bari) mu Ijuru rihambaye
  88,11,Aho batazumva amagambo adafite umumaro
  88,12,Hazaba harimo isoko itemba
  88,13,Hazaba harimo ibitanda byigiye hejuru
  88,14,N’ibikombe biteguwe (neza)
  88,15,N’imisego ishashe (neza)
  88,16,N’amatapi arambuye (biryoheye ijisho)
  88,17,Ese ntibitegereza uko ingamiya zaremwe
  88,18,N’uburyo ikirere cyahanitswe
  88,19,N’uburyo imisozi yashimangiwe (mu butaka)
  88,20,N’uburyo isi yarambuwe
  88,21,"Bityo, (yewe Muhamadi) bibutse kuko mu by’ukuri wowe uri uwibutsa"
  88,22,Ntukabashyireho igitugu
  88,23,Ariko utera umugongo (urwibutso) akanahakana
  88,24,Allah azamuhanisha ibihano bihambaye
  88,25,"Mu by’ukuri, iwacu ni ho garukiro ryabo"
  88,26,"Hanyuma mu by’ukuri, ni twe tuzabakorera ibarura"
  89,1,Ndahiriye ku museke
  89,2,No ku majoro cumi (ya mbere y’ukwezi gutagatifu kwa Dhul-Hijja)
  89,3,No ku kitari igiharwe ndetse n’igiharwe (mu biremwa byose bya Allah)
  89,4,No ku ijoro igihe rigiye gucya
  89,5,Ese muri izo (ndahiro) ntiharimo ibimenyetso bifatika ku muntu ufite ubwenge (bituma areka ibyaha n’ubuhakanyi)
  89,6,Ese (yewe Muhamadi) ntiwamenye uko Nyagasani wawe yagize aba Adi
  89,7,Bo mu bwoko bwa Irama (bari barebare cyane) bareshya nk’inkingi z’inyubako ndende
  89,8,Bo (abo ba Iram) ntihigeze haremwa abandi bameze nka bo mu yindi mijyi
  89,9,N’aba Thamudu bacongaga urutare mu bibaya (bakarukoramo inyubako)
  89,10,Na Farawo wari ufite imambo (yazirikagaho abantu abakorera iyicarubozo)
  89,11,Babandi bakoze ubugizi bwa nabi mu mijyi
  89,12,Maze bayikwizamo ubwangizi bukabije
  89,13,Nuko Nyagasani wawe abasukaho ibihano bibabaza
  89,14,"Mu by’ukuri, Nyagasani wawe yiteguye guhana (inkozi z’ibibi)"
  89,15,"Iyo Nyagasani agerageje umuntu, akamwubahisha akanamuhu- ndagazaho ingabire, aravuga ati \"Nyagasani wanjye yanyubahishije"
  89,16,"Nyamara yamugerageza akamugabanyiriza amafunguro, akavuga ati \"Nyagasani wanjye yaransuzuguje"
  89,17,Oya! Ahubwo ntimugirira neza imfubyi
  89,18,Ndetse nta n’ubwo mubwirizanya kugaburira abakene
  89,19,Kandi murya imirage (y’abandi) mukayimara
  89,20,Ndetse mugakunda imitungo bikabije
  89,21,Oya! Ubwo isi izasandazwa (igacikamo ibice)
  89,22,Nuko Nyagasani wawe akaza (guca imanza) ndetse n’abamalayika bari ku mirongo
  89,23,"Kandi uwo munsi umuriro wa Jahanamu uzazanwa. Kuri uwo munsi, umuntu azibuka, ariko se uko kwibuka kuzamumarira iki"
  89,24,"Azicuza avuga ati \"Iyaba nari narateganyirije ubuzima bwanjye (nkora ibikorwa byiza)"
  89,25,"Bityo, kuri uwo munsi (Allah) azahanisha ibihano bitashoborwa n’undi uwo ari we wese"
  89,26,Kandi azanaboha (abahakanyi) ukuboha kutashoborwa n’undi uwo ari we wese
  89,27,"(Umwemeramana azabwirwa ati) \"Yewe roho ituje"
  89,28,Garuka kwa Nyagasani wawe umwishimiye na we akwishimiye
  89,29,Maze winjire mu bagaragu banjye (b’intungane)
  89,30,Uninjire mu Ijuru ryanjye
  90,1,Ndahiriye kuri uyu mujyi (wa Maka)
  90,2,No kuri wowe (Ntumwa Muhamadi) utuye uyu mujyi
  90,3,No ku mubyeyi (Adamu) n’abo yabyaye
  90,4,"Mu by’ukuri, twaremye umuntu kugira ngo (abeho) mu ngorane"
  90,5,Ese akeka ko nta n’umwe wamushobora
  90,6,"Aravuga ati \"Nakoresheje umutungo mwinshi"
  90,7,Ese akeka ko nta n’umwe umubona
  90,8,Ese ntitwamuhaye amaso abiri
  90,9,Ndetse n’ururimi n’iminwa ibiri
  90,10,Tukanamwereka inzira ebyiri (iy’icyiza n’ikibi)
  90,11,Ariko ntiyigeze ashaka kunyura mu nzira igoranye (iganisha ku byiza n’intsinzi)
  90,12,Ese ni iki cyakumenyesha iyo nzira igoranye
  90,13,(Ni) ukubohora umucakara
  90,14,Cyangwa gutanga amafunguro ku munsi w’amapfa
  90,15,(Ayo mafunguro ukayaha) imfubyi mufitanye isano rya bugufi
  90,16,Cyangwa umukene (uryamye) mu ivumbi (uri mu kaga)
  90,17,"Hanyuma akaba umwe mu bemeramana, bakanagirana inama zo kwihangana ndetse bakanagirana inama zo kugira impuhwe"
  90,18,Abo ni abo mu kuboko kw’iburyo (mu Ijuru)
  90,19,"Naho abahakanye amagambo yacu, ni abo mu kuboko kw’ibumoso (mu muriro)"
  90,20,Bazaba bafungiranye mu muriro (badafite aho binjirira n’aho basohokera)
  91,1,Ndahiriye ku izuba n’urumuri rwaryo
  91,2,No ku kwezi igihe kurikurikiye
  91,3,No ku manywa igihe agaragaje urumuri (rw’izuba)
  91,4,No ku ijoro igihe riritwikiriye
  91,5,No ku kirere ndetse n’uwagihanze
  91,6,No ku isi n’uwayirambuye
  91,7,No kuri roho n’uwayitunganyije
  91,8,Hanyuma akayigaragariza ikibi n’icyiza
  91,9,"Mu by’ukuri, uweza roho ye (akubaha Allah kandi agakora ibikorwa byiza) yaratsinze"
  91,10,Kandi rwose uwatereranye roho ye ari mu gihombo
  91,11,Abantu ba Thamudu bahinyuye (Intumwa yabo) kubera kwigomeka
  91,12,Ubwo ubarusha ububi yahagurukanaga ibakwe (akajya kwica ingamiya y’imbyeyi)
  91,13,"Nuko Intumwa ya Allah (Swaleh) irababwira iti \"Iyo ni ingamiya ya Allah (ntimuyigirire nabi), kandi ntimuyibuze gushoka"
  91,14,"Ariko baramuhinyuye (ya ngamiya) barayica. Nuko Nyagasani wabo arabarimbura ku bw’icyaha cyabo, ndetse bose abarimbura mu buryo bureshya (baba abakuru n’abato, abakire n’abakene, ndetse n’abakomeye n’abaciriritse)"
  91,15,Kandi (Allah) ntatinya ingaruka zabyo
  92,1,Ndahiriye ku ijoro igihe riguye
  92,2,No ku manywa igihe atangaje
  92,3,No ku waremye ikigabo n’ikigore
  92,4,"Mu by’ukuri, ibikorwa byanyu biratandukanye"
  92,5,Wawundi utanga (amaturo) akanatinya (Allah)
  92,6,Kandi akizera icyiza (Ijuru)
  92,7,Tuzamworohereza inzira y’ibyiza
  92,8,"Ariko uzaba umunyabugugu, akirata yumva ko (yishoboye)"
  92,9,Akanahinyura icyiza
  92,10,Tuzamworohereza inzira y’ibibi
  92,11,"Kandi ubwo azaba arimbuka (ajyanywe mu muriro), umutungo we ntacyo uzamumarira"
  92,12,"Mu by’ukuri, ukuyobora ni ukwacu"
  92,13,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, ni na twe tugenga iby’imperuka n’ibibanza (iby’isi)"
  92,14,"Bityo, mbaburiye umuriro ugurumana"
  92,15,Ntawe uzawinjiramo utari inkozi y’ibibi
  92,16,Wawundi wahinyuye (ukuri) akanagutera umugongo
  92,17,"Ariko ukora ibikorwa byiza, azawurindwa"
  92,18,Wawundi utanga umutungo we kugira ngo yiyeze
  92,19,Kandi ntashishikazwe no kwiturwa n’uwo yagiriye neza
  92,20,"Ahubwo (akabikora agamije) gushaka kwishimirwa na Nyagasani we, Uwikirenga"
  92,21,Kandi rwose azishima (ubwo azinjira mu Ijuru)
  93,1,Ndahiriye ku gasusuruko
  93,2,No ku ijoro igihe ryijimye
  93,3,"(Yewe Muhamadi), Nyagasani wawe ntiyagutereranye kandi nta n’ubwo yakurakariye"
  93,4,Kandi rwose ubuzima bw’imperuka ni bwo bwiza kuri wowe kurusha ububanza (ubw’isi)
  93,5,"Mu by’ukuri, bidatinze Nyagasani wawe azaguha kandi uzishima"
  93,6,Ese ntiyagusanze uri imfubyi akaguha icumbi (abakwitaho)
  93,7,"Akanagusanga udasobanukiwe (Qur’an n’amategeko yayo), nuko akakuyobora"
  93,8,Akaba yaranagusanze uri umukene maze akagukungahaza (akaguha kunyurwa)
  93,9,"Bityo, ntugahutaze imfubyi"
  93,10,Ntukanakankamire uje asaba
  93,11,"Kandi ingabire za Nyagasani wawe (yaguhaye), ujye uzigaragaza (umushimira)"
  94,1,Ese (yewe Muhamadi) ntitwa- kwaguriye igituza
  94,2,Tukanagutura umutwaro (tukoro- hereza gusohoza ubutumwa)
  94,3,Wari ukuremereye umugongo
  94,4,Tukanamenyekanisha izina ryawe
  94,5,"Mu by’ukuri, nyuma y’ingorane haza ibihe byiza"
  94,6,"Rwose, nyuma y’ingorane haza ibihe byiza"
  94,7,"Bityo nuhuguka, ujye ushishikara (mu gusenga Allah)"
  94,8,Kandi (imigambi n’ibyiringiro byawe) ujye ubitura Nyagasani wawe (wenyine)
  95,1,Ndahiriye ku giti cy’umutini n’icy’umuzeti
  95,2,No ku Musozi wa Sinayi
  95,3,No kuri uyu mujyi utekanye (Maka)
  95,4,"Mu by’ukuri, twaremye umuntu mu ishusho ryiza"
  95,5,Hanyuma tumushyira ku rwego rwo hasi cyane (ageze mu zabukuru atagishoboye kugira icyo yimarira)
  95,6,"Ariko abemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza (n’iyo bageze mu zabukuru, hari ibikorwa byo kwiyegereza Imana bakomeza gukora); abo bazagororerwa ibihembo bidashira (Ijuru)"
  95,7,"Nonese nyuma y’ibyo (yewe muntu), ni iki kigutera guhakana umunsi w’ibihembo"
  95,8,Ese Allah si we Mucamanza usumba abandi
  96,1,Soma ku izina rya Nyagasani wawe waremye (ibiriho byose)
  96,2,Yaremye umuntu mu rusoro rw’amaraso
  96,3,Soma! Kandi Nyagasani wawe ni Umunyacyubahiro uhebuje
  96,4,We wigishije (umuntu kwandika) akoresheje ikaramu
  96,5,Yigishije umuntu ibyo atari azi
  96,6,"Oya! Mu by’ukuri, umuntu ararengera (arahakana kandi agakora ibibi)"
  96,7,Iyo amaze kubona ko yihagije (kubera ibyo atunze)
  96,8,"Mu by’ukuri, (umenye ko) kwa Nyagasani wawe ari ho garukiro"
  96,9,Ese (yewe Muhamadi) wabonye wawundi (Abu Jahl) ubuza
  96,10,Umugaragu (wacu Muhamadi) gusenga
  96,11,Ese yabuza ate (umugaragu wacu) aramutse ari mu nzira y’ukuri
  96,12,"Cyangwa ari gukangurira (abantu) gukora ibyiza, (mbwira icyaba iherezo ry’umubuza)"
  96,13,Ngaho mbwira (Abu Jahl) aramutse ahinyura (ukuri) akanatera umugongo
  96,14,Ese ntabwo azi ko Allah abona (ibyo akora)
  96,15,"Oya! Natarekera aho, tuzamufata uruhanga rwe turukururire mu muriro"
  96,16,"Uruhanga rubeshya, rw’urunyabyaha"
  96,17,Ngaho nahamagare abambari be
  96,18,Natwe tuzahamagara (abamalayika bacu) barinda umuriro (bamukanire urumukwiye)
  96,19,"Oya! (Yewe Muhamadi), ntukamwumvire (Abu Jahl), ahubwo ujye wubama (usenga) uniyegereze Allah"
  97,1,"Mu by’ukuri, (iyi Qur’an) twayihishuye mu ijoro ry’igeno"
  97,2,Ni iki cyakumenyesha ijoro ry’igeno
  97,3,Ijoro ry’igeno riruta amezi igihumbi (ibyiza bikozwe muri iryo joro birusha ibihembo ibikozwe mu gihe kingana n’amezi igihumbi)
  97,4,"Abamalayika na Roho (Malayika Jibril) barimanukanamo babiherewe uburenganzira na Nyagasani wabo, bazanye (amategeko agenga) buri kintu cyose"
  97,5,Iryo (joro ryose) riba ryuje amahoro (n’impuhwe za Allah ku bagaragu be) kugeza umuseke utambitse
  98,1,"Babandi bahakanye bo mu bahawe igitabo ndetse n’ababangikanyamana, ntibashobora kureka ubuhakanyi (bwabo) kugeza bagezweho n’ikimenyetso kigaragara"
  98,2,"(Icyo kimenyetso ni) Intumwa (Muhamadi) iturutse kwa Allah, ibasomera inyandiko zejejwe (Qur’an)"
  98,3,Zikubiyemo inkuru n’amategeko bitunganye
  98,4,"Kandi abahawe igitabo bacitsemo ibice nyuma y’uko bagezweho n’ikimenyetso kigaragara (kuko mbere y’uko Intumwa Muhamadi ihabwa ubutumwa, bose bayemeranyagaho kuko yari yarahanuwe mu bitabo byabo, ariko imaze kuza bamwe barayihakana)"
  98,5,"Kandi (no mu bitabo byabo) nta kindi bari barategetswe kitari ugusenga Allah bamwiyegurira, bahozaho amasengesho, ndetse bakanatanga amaturo. Iryo ni ryo dini ritunganye"
  98,6,"Mu by’ukuri, abahakanye bo mu bahawe igitabo ndetse n’ababangi- kanyamana bazaba mu muriro wa Jahanamu ubuziraherezo; abo ni bo babi mu biremwa"
  98,7,Naho abemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza; abo ni bo beza mu biremwa
  98,8,"Ibihembo byabo kwa Nyagasani wabo bizaba Ijuru rihoraho, ritembamo imigezi; (iryo Juru) bazaribamo ubuziraherezo. Allah yarabishimiye na bo baramwishimira. Ibyo (bihembo) ni iby’utinya Nyagasani we"
  99,1,Ubwo isi izatigiswa n’umutingito ukomeye
  99,2,Nuko isi igasohora ibiyirimo (abapfuye)
  99,3,"Umuntu azavuga ati \"Ese noneho (isi) yabaye iki"
  99,4,Uwo munsi (isi) izavuga inkuru zayo (z’ibyayibereyeho)
  99,5,Kubera ko Nyagasani wawe azaba yayibitegetse
  99,6,"Kuri uwo munsi, abantu bazasohoka (mu mva) batatanye kugira ngo berekwe ibikorwa byabo"
  99,7,"Icyo gihe uzaba yarakoze icyiza gifite uburemere bungana n’akantu gato cyane kurusha ibindi, azakibona (agihemberwe)"
  99,8,"N’uzaba yarakoze ikibi gifite uburemere bungana n’akantu gato cyane kurusha ibindi, azakibona (agihanirwe)"
  100,1,Ndahiriye ku mafarasi yiruka cyane avuza imirindi
  100,2,Akubita (ibinono) bigatarutsa ibishashi by’umuriro
  100,3,No ku mafarasi agaba igitero mu rukerera
  100,4,Akanatumura umukungugu
  100,5,Akinjira hagati mu ngabo z’umwanzi
  100,6,"Mu by’ukuri, umuntu ni indashima kuri Nyagasani we"
  100,7,Kandi rwose ibyo yabibera umuhamya
  100,8,Ndetse akunda imitungo bikabije
  100,9,Ese ntazi ko hari igihe abari mu mva bazazurwa
  100,10,N’ibiri mu bituza (by’abantu) bigashyirwa ahagaragara
  100,11,"Mu by’ukuri, uwo munsi Nyagasani wabo azaba azi neza ibyabo"
  101,1,Ikizahonda (umunsi w’imperuka)
  101,2,Ikizahonda ni iki
  101,3,Ni iki kizakumenyesha ikizahonda
  101,4,"Ni umunsi (w’imperuka), ubwo abantu bazamera nk’ibinyugunyugu binyanyagiye"
  101,5,N’imisozi ikamera nk’ipamba ritumuka
  101,6,"Bityo, uwo umunzani we (w’ibikorwa byiza) uzaremera (bikaruta ibibi)"
  101,7,Azaba mu buzima bw’umunezero (Ijuru)
  101,8,Ariko uwo umunzani we (w’ibikorwa byiza) uzaba utaremereye (bikarutwa n’ibibi)
  101,9,Ubuturo bwe buzaba ari mu muriro witwa Hawiya
  101,10,Ni iki cyawukumenyesha (umuriro wa Hawiya)
  101,11,Ni umuriro ugurumana bikabije
  102,1,Mwarangajwe no gushaka kwigwizaho ubutunzi
  102,2,Kugeza ubwo mugeze mu mva
  102,3,Oya ntibikwiye! Bidatinze muzamenya (ko ubuzima bw’imperuka ari bwo bwiza kuri mwe)
  102,4,Oya nanone! Bidatinze muzamenya
  102,5,"Oya! Iyo muza kugira ubumenyi budashidikanywaho (bw’ibijyanye n’iherezo ryo kurangazwa no kwigwizaho imitungo, ntimwari guhugira mu by’isi)"
  102,6,"Mu by’ukuri, muzabona umuriro wa Jahanamu"
  102,7,Rwose muzawibonera imbonankubone
  102,8,"Kandi rwose, kuri uwo munsi muzabazwa ku ngabire (mwahawe muri ku isi)"
  103,1,Ndahiriye ku gihe
  103,2,"Mu by’ukuri, umuntu ari mu gihombo"
  103,3,"Uretse abemeye bagakora ibikorwa byiza, bakagirana inama z’ukuri kandi bakanagirana inama zo kwihangana"
  104,1,"Ibihano bikomeye bizaba kuri buri wese unegura abandi, usebanya"
  104,2,Urundanya imitungo agahora ayibara
  104,3,Yibwira ko umutungo we uzatuma abaho ubuziraherezo
  104,4,"Oya! Mu by’ukuri, azajugunywa mu muriro witwa Hutwama (ushwanyaguza)"
  104,5,Ni iki kizakumenyesha Hutwama
  104,6,Ni umuriro wa Allah ucanye
  104,7,(Uwo muriro) uzajya uzamuka ugere ku mitima (y’abazaba bawurimo)
  104,8,"Mu by’ukuri, bazaba bawufungiwemo"
  104,9,(Baziritse) ku nkingi ndende (kugira ngo batawusohokamo)
  105,1,Ese (yewe Muhamadi) ntiwamenye uko Nyagasani wawe yagize abagabye igitero bari ku nzovu (baje gusenya ingoro ya al Kaabat iri i Maka)
  105,2,Ese umugambi wabo mubisha ntiyawuburijemo
  105,3,Nuko akaboherereza uruhuri rw’inyoni
  105,4,Zikabatera amabuye y’ibumba yatuye
  105,5,Maze akabagira nk’ibyatsi byakanjakanjwe
  106,1,Kubera imibanire y’aba Quraish (mu mujyi wabo)
  106,2,No kubera ingendo zabo (z’ubucuruzi) zo mu gihe cy’ubukonje no mu cy’impeshyi (batekanye)
  106,3,"Bityo, nibagaragire (Allah) Nyagasani nyir’iyi ngoro (Al Ka’aba)"
  106,4,"(We) wabagaburiye mu gihe cy’amapfa, ndetse akanabaha umutekano mu gihe cy’ubwoba"
  107,1,Ese wamenye uhinyura umunsi w’ibihembo
  107,2,Uwo ni wa wundi uhutaza imfubyi
  107,3,Ntanashishikarize (abandi) kugaburira abakene
  107,4,"Bityo, ibihano bikomeye biri ku basenga"
  107,5,Babandi birengagiza amasengesho yabo (ntibayakorere ku bihe byayo byagenwe)
  107,6,Babandi bakora ibyiza bagamije kwiyerekana
  107,7,Kandi bakanga (gutiza) ibikoresho byo mu rugo (ku babikeneye)
  108,1,"Mu by’ukuri, (yewe Muhamadi) twaguhaye (ibyiza byinshi birimo) umugezi wo mu Ijuru witwa Kawthar"
  108,2,"Bityo, ujye usenga unatange ibitambo kubera Nyagasani wawe"
  108,3,"Mu by’ukuri, ukwanga ni we nyakamwe (ntazigera abona ibyiza haba ku isi ndetse no ku mperuka)"
  109,1,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Yemwe bahakanyi"
  109,2,Sinsenga ibyo musenga
  109,3,Kandi na mwe ntimusenga uwo nsenga
  109,4,Ndetse nanjye sinzigera nsenga ibyo musenga
  109,5,Kandi namwe ntimuzigera musenga uwo nsenga
  109,6,"Mufite idini ryanyu, nanjye nkagira idini ryanjye"
  110,1,"Igihe ubutabazi bwa Allah (kuri wowe Muhamadi) buzaza, ndetse n’intsinzi (yo kubohora umujyi wa Maka)"
  110,2,Nuko ukabona abantu binjira mu idini rya Allah ku bwinshi
  110,3,"Uzasingize ikuzo rya Nyagasani wawe, unamusabe imbabazi; kuko ari we Uwakira ukwicuza (kw’abagaragu be)"
  111,1,"Amaboko yombi ya Abu Lahab147 arakorama (kubera ko yayakoreshaga abangamira Intumwa y’Imana), ndetse na we ubwe azorama"
  111,2,Umutungo we n’urubyaro rwe ntacyo bizamumarira
  111,3,Azinjira mu muriro ugurumana
  111,4,Ndetse n’umugore we watwaraga ibiti (by’amahwa yajyaga atega mu nzira Intumwa y’Imana yanyuragamo)
  111,5,Mu ijosi rye (uwo mugore) hazaba hari umurunga wo mu muriro
  112,1,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"We ni Allah, umwe Rukumbi"
  112,2,"Allah, Uwishingikirizwa"
  112,3,Ntiyabyaye kandi ntiyanabyawe
  112,4,Ndetse nta na kimwe ahwanye na cyo
  113,1,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Nikinze kuri (Allah), Nyagasani w’igitondo"
  113,2,Ngo andinde inabi y’ibyo yaremye
  113,3,Anandinde ikibi cyo mu ijoro ryijimye igihe riguye
  113,4,Anandinde ikibi cy’abarozikazi bahuha ku mapfundo
  113,5,Ndetse anandinde inabi y’umunyeshyari igihe arigize
  114,1,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Nikinze kuri (Allah), Nyagasani w’abantu"
  114,2,Umwami w’abantu
  114,3,Imana y’abantu
  114,4,"Ngo andinde ububi bwa (shitani) yoshya gukora ibibi, nyuma ikabireka (igihe umuntu yibutse Allah)"
  114,5,Yoshya imitima y’abantu gukora ibibi
  114,6,Yaba (shitani) yo mu majini cyangwa mu bantu